NK131(do)006:1: // rdzogs pa chen po gsang sngags rnying ma la //
NK131(do)006:3: rdzogs chen dka' gnad sbas pa yi //
NK131(do)006:4: sgo 'byed lde mig chen po yod //
NK131(do)006:6: log rtog ngan pa bzlog pa'i bstan bcos /
NK131(do)006:7: 'khrul pa thams cad rab tu 'joms pa zhes bya ba /
NK131(do)006:8: gsung rdo rje longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK131(do)006:9: gzhom du med pa'i sgra dbyangs can /
NK131(do)006:10: mtha' yas pa mtha' yas pa'i gsung gis //
NK131(do)006:11: mtha' yas pa mtha' yas pa'i sems can sna tshogs pa rnams la /
NK131(do)006:12: mtha' yas pa mtha' yas pa'i chos ston par mdzad pa'i //
NK131(do)006:13: ston pa thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK131(do)006:14: nyi tse ba'i tshig 'bru la rten nas /
NK131(do)006:17: ngan 'gror ltung ba rnams thugs rjes bzung du gsol /
NK131(do)006:18: sna tshogs skur ston 'di ni tshangs sku ma yin
NK131(do)006:19: sku yi rdo rje sgyu 'phrul dra ba sprul pa'i
NK131(do)006:20: sku / rang rang skad du legs par 'doms 'di
NK131(do)006:21: dbang phyug ma yin gsung gi rdo rje gzhom med
NK131(do)006:22: sku / longs spyod rdzogs / ji lta ji snyed
NK131(do)006:23: mkhyen 'di khyab 'jug ma yin thugs kyi rdo rje
NK131(do)006:24: mkha' dbyings kun khyab chos kyi sku /
NK131(do)006:25: sku gsum so sor ston kyang debazhina nyid las ma
NK131(do)006:26: g.yos lhan gcig skyes pa ngo bo nyid kyi sku
NK131(do)006:27: / gang yin de la dang por btud nas ma
NK131(do)006:28: rtogs log rtog tshig la rab 'khrul 'khrul 'joms brjod
NK131(do)006:29: / par bya // de la 'dir don la ston pa'i shes rab dang /
NK131(do)006:30: gzu bo gnas pa'i blo dang ni mi ldan /
NK131(do)006:31: phyogs 'dzin yid kyi mun stug gis ni bsgribs /
NK131(do)006:32: nyi tse ba'i sgra tshig yi ge la ni rten cing /
NK131(do)006:34: shes par rlom pa'i mngon pa'i nga rgyal can gyi gang zag kha cig gis /
NK131(do)006:35: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse dang /
NK131(do)006:36: snying po dam par gyur pa'i dam chos rdzogs pa chen po dang /
NK131(do)006:37: sngags snying ma'i mdo rgyud dgongs 'grel gdams pa dang bcas pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:38: de rnams la thos bsam sgom gsum byed pa'i /
NK131(do)006:39: rgya bod kyi mkhas grub rnams la bkur pa btab nas /
NK131(do)006:40: chos spong gi las bsags pa'i log rtog gi phreng ba 'di la brjod par bya ste /
NK131(do)006:41: phyogs zhen gyi dri mas ma slad pa'i skyes bu dam pa rnams kyis gzigs par zhu'o //
NK131(do)006:42: de la log rtog gi phreng bar 'di skad lo //
NK131(do)006:43: 'di ltar bcom dbu ru stod kyi mkhas par grags pa bod kyi dpal 'dzin bzang po na re /
NK131(do)006:45: ma 'ongs pa'i dus na rang gi bstan pa la /
NK131(do)006:46: bdud kyi chos phyin ci log 'byung bar mkhyen nas /
NK131(do)006:47: chos la brtag pa'i chos 'dul ba dang /
NK131(do)006:48: mdo sde dag las rgya cher bshad /
NK131(do)006:49: khyad par du gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa la ma brtags par /
NK131(do)006:51: chos phyin ci log pa'i rgyus dmyal bar 'gro bas /
NK131(do)006:52: chos dang bla ma dang slob ma gsum la brtags shing dpyad nas /
NK131(do)006:53: gsum ka la yid ches nas sdod 'chad nyan bya bar gsungs /
NK131(do)006:55: thog mar rang gi tshig dang yang 'gal te /
NK131(do)006:57: bdud kyi chos phyin ci log 'byung bar mkhyen nas chos la brtag pa bshad na /
NK131(do)006:58: bod lta bu'i yul chung re rer chos log gang byung lung ston gyis mi lang pa 'gal lo //
NK131(do)006:59: de lung ston gyis mi lang na /
NK131(do)006:60: thams cad mkhyen pas sems can mos pa'i dbang gis /
NK131(do)006:61: yul so so'i skad kyis sems can sna tshogs pa rnams la chos sna tshogs pa ston pa 'gal /
NK131(do)006:62: chos sna tshogs pa ma bstan na ni thams cad mkhyen pa yin par 'gal lo //
NK131(do)006:63: spyir yang chos la brtag pa'i cho ga yang spyir
NK131(do)006:64: btang tsam la yin gyis dmigs kyis bsal ba la
NK131(do)006:65: de tsam gyis chos min du mi 'grub ste 'og
NK131(do)006:66: nas 'chad do / brtag pa gsum ni shin tu nas kyang bshed /
NK131(do)006:67: slob dpon chen po pad+ma sam b+ha was /
NK131(do)006:68: bla mas slob ma ma brtags bcud med chos kyis 'brel /
NK131(do)006:69: slob mas bla ma ma brtags bcud med chos kyis 'brel /
NK131(do)006:70: gnyis kas dam tshig ma bsrungs be sbrel g.yang sar ltung /
NK131(do)006:71: de 'dra'i dpon slob dus kyi mtha' la 'byung /
NK131(do)006:73: zhes pa chos rje bu ston rin po ches /
NK131(do)006:74: dus 'khor gyi bla ma'i mtshan nyid brtag pa'i skabs su drangs nas gsungs shing /
NK131(do)006:75: gzhan yang slob dpon gyi 'brel dang /
NK131(do)006:76: snod brtag pa la sogs la /
NK131(do)006:77: bla ma lnga bcu pa nas lo bcur 'grogs pas brtag thub bu la bstan /
NK131(do)006:78: zhes sogs rin chen gling pa can /
NK131(do)006:79: bshad pa la sogs las kyang rgyas pa yod pas /
NK131(do)006:80: bla ma dang slob ma'i brtag pa med pa'i shes byed ci yang khyed la med do //
NK131(do)006:83: sgra tshig dang 'gal ba lta bu dang /
NK131(do)006:86: ma tshang ba lta bu ni /
NK131(do)006:87: chos min dang bka' min du mi 'grub par /
NK131(do)006:89: bde mchog stod 'grel sogs sems 'grel rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:90: n+aa ro 'grel chen sogs las gsal bar gsungs pa 'di yin /
NK131(do)006:91: tshig la mi ston don la ston pa dpang du byas te brtags pas 'grub na ni /
NK131(do)006:92: rgya gar gyi pan chen dang /
NK131(do)006:102: sras mo go ma d+he bi /
NK131(do)006:109: pan chen sh+aakya sh+ri la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:110: bod kyi bee ro tsa na /
NK131(do)006:118: rtsag la sogs pa'i mkhas grub rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:119: khon klu dbang bsrung ba nas /
NK131(do)006:120: chos rje bsod nams rgyal mtshan yan chad kyi sa skya pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:121: rngog legs shes la sogs pa'i bka' gdams pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:124: mtshal 'brug la sogs dgas po bka' rgyud pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:125: shangs pa bka' rgyud pa'i bla ma ji snyed gcig gis /
NK131(do)006:126: thos bsam sgom gsum mdzad pa 'di kho nas kyang yid ches par 'grub ste /
NK131(do)006:127: blo chung skal med log rtog can gyi spyod yul du ma gyur pa 'di zhe re 'gyod /
NK131(do)006:128: de ltar brtag pa gsum dang /
NK131(do)006:129: yid ches gsum gyis 'jug pa ni shin tu nas kyang yod la /
NK131(do)006:130: da lta kha cig thun mong du ma gyur pas ni med par mi 'grub ste /
NK131(do)006:131: khyed rang la yang mtshungs so //
NK131(do)006:134: deng sang rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya ba'i rgyud
NK131(do)006:135: gzhung mtha' yas pa gcig 'dug /'di ni kun tu
NK131(do)006:136: bzang pos gsungs / dga' rab rdo rje dang /
NK131(do)006:140: ku ku ra tsa la sogs pa /
NK131(do)006:141: u rgyan dang rgya gar gyi mkhas grub thams cad kyi nyams len gyi gtso bo 'di yin /
NK131(do)006:143: b+ai ma la mi tra dang /
NK131(do)006:144: bee ro tsa nas bod du khyer nas byon te /
NK131(do)006:145: sngon gyi rgyal slon byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi dus su bsgyur ba yin zer ba 'dug /
NK131(do)006:147: rgya bod kyi pan grub de rnams kyi nyams len min pa dang /
NK131(do)006:148: rgyal blon de rnams kyi sku ring la ku ku
NK131(do)006:149: ra tsas sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor skor rin chen rdo
NK131(do)006:151: ma bsgyur ba'i shes byed dang lung rig tshad ma ci yang med /
NK131(do)006:152: bod kyi skyes chen dam pa snga phyir byon pa thams cad dang /
NK131(do)006:153: sa pan dang bu dol la sogs pa rnams /
NK131(do)006:154: snga 'gyur gsang sngags rnying ma zhes dang /
NK131(do)006:155: sngags rnying ma rnams 'di ltar bzhed ces /
NK131(do)006:156: gsung gcig tu bsnyad pa la snyon du med do /
NK131(do)006:157: gal te de rnams kyis nyams su ma blangs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:160: de rnams la kha 'phangs nas rang bzor byas par 'dod na ni ha cang thal te /
NK131(do)006:161: gong du smos pa'i sa skya pa la sogs pa rnams kyang /
NK131(do)006:162: rang bzo'i rdzun gyi rjes su 'brengs nas chos log spyod ces /
NK131(do)006:163: bkur pa btags par shugs la grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:164: gzhan yang mang ste mtha' med do //
NK131(do)006:166: 'on kyang 'di la brtags shing dpyad na /
NK131(do)006:167: dang por brtsom pa'i nyams ngan pas 'gal ba dang /
NK131(do)006:170: zlos pa dang rang bzhin gyi skal ba ngan pa byis pa dang /
NK131(do)006:172: smyon pa'i tshig gi mtshan nyid ci rigs pa tshang ba zhig 'dug /
NK131(do)006:176: sngags kyi skabs rgya gar dang u rgyan gyi skad du 'dod pa rnams la /
NK131(do)006:177: rgya gar gyi skad rigs kyi rnam pa blo yul du ma shar bar /
NK131(do)006:179: zha za 'a rnams bsres pa dang /
NK131(do)006:180: bod skad kyi shan 'dres pa dang /
NK131(do)006:181: gsal byed re re'i khongs su /
NK131(do)006:182: dbyangs i u e o mi mthun pa gnyis sam /
NK131(do)006:183: gsum dang bzhi zhugs pa la sogs pa'i sgra nor ba mtha' yas pa byung 'dug /
NK131(do)006:187: nang rig pa'i chos skad dang 'brel ba'i skad rnams su /
NK131(do)006:188: de dag ma shes pa'i blun tshig mtha' yas pa byung 'dug /
NK131(do)006:189: gza' sgra gcan gyi ming la khyab 'jug tu 'dod pa dang /
NK131(do)006:191: bdud po skos rje brang dkar zhes zer ba la sogs pa /
NK131(do)006:192: lha klu lha min 'byung po dang /
NK131(do)006:196: ljon shing la sogs pa ming gi brjod pa nor ba /
NK131(do)006:197: phyi nang gtsug lag gang dang yang mi mthun pa mang du 'dug /'gogs po dang /
NK131(do)006:203: bzed la sogs pa'i mi ma yin gyi rigs kyi ming /
NK131(do)006:204: rgya gar gyi skad dod la med cing /
NK131(do)006:207: bon po'i gzhung las drangs pa /
NK131(do)006:211: de la brtsom pa'i nyams bzang ba dang 'gal ba dang /
NK131(do)006:214: zlos pa sogs rnams med pas /
NK131(do)006:215: sangs rgyas kyi bka' tshad ma yin par 'dod na /
NK131(do)006:216: de ni shin tu nas kyang mi 'thad de /
NK131(do)006:217: de lta na phyi rol mu stegs byed kyi gzhung lugs rnams /
NK131(do)006:218: rtsod pa dang bral ba'i gzhung lugs rnam dag tu 'gyur te /
NK131(do)006:219: phyi rol pa'i ston pa dbang phyug dang /
NK131(do)006:221: sgra tshig yi ge la rten zhing /
NK131(do)006:222: legs sbyar gyi skad gcig pus mtho rigs su 'gro bar 'dod pa'i bram ze dang /
NK131(do)006:223: sgra smra ba'i drang srong rnams kyis byas pa'i gzhung
NK131(do)006:224: lugs rnams brtsom pa'i nyams bzang pas 'gal 'du med
NK131(do)006:225: pa dang / tshig gi sdebs sbyor legs pas 'brel chags pa dang /
NK131(do)006:226: zlos pa rnams med pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:227: de'i phyir thams cad mkhyen pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni /
NK131(do)006:228: don la ston pa nyid la rten nas yul so so'i sems can sna tshogs pa rnams la /
NK131(do)006:229: rang rang gi yul gyi skad kyi chos sna tshogs pa rnams ston pa'i phyir na /
NK131(do)006:230: lce rkan gyi rtsol bas bskyed pa'i lha'i skad gcig pu dang /
NK131(do)006:231: sgra tshig yi ge rnams la rten pa ma yin pas so //
NK131(do)006:232: des na dus kyi 'khor lo'i rgya 'grel dri med 'od las /
NK131(do)006:233: sgra bzang po smra ba rnams kyi sgra bzang po la zhen pa spang ba'i slad du /
NK131(do)006:234: don la ston pa nyid la rten te /
NK131(do)006:236: kha cig tu sgra nyams pa dang /
NK131(do)006:237: kha cig tu gcod 'tshams nyams pa dang /
NK131(do)006:238: kha cig tu rnam dbye med pa'i tshig dang /
NK131(do)006:239: kha cig tu dbyangs dang gsal byed phyis pa dang /
NK131(do)006:240: kha cig tu ring po la thung ngu dang /
NK131(do)006:241: thung ngu la ring po dang /
NK131(do)006:242: kha cig tu lnga pa'i don la bdun pa dang /
NK131(do)006:243: bzhi pa'i don la drug pa dang /
NK131(do)006:244: gzhan gyi tshig la bdag nyid kyi tshig dang /
NK131(do)006:245: bdag nyid kyi tshig la gzhan gyi tshig dang /
NK131(do)006:246: kha cig tu gcig gi tshig la mang po'i tshig dang /
NK131(do)006:247: mang po la gcig tshig dang /
NK131(do)006:248: kha cig tu pho'i rtags can la ma ning gi rtags dang /
NK131(do)006:249: ma ning la mo'i rtags dang /
NK131(do)006:250: kha gcig tu ni rkan las byung pa la swo dang spyi bo las 'byung pa dang /
NK131(do)006:251: kha gcig tu spyi bo las 'byung pa la swo dang rkan las 'byung ba ste /
NK131(do)006:252: gzhan yang rjes su rtogs par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:255: sgra bzang po mngon pa'i nga rgyal nyams par bya ba'i slad du /
NK131(do)006:256: bdag gis don la ston pa nyid la rten te bri bar bya'o //
NK131(do)006:260: byis pa'i skye bo tshig 'bru la rab tu ston pa la ma rten pa rnams kyis /
NK131(do)006:261: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa zhes pa la sogs pa dang bral ba'i /
NK131(do)006:262: rgyud kyi rgyal po ni bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)006:263: zhes gang zhig smra bar 'gyur ba de ni ma yin te /
NK131(do)006:264: gang gi phyir bcom ldan 'das kyis gzhan du rten pa bzhi gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:266: don la ston par bya yis /
NK131(do)006:267: tshig 'bru la ston pa ma yin pa dang /
NK131(do)006:268: ye shes la ston par bya yis /
NK131(do)006:269: rnam shes la ston par bya ba ma yin pa dang /
NK131(do)006:270: nges don la ston par bya yis /
NK131(do)006:271: drang don la ston pa ma yin pa dang /
NK131(do)006:272: chos la ston par bya yis /
NK131(do)006:273: gang zag la rten par bya ba ma yin pa'o //
NK131(do)006:275: tshig 'bru la rab tu rten pa ni /
NK131(do)006:276: theg pa gang du yang bcom ldan 'das kyis ma gsungs so //
NK131(do)006:279: rang rang skad kyi khyad par rnams kyis ni /
NK131(do)006:280: srid gsum ma lus lam la legs bkod nas /
NK131(do)006:281: kun mkhyen gsung 'dis zhi bde'i 'bras bu ster /
NK131(do)006:282: lha yi skad las de dag gang du 'gyur /
NK131(do)006:283: zhes dang bsdus rgyud kyi rgyal po ye shes le'u las kyang /
NK131(do)006:284: dud 'gro yi dwags lha min rnams dang lho 'phye lha mi 'phags pa bod la sogs rnams la /
NK131(do)006:285: byung dang 'byung 'gyur da ltar byung ba rnam pa gsum dang rtag tu bden pa'i chos gsung zhing /
NK131(do)006:286: rang rang skad gzhan rnams kyis srid gsum ma tshang med pa lam la yang dag 'god byed pa /
NK131(do)006:287: 'di ni bde mnyam 'bras bu ster ba thams cad mkhyen pa'i gsung ste lha yi skad kyis min /
NK131(do)006:289: dri med 'od kyi 'jig rten khams le'i mdor bsdus dang por /
NK131(do)006:290: kun mkhyen lam don gnyer ba rnams la sgra dang sgra min rnam dpyad chen po med /
NK131(do)006:291: sna tshogs yul skad ngan pa yis kyang chen po rnams kyi lam la rtag tu 'jug /
NK131(do)006:292: sems can rnams kyi mos pa'i sems kyi dbang gis thams cad mkhyen pa'i gsung mchog la /
NK131(do)006:293: brda sprod pa la klus bkod pa yi sgra rtsogs rtsod pa don gnyer rnams kyi de las gzhan /
NK131(do)006:294: sgra nyams pa dang yul gyi skad las kyang /
NK131(do)006:295: rnal 'byor ldan pas don ni 'dzin byed de /
NK131(do)006:296: chu la 'o ma nges par zhugs pa de /
NK131(do)006:297: ngang pas rab tu phyung te 'thung bar byed /
NK131(do)006:298: don dam de nyid yul la rtag tu ni /
NK131(do)006:299: chen po dag rnams tshig la rton pa min /
NK131(do)006:300: yul gyi skad rnams kyis ni don shes na /
NK131(do)006:301: bstan bcos sgra dag gis ni ci zhig bya /
NK131(do)006:302: gang zhig zur chag sgra dang sgra gyur pa /
NK131(do)006:303: brjod pa de nyid ye shes ma yin zhing /
NK131(do)006:304: gang zhig 'gro ba dag la nyi tse ba /
NK131(do)006:305: de ni thams cad mkhyen pa'i gsung ma yin /
NK131(do)006:309: byis pa'i skye bo ming tshig yi ge la rten la /
NK131(do)006:310: rten pa dag gis rgyud thams cad du 'di skad bdag gis zhes sogs kyis /
NK131(do)006:311: sangs rgyas kyi bzhugs gnas nges par bstan par /
NK131(do)006:312: de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs par gang brjod pa de ni ma yin te /
NK131(do)006:313: gang gi phyir chos ston pa po'i sangs rgyas don
NK131(do)006:314: la ston pa la rten pa nyid kyi phyir dang
NK131(do)006:315: / bsdud par byed pa po rnams kyis kyang yul
NK131(do)006:316: sna tshogs kyi skad gzhan gyis yang dag par byed
NK131(do)006:317: / pa'i phyir ro // 'dir gal te 'di skad bdag gis thos pa la sogs /
NK131(do)006:318: legs par sbyar ba'i tshig mgrin pa dang rkan la
NK131(do)006:319: sogs pa'i 'bad rtsol gyis bskyed pa nyi tse bas
NK131(do)006:320: / de bzhin gshegs pa chos ston par byed pa
NK131(do)006:321: de ltar na chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi
NK131(do)006:322: / stong / dus du mar yang de bzhin gshegs pas bstan pa dang /
NK131(do)006:323: bsdud pa pos kyang bri bar mi nus te /
NK131(do)006:324: nyi tse ba legs par sbyar ba'i tshig gcig bu yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:325: 'dir sprul pa'i sku mtha' yas pa med pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)006:326: mtha' yas pa mtha' yas pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams rnams su /
NK131(do)006:327: mtha' yas pa mtha' yas pa'i sems can rnams kyis
NK131(do)006:328: sgra dag gis gcig char du chos ston pa yang
NK131(do)006:330: chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong ston par byed pa med pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)006:331: thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin par 'gyur te de lta ma yin no //
NK131(do)006:334: dge 'dun tshad med par de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa 'di'i phyir /
NK131(do)006:335: chos ston pa po'i thams cad mkhyen pa po ni gcig ma yin no //
NK131(do)006:336: thams cad mkhyen pa'i skad gang sems can thams cad
NK131(do)006:337: kyi skad rnams don rtogs par byed pa gcig ma
NK131(do)006:338: yin no // bzhugs pa'i gnas nges par bstan pa gcig ma yin no //
NK131(do)006:339: de bzhin gshegs pa'i nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang /
NK131(do)006:340: gsol ba 'debs pa po gcig ma yin gyi /
NK131(do)006:341: 'dir sems can rnams kyi mos pa sna tshogs kyi dbang gis thams cad mkhyen pa du ma dang /
NK131(do)006:342: thams cad mkhyen pa'i skad du ma dang /
NK131(do)006:343: bzhugs pa'i gnas du ma dang /
NK131(do)006:345: de'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pas mgrin pa dang /
NK131(do)006:346: rkan la sogs pa'i 'bad rtsol gyis bskyed pa'i lha'i
NK131(do)006:347: skad gcig bus rgyud thams cad bstan pa ma yin
NK131(do)006:350: bcom ldan 'das mtha' yas pa'i chos ston pa po yin pa 'di'i phyir /
NK131(do)006:351: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa la sogs pas /
NK131(do)006:352: rgyud kyi rgyal po thams cad du bzhugs pa'i gnas nges par bstan zhes /
NK131(do)006:353: sangs rgyas pa rnams kyis brjod par mi bya'o //
NK131(do)006:354: sems can thams cad kyi skad kyi rang bzhin thams cad mkhyen pa'i skad med par /
NK131(do)006:355: legs par sbyar ba'i skad nyi tse ba gcig bu
NK131(do)006:356: 'di yis yin na sangs rgyas kyang nyi tse bar
NK131(do)006:357: 'gyur ro // 'phags yul 'dir sgra smra ba po /
NK131(do)006:358: mu stegs pa mkhas pa mngon pa'i nga rgyal dang ldan pa rnams mthong nas /
NK131(do)006:361: zhi ba pa la sogs pa rnams kyis /
NK131(do)006:364: drag po la sogs pa rnams legs par sbyar ba'i smra ba po yin pa de bzhin du /
NK131(do)006:365: bdag cag gi 'dod pa'i lha sangs rgyas dang /
NK131(do)006:366: byangachuba sems dpa' thams cad kyang /
NK131(do)006:367: legs par sbyar ba'i smra ba po yin no //
NK131(do)006:369: sangs rgyas pa byis pa'i blo can rnams kyi bsam pa ste /
NK131(do)006:370: 'dir sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' de dag thams cad /
NK131(do)006:371: thams cad mkhyen pa'i skad med par /
NK131(do)006:372: legs par sbyar ba'i skad nyi tse ba 'di yis ma yin te /
NK131(do)006:373: sems can thams cad kyi skad kyis chos ston par byed pa po dang /
NK131(do)006:374: yang dag par bsdud par byed pa po yin no //
NK131(do)006:375: de'i phyir sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams
NK131(do)006:376: ni lha'i skye ba dang 'brel ba nyi tse bas
NK131(do)006:377: ma yin te / sems can sna tshogs kyi skad kyis chos ston pa po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:380: sgra gcig bu legs par sbyar ba'i skad kyis mtho ris su 'dod pa 'ajo'o zhes pa ni /
NK131(do)006:381: log pa'i nga rgyal gyi zil gyis gnon pa rnams kyi bsam pa ste /
NK131(do)006:382: thams cad mkhyen pa'i skad med pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:384: 'dir khyab 'jug dang drag po la sogs pa rnams kyis bstan pa'i chos nyi tse ba /
NK131(do)006:385: sems can thams cad la brtse ba dang bral ba /'khor ba'i sdug bsngal ster bar byed pa /
NK131(do)006:386: log pa'i nga rgyal bskyed par byed pa /
NK131(do)006:387: rigs su smra ba mngon par khengs par byed pa dag la /
NK131(do)006:388: sangs rgyas pa rnams kyis rjes su yi rang bar mi bya'o //
NK131(do)006:390: sgra tshig yi ge la rten pa rnams ltar ni /
NK131(do)006:391: de rnams la snying po rab mchog dam pa byed nas /
NK131(do)006:392: rjes su yi rang par bya dgos par 'dug ste /
NK131(do)006:393: de rnams dang rjes su 'thun pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:395: re zhig yul gyi khyad par gzhan lta zhog gi /
NK131(do)006:396: de bzhin gshegs pa mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa /
NK131(do)006:397: 'phags yul 'dir bcom ldan 'das yongs su mya ngan las 'das par gyur pa na /
NK131(do)006:398: bsdud par byed pa po dag gis /
NK131(do)006:399: theg pa gsum glegs bam la bris te /
NK131(do)006:400: de bzhin gshegs pas nges pa'i sde snod gsum ma ga ta'i skad kyis so //
NK131(do)006:401: mdo sde ni sin d+hu'i skad kyis so //
NK131(do)006:402: pha rol tu phyin pa'i tshul dang /
NK131(do)006:403: sngags kyi tshul ni legs sbyar gyis skad kyis so //
NK131(do)006:404: rgyud dang rgyud gzhan ni legs sbyar dang /
NK131(do)006:407: legs sbyar ma yin pa ri khrod pa la sogs pa kla klo'i skad kyis te /
NK131(do)006:408: de lta bu la sogs pa thams cad mkhyen pas bstan pa'i chos rnams /
NK131(do)006:409: bsdud par byed pa pos bris so //
NK131(do)006:410: de bzhin du bod kyi yul du /
NK131(do)006:411: theg pa gsum bod kyi skad kyis bris te /
NK131(do)006:412: rgya nag tu rgya nag gi skad kyi so //
NK131(do)006:413: de bzhin du rgya nag chen po /
NK131(do)006:415: tsam pa ka spre'u'i yul gser zhes bya ba /
NK131(do)006:416: rug ma su ram ma'i yul gyi skad kyis so //
NK131(do)006:417: de ltar grong bye ba'i bdag nyid yul dgu bcu
NK131(do)006:418: rtsa drug rnams su dgu bcu rtsa drug gi skad
NK131(do)006:419: kyis so // de bzhin du dum bu bcu gnyis dang /
NK131(do)006:422: sa 'og rnams su sems can sna tshogs kyi skad
NK131(do)006:423: kyis bsdud par byed pa po dag gis theg pa
NK131(do)006:424: gsum bris te / nyan thos rnams kyis nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK131(do)006:425: rang sangs rgyas rnams kyis rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa dang /
NK131(do)006:426: byang sems rnams kyis theg pa chen po phar phyin dang /
NK131(do)006:427: theg pa chen po gsang sngags rgyu dang 'bras bu'i bdag nyid de /
NK131(do)006:428: bsdud par byed pa po sna tshogs kyis sems can rnams 'dul bar bya ba'i don du'o //
NK131(do)006:429: bsdud par byed pa sna tshogs kyis /
NK131(do)006:430: yul sna tshogs kyi skad kyis bris pa'i lung dang rig pa 'dis rnam par dpyad pas na /
NK131(do)006:431: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das thams cad mkhyen pa /
NK131(do)006:432: thams cad mkhyen pa'i skad kyis chos ston pa po yin gyis /
NK131(do)006:433: khyab 'jug dang drag po la sogs gzhan ni ma yin no //
NK131(do)006:434: ci ste khyab 'jug dang drag po la sogs pa rnams kyi nang na /
NK131(do)006:435: yon tan 'di dag yongs su rdzogs pa 'ga' zhig yod na /
NK131(do)006:436: de yang bdag cag gis rnam pa thams cad du phyag bya ba dang /
NK131(do)006:437: mchod pa dang bkur bar bya ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:438: zhes legs par gsungs pas so /
NK131(do)006:440: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK131(do)006:442: mya ngan las ma 'das kyi bar du /
NK131(do)006:443: lce rkanagyi rtsol ba las byung pa'i /
NK131(do)006:444: tha na yig 'bru gcig kyang ma gsungs so //
NK131(do)006:445: de'i rgyu mtshan dbugs 'byung rngubs mi mnga' zhing rnam par mi rtog pas so /
NK131(do)006:446: de ltar yin kyang sems can gyi bsam pa dang 'thun par /
NK131(do)006:447: skad mtha' yas pas theg pa ma lus pa thams cad /
NK131(do)006:448: sems can gyi bsam pa bzhin ston pa'i sgra 'byung ste /
NK131(do)006:449: nam mkhas ji srid khyab par gsung gi sgras khyab cing chos ston pa yin te /
NK131(do)006:450: bya rgod phung po'i ri la /
NK131(do)006:451: byams pa la rten nas dbyangs kyi dkyil 'khor yongs
NK131(do)006:452: su dag pa zhes bya ba'i chos ston pa'i tshe
NK131(do)006:453: / mo'u 'gal gyi bus gsung gi mtha' dpog par 'dod nas /
NK131(do)006:454: 'jig rten gyi khams 'od zer rgyal mtshan du phyin pa na /
NK131(do)006:455: de bzhin gshegs pa 'od zer rgyal mtshan gyis bka' stsal pa /
NK131(do)006:456: 'jig rten gyi khams gang ga'i klung dgu bcu /
NK131(do)006:457: rtsa dgu'i byed ma snyed nas khyod 'dir 'ongs so //
NK131(do)006:458: nam mkhas ji tsam khyab pa de tsam du /
NK131(do)006:459: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gis khyab bo //
NK131(do)006:461: gdul bya'i bsam pa dang 'thun par /
NK131(do)006:462: chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi stong ma lus par 'chad pa ni /
NK131(do)006:463: gsung gi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK131(do)006:464: phal po che'i byang sems chen po kun tu bzang po'i /
NK131(do)006:465: bzang por spyod pa'i smon lam las kyang lha yi skad dang klu dang gnod sbyin skad /
NK131(do)006:466: grul bum dag dang mi yi skad rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:467: 'gro ba kun gyi sgra skad ci tsam par /
NK131(do)006:468: thams cad skad du bdag gis chos bstan to //
NK131(do)006:470: rdzogs pa chen po la sogs pa'i rgyud kyi yi ge dang sngags dang sgra tshig kha gcig /
NK131(do)006:471: legs par sbyar ba la sogs pa'i /
NK131(do)006:472: rgya gar gyi sgra tshig yi ge dang ma mthun kyang skyon med de /
NK131(do)006:474: lus can kun gyi bya dang ni /
NK131(do)006:475: shing dang 'od zer thams cad dang /
NK131(do)006:476: nam mkha' las kyang chos kyi sgra /
NK131(do)006:477: rgyun mi 'chad pa thos par shog /
NK131(do)006:479: rang byung gi ye shes chos kyi sku /
NK131(do)006:480: chos nyid de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK131(do)006:481: gsung rdo rje longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku gzhom du med pa'i rang sgra yin pas /
NK131(do)006:482: sang kri ta'i yi ge la sogs dang 'gal ba'i skyon ni /
NK131(do)006:483: thams cad mkhyen pas kyang mi khel lo //
NK131(do)006:485: bstan bcos gang la yang ma grags par /
NK131(do)006:486: de bzhin gshegs pas brdas rtags nas gsungs pa yin te /
NK131(do)006:488: ko ta k+sha la sogs pa'i sgra /
NK131(do)006:489: de bzhin gshegs pa'i brdar gyur pa /
NK131(do)006:490: 'jig rten bstan bcos las ma grags /
NK131(do)006:492: rlung bcu po ming bcu'i brda'i sgo nas btags pa lta bu yin pas /
NK131(do)006:493: tshig la rten pa ni snying po med pa kho na'o //
NK131(do)006:494: zlos pa lta bu'i tshig kha cig kyang /
NK131(do)006:495: dus 'khor du thams cad mkhyen pa ye shes sku dang /
NK131(do)006:496: zhes pa rnams zlos pa gsungs pa lta bu ste /
NK131(do)006:497: khyab 'jug la sogs pa kha gcig gis /
NK131(do)006:498: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid du btags pa dang /
NK131(do)006:500: rnam shes smra ba'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK131(do)006:501: ye shes kyi sku gzugs can du dgos pa bsal ba'i phyir du thams cad mkhyen pa dang /
NK131(do)006:502: ye shes sku dang nyi mor byed pa dang /
NK131(do)006:503: pad ma 'dab ma rgyas pa'i spyan /
NK131(do)006:504: zhes pa'i sangs rgyas kyi ming zlos pa gsungs pa lta bu ste /
NK131(do)006:506: zlos pa yod pas thams cad du skyon yod pas ma khyab bo /
NK131(do)006:507: ming gi mngon brjod sogs kyang dri med 'od las /
NK131(do)006:509: e wam nyid ming ma yin te /
NK131(do)006:510: ngo bo gcig la ming du ma'o //
NK131(do)006:511: ming mang po nyid kyi phyir /
NK131(do)006:512: ming gcig kho na gtso ba ma yin te /
NK131(do)006:513: ming thams cad kyi dngos po gcig go bar bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:517: bud med gcig bu gtso bo'i ming ma yin te /
NK131(do)006:518: thams cad kyis kyang nu ma dang skrar ldan pa'i dngos po go bar byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:520: gza' sgra gcan la khyab 'jug dang /
NK131(do)006:521: lha khyab 'jug la skos rje brang dkar du btags pa la 'gal ba ci yang med la /
NK131(do)006:522: lha klu 'byung po thams cad re re la yang /
NK131(do)006:523: ming gi rnam grangs mang por snang zhing /
NK131(do)006:524: kha cig yul so so'i 'dod rgyal gyi sgras btags pa yin te /
NK131(do)006:525: rgyu skar nyer brgyad po la bstan bcos kyi skad dang /
NK131(do)006:526: yul so so bas btags pa'i ming gi rnam grangs mang /
NK131(do)006:527: dbang phyug chen po gcig po la yang dbang phyug dang /
NK131(do)006:533: drag po chen po la sogs ming mang bas /
NK131(do)006:534: gcig la zhen pa ni 'khrul tshabs che zhing /
NK131(do)006:535: lar yang 'di 'dra ba'i ming tshig la rten pa ni snying po med pa kho na'o //
NK131(do)006:536: de ltar na don la ston cing tshig la mi rton pa ni shes ldan rnams kyis bsgrub bya'o //
NK131(do)006:537: de la legs sbyar gyi skad kyi skabs 'ga' zhig tu gsungs pa ni dgongs pa can te /
NK131(do)006:538: 'di ltar lha rnams kyi yul du ni /
NK131(do)006:539: lha rnams yongs su smin par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK131(do)006:540: 'phags pa'i yul ma ga tar ni /
NK131(do)006:541: sgra smra ba'i drang srong phyir rol pa rnams yod pas /
NK131(do)006:542: de rnams kyis legs sbyar gyis smra zhing /
NK131(do)006:543: mkhas pa'i nga rgyal dang ldan pa rnams 'dul bar bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK131(do)006:544: gzhan yang nang pa'i byis pa kha gcig kyang /
NK131(do)006:545: de rnams kyis smra ba'i rjes su 'brengs nas /
NK131(do)006:546: bdag cag gi ston pa sangs rgyas sras bcas kyis
NK131(do)006:547: kyang legs sbyar gyis smra bar rigs so snyam du
NK131(do)006:548: rtogs pa rnams la gsungs pa'o //
NK131(do)006:549: de ltar sangs rgyas thams cad kyis kyang yul so so'i sems can sna tshogs pa la /
NK131(do)006:550: so so'i skad kyis bstan nas /
NK131(do)006:551: bsdud pa po rnams kyis kyang yul so so'i skad dang /
NK131(do)006:554: b+hi ma la mi tra la sogs pas kyang /
NK131(do)006:555: bod la sogs pa yul so so'i brda dang skad dang /
NK131(do)006:557: ming tshig gi yi ge dang bstun nas bsgyur zhing bshad pas /
NK131(do)006:558: nyi tse ba'i ming tshig yi ge la rten pa'i phyogs lhung thams cad /
NK131(do)006:559: phyogs med ris med kyi mkhas pa rnams kyis dor nas /
NK131(do)006:560: don la ston par byang chub sems dpa'i 'grel pa skor gsum la sogs pa'i //
NK131(do)006:561: gsung rab thams cad du dgongs pa gcig dang /
NK131(do)006:562: dbyangs gcig gis gsungs pa rnams gzigs su gsol /
NK131(do)006:563: yang 'di skad du dkyil 'khor gyi lha la khu le lag dgu dang /
NK131(do)006:566: nag shod kyi sku la gsang pa dang //
NK131(do)006:567: tsha ba sgang gi rdo rje g.yu sgron ma dang //
NK131(do)006:568: bla ba lam gyi dre'u sna ma dang /
NK131(do)006:569: mon yul gyi stun ting nag mo la sogs pa bod 'dre /
NK131(do)006:572: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor la lha 'dre rnams bsgrigs pas log pa yin na /
NK131(do)006:573: dus 'khor la sogs pa'i bla med kyi rgyud mang po dang /
NK131(do)006:575: chos dbyings gsung dbang gnod sbyin shing rta /
NK131(do)006:576: sku'i rgyud rdo rje gtsug tor /
NK131(do)006:578: srid pa gsum gyi lha 'dre mang po bkod par bshad cing /
NK131(do)006:580: phyi yi dkyil 'khor phyi rol du //
NK131(do)006:581: gling bzhi po yang bri bar bya //
NK131(do)006:582: 'dzam bu'i gling du tshangs pa bri //
NK131(do)006:583: byang phyogs su ni dbang phyug che //
NK131(do)006:584: shar dang nub kyi gling du ni //
NK131(do)006:585: brgya byin gtogs 'dod thams cad kyang //
NK131(do)006:586: 'khor dang bcas pa bri bar bya //
NK131(do)006:587: gzhan dag kyang ni de bzhin te //
NK131(do)006:588: lha min dri za nam mkha' lding //
NK131(do)006:589: gnod sbyin srin po lto 'phye che //
NK131(do)006:591: klu dang klu yi rigs rnams dang //
NK131(do)006:592: rgyal po bzhi rnams bri bar bya //
NK131(do)006:593: gza' dang skar ma rgyu skar dang //
NK131(do)006:594: khro bo ma rungs 'tshe ba yi //
NK131(do)006:595: bgegs dang byi na ya ka rnams //
NK131(do)006:596: sems can kun la phan byed pa'i //
NK131(do)006:597: drang srong skal pa chen po rnams //
NK131(do)006:598: mkha' 'gro ma dang bud med bri //
NK131(do)006:599: de bzhin sring mo rnal 'byor ma //
NK131(do)006:600: 'byung po bzhi yi lha chen po //
NK131(do)006:601: khyim dang ri la gnas pa dang //
NK131(do)006:602: shing dang kun dag'i nags la sogs //
NK131(do)006:603: dur khrod grong khyer gnas pa rnams //
NK131(do)006:604: ming ngam barda'am yang na ni //
NK131(do)006:605: thig le rnams kyang bri bar bya /
NK131(do)006:607: thag zangs ris ni lha min dang //
NK131(do)006:608: dri za zur phud lnga pa dang //
NK131(do)006:609: nam mkha' lding gser mig can dang /
NK131(do)006:611: srin po lang ka mgrin bcu dang /
NK131(do)006:612: lto 'phye'i rgyal po sa bdag sngon po dang /
NK131(do)006:620: spyi bo tshugs thur lta sogs drug dang /
NK131(do)006:621: kha cig gis yi dwags phyi nang sgo khur can rnams la bzhed pa dang /
NK131(do)006:622: 'byung po'i 'khor la gdon chen bco lnga dang /
NK131(do)006:623: khro bo ma rungs 'tshe ba ni dmyal bsrungs rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:624: bud med ni 'bru 'grel rgan mo sogs nas /
NK131(do)006:625: kha rag khyung btsun rdo rje yum gcig ma /
NK131(do)006:626: sha med gangs dkar rdo rje spyan gcig ma sogs bdun /
NK131(do)006:627: bod kyi yul na gnas pa bkod pa dang /
NK131(do)006:629: lha 'dre mtha' las 'das pa gcig bsgrigs par 'dug pa dang /
NK131(do)006:630: sbyong rgyud kyi 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i skabs su yang /
NK131(do)006:631: de yi phyi rol dmyal kun dang /
NK131(do)006:632: 'dod chags la sogs byol song bri /
NK131(do)006:635: dug gsum gyi mtshan ma rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:636: phyi rol gyi phyogs 'tshams rnams su /
NK131(do)006:637: rigs drug gi 'gro ba pa rnams kyang bkod par gsungs shing /
NK131(do)006:639: 'jig rten gyi 'byung po mang po dang /
NK131(do)006:640: dur khrod brgyad du dmyal bsrungs kyi gshin rje rnams kyang bkod par bshad pas /
NK131(do)006:642: de dag gi cho ga rnams kyang log par 'gyur ram /
NK131(do)006:643: des na srid pa gsum gyi 'byung po /
NK131(do)006:646: gnod sbyin la sogs pa'i sde brgyad dang /
NK131(do)006:647: dbang phyug chen po chen po la sogs pa'i 'jig rten gyi dregs pa can gyi lha 'dre rnams /
NK131(do)006:648: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor du bzhag nas gtor ma byin te las la bskul /
NK131(do)006:649: bstan pa bsrungs par bka' bsgo ba rnams byed pa la skyon du blta na ni /
NK131(do)006:650: sngags gsar snying gnyis kyi rgyud sde mtha' dag gcig dor ba min pa /
NK131(do)006:651: de dag ma bshad pa'i dkyil 'khor srid pa tsam mo /
NK131(do)006:652: gal te bod 'dre yin pas dkyil 'khor la bkod du mi rung na ni /
NK131(do)006:653: rgya 'dre yang bkod du mi rung dgos te /
NK131(do)006:654: srid gsum khyab pa'i lha 'dre la rgya bod khyad par med pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:656: thams cad bla ma'i gnas la sogs //
NK131(do)006:657: mkha' 'gro mas ni thams cad khyab /
NK131(do)006:660: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten man chad dang /
NK131(do)006:661: khyad par 'dzam bu gling gi rgya gar rgya nag /
NK131(do)006:666: bod la sogs pa thams cad du mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK131(do)006:669: bde mchog gi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i tshe na /
NK131(do)006:670: he ma la yar kha ba'i ri ti ser gnas pa'i /
NK131(do)006:671: dpa' bo mig mi bzang dang /
NK131(do)006:672: mkha' 'gro ma bya gdong ma la sogs kyang sgom pa dang /
NK131(do)006:673: bkod du mi rung dgos te /
NK131(do)006:674: bod du gnas pa'i phyir ro /
NK131(do)006:675: bod 'dre bkod du mi rung na /
NK131(do)006:683: rgya gar gyi ri khyim dang /
NK131(do)006:684: grong la gnas pa'i lha 'dre rnams min pa /
NK131(do)006:685: bod kyi ri khyim la gnas pa rnams ni /
NK131(do)006:686: mi rung pa'i bsgrub byed bstan dgos so //
NK131(do)006:687: gzhan yang bod kyi tshe ring ma dpon g.yog dang /
NK131(do)006:688: bstan ma bcu gnyis la sogs pa thams cad bod du gnas kyang /
NK131(do)006:689: rgya gar dang u rgyan la sogs pa thams cad du khyab par rgyu zhing /
NK131(do)006:690: phan tshun du tshogs 'khor la bsgrod pa la sogs mang du bshad pa /
NK131(do)006:691: rgya gar gyi lha 'dre dkyil 'khor la sgrig tu rung zhing /
NK131(do)006:692: bod 'dre mi rung pa'i shes byed ci yang med do /
NK131(do)006:693: de yang 'jig rten gyi lha 'dre rnams /
NK131(do)006:694: sngon sangs rgyas kyis dam la bzhag nas /
NK131(do)006:695: bsrung mar khas blangs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:696: kha cig ni pad+ma 'byung ga nas la sogs pas dam la btags te /
NK131(do)006:697: srog gi snying po phul nas dam tshig byin /
NK131(do)006:698: dbang bskur bas spangs rtogs kyi yon tan mang po rdzogs kyang /
NK131(do)006:699: cha lugs de nyid kyis bstan pa bsrung par mdzad cing /
NK131(do)006:700: dkyil 'khor la bzhag nas bsrung mar bka' bsgos gnyer gtad de /
NK131(do)006:701: las bsgrub cing 'khor du gnas pa la skyon med /
NK131(do)006:702: spyir yang gdul bya'i snang ba la /
NK131(do)006:703: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo 'jig rten las 'das pa dang /
NK131(do)006:704: 'khor 'jig rten pa'i lha 'dre'i cha lugs su snang ba'i tshul ston pa la skyon du blta na /
NK131(do)006:705: rgyud dang bsgrub dkyil mtha' yas pa gcig dor dgos par 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)006:706: gzhan yang bod 'dre dkyil 'khor du bzhag pa la skyon du byed na /
NK131(do)006:707: rgyud sde rnams nas rgya bod la sogs yul so so'i mi ma yin dang /
NK131(do)006:708: 'jig rten pa'i lha 'dre rnams kyi ming /
NK131(do)006:710: s+w+aa h+aa la sogs pa'i bar du ltems nas byin gyis brlabs te /
NK131(do)006:711: 'jig rten gyi dngos grub gter ba sogs bshad pa rnams la'ang /
NK131(do)006:712: bod kyi yul du gnas pa'i lha 'dre rnams kyi ming spel nas /
NK131(do)006:713: las sgrub pa sogs kyang mi 'thad dam /
NK131(do)006:715: dus 'khor rgyud 'grel la sogs pa rnams kyang log par 'gyur ram /
NK131(do)006:716: des na gdul bya'i snang ba la /
NK131(do)006:717: gdul byed kyi lha tshogs kyang /
NK131(do)006:719: ming dang gzugs cha lugs 'thun par bstan pa rnams la 'gal bar gzung ba ni /
NK131(do)006:720: rtol med kyi tshig yang dag pa'o //
NK131(do)006:721: sangs rgyas kyi gzugs sku sgyu 'phrul rol pa'i rnam
NK131(do)006:722: 'phrul mig 'phrul lta bu gang la gang 'dul du
NK131(do)006:723: bstan pa la bkur pa btab pa kho na'o //
NK131(do)006:725: gsang sngags bstan pa'i snod ma yin pas /
NK131(do)006:727: rang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi mgo bregs shing /
NK131(do)006:728: gsang ba bstan pa gzhan la sgrogs pas /
NK131(do)006:729: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi yang mgo bregs nas /
NK131(do)006:730: dpal chen po'i sku la brgyan zer ba dang /
NK131(do)006:731: sangs rgyas rigs lnga bsgyel ba'i gdan la khram kha
NK131(do)006:732: stong gi dbang mo la sogs pa ma mo lngas
NK131(do)006:733: rdzis pa dang / rta mgrin pad ma dbang chen gyi zhabs brgyad kyis /
NK131(do)006:734: ye shes kyi khro bo chen po brgyad kyi snying khar bardzisa te khog pa bral nas /
NK131(do)006:735: sgal tshigs 'joms par bsgom pa la sogs bskyed rim gyi cho ga log pa mtha' yas pa 'dug /
NK131(do)006:737: 'di rnams phal cher rgyud 'dir bshad kyi nges pa khungs dang bcas pa yang mi snang bas /
NK131(do)006:738: snying ma'i rgyud gzhung khungs ma rnams nas bshad pa'i nges pa med la /
NK131(do)006:740: bskyed rims nor bar ji ltar 'gyur te /
NK131(do)006:741: rgyud thams cad rdo rje'i tshig gis sbas nas dgongs pa can du gasungasapa dang /
NK131(do)006:742: mdo bstan bcos phal cher ldem por dgongs te gsungs pa rnams la /
NK131(do)006:743: sgra ji bzhin par bzung nas log par bsgrubs na /
NK131(do)006:745: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga bsreg cing /
NK131(do)006:746: spyan la sogs pa yang bsreg bya ste /
NK131(do)006:749: sangs rgyas lha mo bcu bsad nas /
NK131(do)006:752: khyod kyi srog chags bsad par gyis /
NK131(do)006:753: ma byin pa yang khyod kyis long /
NK131(do)006:754: rdzun gyi tshig kyang smra bar gyis /
NK131(do)006:755: pha rol bud med brten par gyis /
NK131(do)006:758: rdo rje sems dpa' zhe sdang che //
NK131(do)006:759: thub par rnam par snang mdzad rmongs //
NK131(do)006:761: ser sna rdo rje snang byed do //
NK131(do)006:762: don yod skyon mi thams cad byed //
NK131(do)006:763: 'dren pa lnga ni skyon ldan no //
NK131(do)006:764: zhes sangs rgyas rigs lnga ni /
NK131(do)006:765: nyon mongs pa dug lnga'i skyon dang ldan par bshad pa dang //
NK131(do)006:766: sangs rgyas dngos grub 'dod pa yis //
NK131(do)006:767: stobs kyi sangs rgyas phur bus gdab /
NK131(do)006:769: gal te dngos grub mi ster na //
NK131(do)006:770: rdo rje sems dpa' bsad par bya /
NK131(do)006:772: phyag rgya chen po thig le'i rgyud las //
NK131(do)006:773: srog gcod pa yi mchod sbyin ni //
NK131(do)006:776: srog gcod pa yi mchod sbyin gyis //
NK131(do)006:777: mchog gi mchog ni yang dag rnyed /
NK131(do)006:779: de nyid las mthar phyag rgya chen po'i rang bzhin bshad pa thos nas /
NK131(do)006:780: 'khor mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis bskor ba dang phyag byas te /
NK131(do)006:781: bcom ldan 'das la khrag dron mos mchod /
NK131(do)006:784: srog gcod pa yi sems can gang //
NK131(do)006:785: rdzun du smra la dga' ba dang //
NK131(do)006:786: gzhan gyis nor la chags pa dang //
NK131(do)006:787: rtag tu 'dod pa spyod pa gang /
NK131(do)006:788: gshang lci zas su za ba ste //
NK131(do)006:789: de dag bsgrub pa'i snod du 'gyur /
NK131(do)006:791: ma dang sring mo bu mo la //
NK131(do)006:792: 'dod pa bas ni mnyes byas na //
NK131(do)006:793: theg chen mchog gi chos nyid kyi //
NK131(do)006:794: dngos grub rgya chen des thob bo /
NK131(do)006:796: de bzhin gshegs pa'i tshogs bsad na //
NK131(do)006:797: dngos grub rab mchog thob par 'gyur //
NK131(do)006:798: de bzhin gshegs dang bdag gi lus //
NK131(do)006:799: bla ma gshang dang lci bas mchod /
NK131(do)006:801: 'di ni gsungs ma thag tu yang /
NK131(do)006:802: sangs rgyas grags pa chen po kun //
NK131(do)006:803: brgyal zhing rab tu 'jigs gyur nas //
NK131(do)006:804: rdo rje'i sku ni rjes su dran //
NK131(do)006:805: sngags rnams kyis ni sbyor ba dang //
NK131(do)006:806: rdo rjes bskrad pa'i las rnams la //
NK131(do)006:807: sangs rgyas nyid ni gsung dag kyang //
NK131(do)006:808: tshul bzhin byas na sprod par 'gyur /
NK131(do)006:810: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK131(do)006:811: skye bo gdug pa gzhan dag kyang //
NK131(do)006:812: sngags 'dis skrag par byas nas ni //
NK131(do)006:816: nges par rdo rje'i rigs dag la ni srog gcod
NK131(do)006:817: bya ste ral gri la yang bden pa min pa'i
NK131(do)006:818: tshig / rin chen rigs la gzhan nor 'phrog bya
NK131(do)006:819: mchog gi pad+ma'i rigs nyid la yang gzhan gyi bud
NK131(do)006:820: tshig / med 'phrog / ces sogs shin tu mang ba dag /
NK131(do)006:821: rgyud rnams su rdo rje'i tshig gis sbas te bstan pa rnams dang //
NK131(do)006:822: mdo rnams su yang pha dang ma gnyis bsad bya zhing /
NK131(do)006:823: rgyal po yul 'khor bcas bcom na //
NK131(do)006:824: mi de dag par 'gyur ba yin //
NK131(do)006:825: zhes pa la sogs shin tu mang bas //
NK131(do)006:826: tshig de dag 'byung pa'i rgyud gzhung rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:827: de dag nas bshad pa'i bskyed rdzogs kyi cho ga rnams log par 'gyur ram /
NK131(do)006:829: so skye la 'di ltar snang ba'i ri ra ba dang /
NK131(do)006:831: las kyi 'khrul snang 'di thams cad chos nyid chos dbyings /
NK131(do)006:833: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes mthar thug pa de nyid /
NK131(do)006:834: 'di ltar snang ba yin zer ba la sogs pa lta ba'i nor sa dang /
NK131(do)006:837: spyir rdzogs pa chen po la yang sde gsum sko
NK131(do)006:838: bzhi la sogs pa'i rnam grangs mtha' yas pa gcig
NK131(do)006:839: yod pa las / gsang ba man ngag gi sde /
NK131(do)006:840: yang gsang bla na med pa'i skor /
NK131(do)006:843: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor sogs rnams nas ni /
NK131(do)006:844: chos skad 'di lta bur ri bong rwa dang mtshungs shing /
NK131(do)006:845: gzhi lta ba ka dag dang lhun grub kyis gshis kyi gnas lugs gtan la dbab /
NK131(do)006:846: lam sgom pa khregs chod dang thod rgal gyis nyams su blangs pas /
NK131(do)006:847: ma dag pa snodabacuda phung khams skye mched thams cad dag nas /
NK131(do)006:848: dngas ma ye shes kyi sku'i rang bzhin /
NK131(do)006:849: 'bras bu chos sku dang gzugs sku gnyis /
NK131(do)006:851: don gnyis lhun grub kyi mdzad pa mthar phyin pa sogs shin tu mang yang /
NK131(do)006:852: gsang ba bas kyang gsang chen gyi man ngag yin phyir /
NK131(do)006:853: gsang sgrogs su 'gro bas zhib du ma spros so //
NK131(do)006:854: phyi sems sde snang ba sems su ston pa'i skor rnams su /
NK131(do)006:855: gal te de ltar yod na yang nor pa yin pa'i khyab pa med de /
NK131(do)006:856: de lta bu byung pas lta ba nor na /
NK131(do)006:857: rgya bod kyi phyag chen pa mang po dang /
NK131(do)006:860: zhi byed pa sogs thams cad kyis 'di ltar bzhed cing /
NK131(do)006:861: chos rje yang dgon pas kyang /
NK131(do)006:862: 'di ka ltar snang ba 'di nyid so ma nyams /
NK131(do)006:864: chos nyid chos kyi sku'i rol pa /
NK131(do)006:865: ye shes kyi snang ba ces dang /
NK131(do)006:866: 'khrul lugs phyag rgya chen po zhes gsungs shing /
NK131(do)006:867: 'khrul lugs phyag rgya chen po 'di nyid rtogs pas /
NK131(do)006:869: sangs rgyas la nyin khugs byas /
NK131(do)006:870: shes sogs mang du gsungs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:871: sa skya pa'i 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi khrid dang /
NK131(do)006:873: 'gro ba'i bla ma gong ma rnams kyis /
NK131(do)006:874: phyi snang ba sna tshogs dmigs pa dang bcas pa'i
NK131(do)006:875: stong gzugs phyag rgya chen po sogs mang du gsungs
NK131(do)006:876: pa dang / gzhan yang sems can gyi las snang sna tshogs /
NK131(do)006:877: stong gzugs phyag rgya chen po /
NK131(do)006:879: der ma zad rgyud du yang 'di nyid 'khor ba zhes bya ste /
NK131(do)006:881: 'khor ba spangs nas gzhan du ni /
NK131(do)006:883: 'khor ba gzugs dang sgra la sogs /
NK131(do)006:884: 'khor ba tshor ba la sogs pa /
NK131(do)006:885: 'khor ba dbang po rnam nyid de /
NK131(do)006:886: 'khor ba zhe sdang la sogs pa /
NK131(do)006:890: chos kyi dbyings las ma gtogs pa'i /
NK131(do)006:891: 'di ltar chos yod ma yin te /
NK131(do)006:894: gang ga la sogs chu klung sna tshogs pa /
NK131(do)006:895: ba tsha can gyi rgya mtshor ro gcig ltar /
NK131(do)006:898: chos kyi dbyings su ro gcig shes par byos /
NK131(do)006:900: gzhan yang sems snang gcig bu 'di nyid /
NK131(do)006:901: rigs drug gi sems can rnams la 'khrul pa'i snang bas /
NK131(do)006:902: so so'i las snang sna tshogs su mthong /
NK131(do)006:903: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi nyams kyi snang bas sgyu ma'i snang ba lta bur gzigs /
NK131(do)006:904: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis dag pa
NK131(do)006:905: ye shes kyi snang ba 'ba' zhig tu gzigs par
NK131(do)006:906: bshad cing / thams cad chos kyi dbyings la ma 'das par bshad pas /
NK131(do)006:907: bshad sgrub kyi rgyud pa de rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:908: gzhung dang gdams pa de rnams kyi lugs kyi lta ba yang nor par mdzad pa ni /
NK131(do)006:911: sems glo ba'i nang nas gnas shing /
NK131(do)006:912: rig pa snying dang klad pa'i nang na /
NK131(do)006:914: spyan phul thag tsam gyi lha'i gzugs su gnas par 'dod pa la sogs pa gzhi'i nor pa yin /
NK131(do)006:918: sgos rdo rje theg pa'i rten /
NK131(do)006:919: dal 'byor gyi lus skyon med mtshan nyid dang ldan pa thob pa thams cad la /
NK131(do)006:920: dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs /
NK131(do)006:921: gnyug ma sems kyi rang gdangs /
NK131(do)006:923: lhan cig skyes pa'i bde ba chen po de nyid /
NK131(do)006:924: gdod ma nas rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs kyi rang bzhin lus la gnas par 'dod pa de /
NK131(do)006:928: bde kye la sogs pa'i rgyud sde nas bshad pa'i /
NK131(do)006:929: gnyug ma'i lha sngags thams cad dang /
NK131(do)006:931: gdod ma nas rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i lus kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK131(do)006:933: rtsa thig rlung gsum lha'i rang bzhin can du /
NK131(do)006:934: gdod ma nas grub par bshad pa thams cad dang brtag gnyis las /
NK131(do)006:935: rtog pa thams cad rnam par spangs /
NK131(do)006:936: lus la ye shes chen po gnas /
NK131(do)006:937: dngos pa kun la khyab pa po /
NK131(do)006:938: lus la gnas kyang lus skyes min /
NK131(do)006:941: lus las ma gtogs gang zhig khyab byed thar pa
NK131(do)006:942: ster ba'i sangs rgyas dag ni 'ga' yang yod pa
NK131(do)006:943: min / sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas yin te
NK131(do)006:944: sangs rgyas chen po gzhan 'dir 'jig rten khams na
NK131(do)006:945: min / yod pa min / zhes dang /
NK131(do)006:947: 'dir sems can thams cad kyi snying gi nang du gnas pa ni ye shes so //
NK131(do)006:948: de yang gzhom du med pa'i sgra de n+aa da'i mtshan nyid do //
NK131(do)006:951: snying kha'i dbus gyur pad+ma ni /
NK131(do)006:952: 'dab ma brgyad ni lte bar bcas /
NK131(do)006:953: de yi dbus su gyur pa'i rtsa /
NK131(do)006:954: mar me lta bu'i gzugs can de /
NK131(do)006:955: chu shing me tog lta bu'i dbyibs /
NK131(do)006:956: kha ni thur du bltas nas kyang /
NK131(do)006:957: de yi dbus na dpa' bo ni /
NK131(do)006:958: nyungs kar sbom pa'i tshad tsam ste /
NK131(do)006:959: h+aum gi sa bon mi bshigs pa /
NK131(do)006:960: kha ba lta bur 'dzag pa yin /
NK131(do)006:961: b+ha pan ta zhes bshad pa ste /
NK131(do)006:962: lus can rnams kyi snying dga' byed /
NK131(do)006:964: shin tu mdzes pa'i rtsa la ni /
NK131(do)006:965: byung ba rdul bral zhes byar grags /
NK131(do)006:966: dri med shel dang mtshungs pa'i 'od /
NK131(do)006:967: byang chub sems ni 'od gsal ba /
NK131(do)006:968: ye shes lnga yi ngo bo nyid //
NK131(do)006:969: nyungs kar sbom pa'i tshad tsam bdag /
NK131(do)006:970: de yi dbus na gnas pa'i lha //
NK131(do)006:971: mi gsal gsal ba'i rang bzhin can //
NK131(do)006:972: cha med mchog tu phra ba ste //
NK131(do)006:973: thig le'i gzugs can yid kyi dngos //
NK131(do)006:974: gzi brjid chen po'i 'od dang ldan //
NK131(do)006:975: rtag tu snying gi dbus na gnas /
NK131(do)006:977: rgyu rnams kun gyi rtsa ba ste /
NK131(do)006:978: gru gsum shin tu yangs pa'i gzugs //
NK131(do)006:979: sems can kun gyi thun mong ba //
NK131(do)006:980: lha min lhar bcas tshangs sogs kyi //
NK131(do)006:981: gnas su de ni gyur pa ste //
NK131(do)006:982: kun rdzob tshul du rang bzhin gyis //
NK131(do)006:983: de nyid shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK131(do)006:984: de nyid yul las 'das pa ste //
NK131(do)006:985: srog chags kun gyi snying la gnas /
NK131(do)006:988: sems can kun gyi snying la ni /
NK131(do)006:989: thugs kyi pad+ma snying po bzhugs /
NK131(do)006:990: de nyid snying po gsum ldan pa /
NK131(do)006:991: bde gshegs snying po 'jug pa nyid /
NK131(do)006:993: rgyud sde rnams las shin tu mang zhing /
NK131(do)006:994: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'i mdor yang /
NK131(do)006:995: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyan dang ldan pa /
NK131(do)006:996: sems can thams cad kyi lus kyi nang na /
NK131(do)006:997: ji bzhin mi g.yo bar bzhugs so /
NK131(do)006:998: shes sogs mdo rnams su yang mang zhing /
NK131(do)006:1000: sangs rgyas pad nang sbra rtsi sbrang ma la /
NK131(do)006:1001: sbun pa snying po mi gtsang nang na gser /
NK131(do)006:1002: sa la gter dang myug sogs 'bras chu dang /
NK131(do)006:1003: gos hrul nang na rgyal ba'i sku dang ni /
NK131(do)006:1004: bud med ngan pa'i lto na mi bdag dang /
NK131(do)006:1005: sa nang rin chen gzugs yod ji lta bar /
NK131(do)006:1006: blo bur nyon mongs dri mas bsgribs pa yis /
NK131(do)006:1007: sems can rnams la de bzhin khams 'di gnas /
NK131(do)006:1009: dgas po bka' rgyud pa'i man ngag kun du yang /
NK131(do)006:1010: lta stangs kyis rig pa bcun pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK131(do)006:1011: rtogs pa'i gnad rlung la yod /
NK131(do)006:1012: rlung gi gnad rtsa la yod /
NK131(do)006:1013: rtsa'i gnad mig la yod de /
NK131(do)006:1014: mig btsum na glo srol gnyis kyi bar du subs nas 'gro /
NK131(do)006:1015: mig phye tsa na glo srol gnyis kyi bar du snying yod pa yang rjen 'gro la /
NK131(do)006:1016: rtsa b+ha pan ta yang gyen la blta zhing kha bye nas /
NK131(do)006:1017: shes pa gsal la rtog pa med pa'i gnyug ma gcig 'ong ba yin te /
NK131(do)006:1018: des na lta stangs gal che gsungs pa'i don yang /
NK131(do)006:1019: gnad 'di lta bu yod pa'i don gyis gsungs pas na /
NK131(do)006:1020: gzhi la de ltar mi gnas par 'dod pa rnams kyis ni /
NK131(do)006:1022: bla med rdo rje theg pa'i don la rgyab kyis phyogs pa'i rtags yin no //
NK131(do)006:1024: bskal pa gsum dang mi tshe bdun /
NK131(do)006:1025: zla drug lo gcig zla drug bcu /
NK131(do)006:1026: rtsol bar byed pa'i theg pa can /
NK131(do)006:1027: byar med ngo bo 'di bstan pas /
NK131(do)006:1028: mi rtsol lhun grub bde la gnas /
NK131(do)006:1029: shes mdo sngags gnyis ka'i lam thams cad khyad du bsad nas /
NK131(do)006:1030: rdzogs pa chen po thob pa tsam gyis 'tshang rgya zer ba dang /
NK131(do)006:1033: spyir chos thams cad kyi rang gzhung la che ba'i yon tan brjod pa lugs yin zhing /
NK131(do)006:1035: rnal 'byor pa yang blo khyad kyis /
NK131(do)006:1036: gong ma gong ma rnams kyis gnod /
NK131(do)006:1037: ces gsungs shing dam pa sangs rgyas kyis zhi byed phyi mar yang /
NK131(do)006:1039: sngags kyi lam thams cad kyi gong ma phyag chen nam /
NK131(do)006:1040: rdzogs pa chen po yin par bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1041: rje btsun chen po ti lo pas /
NK131(do)006:1042: blo yi chos kyis blo 'das don mi mthong /
NK131(do)006:1043: byas pa'i chos kyis byar med don mi rtogs /
NK131(do)006:1044: blo 'das byar med don 'di thob 'dod na /
NK131(do)006:1045: rang sems rtsad chod rig pa gcer bur zhog /
NK131(do)006:1046: rtog pa dri ma'i chu de dngas su chug /
NK131(do)006:1047: snang ba dgag sgrub ma byed rang sar zhog /
NK131(do)006:1048: spangs blang med na phyag rgya chen por grol /
NK131(do)006:1050: 'dul ba'i sde snod la sogs chos rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:1051: rang rang gzhung dang grub pa'i mtha' yis ni /
NK131(do)006:1052: 'od gsal phyag rgya chen po mthong mi 'gyur /
NK131(do)006:1053: zhes 'dod byung pas 'od gsal ma mthong bsgribs /
NK131(do)006:1054: rtog pa'i bsrung sdoms dam tshig don la nyams /
NK131(do)006:1057: phyag rgya chen po gcig chod la /
NK131(do)006:1058: sa lam rtsi ba rmongs pa 'khrul /
NK131(do)006:1059: zhes gsungs pa rnams kyis kyang mdo sngags kyi lam thams cad khyad du bsad par 'gyur ram /
NK131(do)006:1060: thos pa tsam gyis grol ba dang 'tshang rgya ba 'gog na /
NK131(do)006:1063: chos tshig re thos pa tsam gyis bdag med pa rtogs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1064: mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1066: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK131(do)006:1067: rgyud la skyes pa la sogs pa shin tu mang
NK131(do)006:1069: bram ze chen po yab sras /
NK131(do)006:1071: rgyal bu sa ka ra sogs mang po dang /
NK131(do)006:1072: bod du yang dpal phag mo grub pa /
NK131(do)006:1075: so chung pa la sogs gcig char ba'i gang zag mang po /
NK131(do)006:1076: gdams pa tshig re thos pa tsam gyis rtogs grol dus gcig du gyur pa kun gyis /
NK131(do)006:1077: mdo sngags kyi lam khyad du bsad nas /
NK131(do)006:1078: lam log pa'i grub thob tu 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)006:1080: yi ge dang 'khor lo btags pas skye ba 'di'i bar do tshun chad du grol zer ba dang /
NK131(do)006:1083: yi ge dang 'khor lo gzugs sngags btags pas grol ba thob pa rnams 'gog na /
NK131(do)006:1085: mdo sngags phal cher las de ltarabashada pas /
NK131(do)006:1086: de dag thams cad dgag par bya dgos te /
NK131(do)006:1089: glegs bam sor ni bcu gnyis pa //
NK131(do)006:1090: gro gar dam tshig can gyis bri //
NK131(do)006:1091: bris sku dang ni glegs bam dag /
NK131(do)006:1092: gal te skal med mthong ba na //
NK131(do)006:1093: skye ba 'dir ni dngos grub med /
NK131(do)006:1095: glegs bam lam gyi spyod yul du /
NK131(do)006:1096: skra dang mchan khung nyid du sba /
NK131(do)006:1100: de bzhin gshegs pas ngan song sbyong ba'i gzi brjid kyi rgyal po'i gsang ba'i snying po 'di /
NK131(do)006:1101: rigs kyi bu'am rigs kyi bu mo gang yang rung bas /
NK131(do)006:1102: ming tsam bde mchog rtsa rgyud kyi phan yon dang /
NK131(do)006:1103: gsang 'dus rgyud phyi ma nas kyang /
NK131(do)006:1107: bris nas kyang mgo bo'i gtsug gam /
NK131(do)006:1108: dpung pa'am mgul du btags na /
NK131(do)006:1109: tshe 'di nyid la dus ma yin pa'i 'chi ba brgyad dam /
NK131(do)006:1110: dus ma yin par 'chi ba dang 'brel ba'i rmi lam gyi rnam pa'am /
NK131(do)006:1111: ngan song dang 'brel ba'i mtshan ma de dag rmi lam du yang mi 'byung ngo /
NK131(do)006:1113: ngan 'gro thams cad sbyong ba'i gatsugatora rnam rgyal las /
NK131(do)006:1117: de las gzhan pa gang la las /
NK131(do)006:1118: gzungs 'di bris te rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mor btags pa mthong ngam /
NK131(do)006:1119: de dang nye bar gnas par gyur ram /
NK131(do)006:1120: tha na de'i grib mas phog gam /
NK131(do)006:1121: de'i rdul rlung gis khyer ba phog na yang /
NK131(do)006:1123: sems can de dag la sdig pa thams cad dang /
NK131(do)006:1124: ngan 'gror 'gro ba'i 'jigs pa thams cad mi 'byung ngo /
NK131(do)006:1129: lha ma yin gyi rigs thams cad du mi skye bar rigs par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:1130: lha'i dbang po sems can de dag ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis lung bstan cing /
NK131(do)006:1131: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub las phyir mi ldog par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:1133: so sor 'brang ba'i mdo las bram ze chen po
NK131(do)006:1134: gang la la zhig gis rig sngags kyi rgyal mo
NK131(do)006:1135: chen mo / so sor 'brang ba 'di cho ga bzhin du bris te /
NK131(do)006:1136: lag pa'am mgul du btags na /
NK131(do)006:1137: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis byin gyis brlab par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:1138: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi skur rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:1139: rdo rje'i lus yin par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:1140: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ring bsrel gyi snying po can yin par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:1141: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyan yin par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:1142: rdo rje'i lus su rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:1143: de 'bar ba'i 'od 'phro ba'i lus dang ldan pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1144: de mi bshigs pa'i go cha can dang /
NK131(do)006:1145: des dgra thams cad rab tu 'joms pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1146: des sdig pa dang sgrib pa thams cad rab tu 'joms par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:1147: des sems can dmyal ba'i 'gro ba rnams sbyong par rig par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:1149: gzhan yang phan yon gtam rgyud dang bcas pa ches mang bar snang bas /
NK131(do)006:1150: mdo rgyud de rnams kyang dor dgos par snang zhing /
NK131(do)006:1151: jo bo rje grong khyer sgrol 'khor gyi lugs /
NK131(do)006:1155: cha pa chos kyi seng ge sogs kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen rnams las brgyud de /
NK131(do)006:1156: grong khyer sgrol 'khor bya ba'i gdams pa /
NK131(do)006:1157: grong khyer gcig la 'khor lo gcig yod na /
NK131(do)006:1158: de thams cad 'khor ba las bsgral nas /
NK131(do)006:1159: thar pa thob par bshad pa de dag kyang dor dgos sam /
NK131(do)006:1160: de las sogs pa gzhan yang ches mang ste mtha' med /
NK131(do)006:1161: spyir sangs rgyas thams cad mkhyen pa gang yang mi mkhyen pa med pa yin na ni /
NK131(do)006:1162: yi ge dang 'khor lo btags pas grol ba yang mkhyen dgos shing /
NK131(do)006:1163: khyad par gsang sngags thabs mang ba dang /
NK131(do)006:1165: thabs tshul gyis sgo bsam gyis mi khyab pa gcig yin na'ang de ltar dgos so //
NK131(do)006:1169: mar me la mig zim bur blta ba'i mthong snang bsrung ba dang /
NK131(do)006:1170: mig 'theb 'dzub kyis btsir ba'i 'od skor la bltas
NK131(do)006:1171: na lo gsum gyi 'khrul snang 'gag par 'dod pa
NK131(do)006:1174: de lta bu yod pa rnams sgom pa'i nor pa yin na /
NK131(do)006:1175: spyir de lta bu la mtha' yas shing /
NK131(do)006:1176: 'di rnams sgom ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo ni ma yin mod /
NK131(do)006:1177: ting nge 'dzin rgyud la skye ba dang /
NK131(do)006:1178: de yang myur du skye ba dang /
NK131(do)006:1179: bogs 'don gyi thabs byed cing gi sbyor ba lta bu yin mod kyi /
NK131(do)006:1180: thabs de lta bu rnams yod pas nor na /
NK131(do)006:1182: bsam gtan gyi khang pa sgo khyog gsum dang ldan pa /
NK131(do)006:1184: lus gnad lta stangs byed cing /
NK131(do)006:1185: rdor bzlas dgang stong bum pa can sogs dang /
NK131(do)006:1187: longs spyod kyis ni rlabs gnyis la //
NK131(do)006:1188: rang gi g.yas dang lag gzhan gyis //
NK131(do)006:1190: de ni rnal 'byor pa yis rtsir //
NK131(do)006:1191: de la ye shes skye bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)006:1192: de la ci zhig skye zhes na //
NK131(do)006:1193: gzhon nu'i dga' ba ji lta'am //
NK131(do)006:1194: lkugs pa'i rmi lam ji lta'o //
NK131(do)006:1195: mchog dag'i dga' ba dga' bral dbus //
NK131(do)006:1196: stong dang stong min he ru ka /
NK131(do)006:1197: ces sogs drag rlung gi sbyor ba la rten nas /
NK131(do)006:1198: nyams myong skye ba'i thabs dang /
NK131(do)006:1199: srin po'i sbyor drug btsan thabs kyi nyams khrid skor rnams kyang /
NK131(do)006:1200: 'di lta bu'i thabs kho na yin pas /
NK131(do)006:1201: 'di rnams thams cad kyang nor pa yin mi gsung ngam /
NK131(do)006:1202: gzhan yang snod chus bkang ba la lta stangs yun ring du bltas na /
NK131(do)006:1203: 'od zer sna tshogs chu nang du mthong pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1204: de nas nam mkha' la bltas pas stong gzugs gsal ba'i thabs dang /
NK131(do)006:1205: mun khang gi rang gi thad du /
NK131(do)006:1206: bug pa lhung bzed lta bu brus nas /
NK131(do)006:1207: rtsi nag po byugs pa la yun ring du bltas pas stong gzugs gsal ba'i thabs dang /
NK131(do)006:1209: lam 'bras lam skor dgu dang bcas pa /
NK131(do)006:1210: rim lnga gnyis la sogs pa'i man ngag thams cad nas /
NK131(do)006:1212: skyes pa bogs dbyung ba la sogs kyi gdams pa /
NK131(do)006:1214: bcing ba sogs thabs du ma sna tshogs gsungs pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:1215: tha na 'og sgo 'byed 'dzums kyi thabs dang sbyor ba la rten nas /
NK131(do)006:1216: gtum mo'i bde drod skye ba sogs kyi thabs dang /
NK131(do)006:1217: bud med rten nas lam nyams su len pa'i thabs
NK131(do)006:1218: du ma ston pa'i rgyud gzhung man ngag thams cad
NK131(do)006:1220: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1221: dbang po rnon pos dbang byas pas /
NK131(do)006:1222: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags /
NK131(do)006:1223: shes pa'i gzhung de ltar kyang /
NK131(do)006:1224: khyed kyi dgongs pa ltar na dor dgos so //
NK131(do)006:1226: kun byed pa rnams lus gnad dang /
NK131(do)006:1227: lta stangs dang sems nang du mnyam par 'jog pa thams cad bkag nas /
NK131(do)006:1228: spyod lam tha mal du gnas nas /
NK131(do)006:1229: snang grags chos nyid du shes par byas pas grol
NK131(do)006:1230: ba yin zer ba la sogs pa sgom pa'i nor
NK131(do)006:1234: spyir gnas lugs kyi rtogs pa mthar thug pa mngon du gyur nas /
NK131(do)006:1235: yid byed thams ca da dang bral ba'i lta ba ci yang yid la mi byed par /
NK131(do)006:1236: rang grol klong yangs su la zla ba la dgongs pa yin mod /
NK131(do)006:1239: kha gcig dbang bskur ba yis yongs su gdungs par byed /
NK131(do)006:1240: kha cig h+aum phatahzera zhing phreng ba yongs su bgrang /
NK131(do)006:1241: kha cig rtsa dang rlung gi rnal 'byor sgom ste yongs su 'khrul /
NK131(do)006:1243: mi spang mi bsgrub mi zhen mi spyod mi 'gog par /
NK131(do)006:1244: rang lus ci bder spyod pa rab mchog dam pa'o /
NK131(do)006:1247: rlung ni mi bzung yid ni mi bcing bar /
NK131(do)006:1248: ma bcos shes pa bu chung lta bur zhog /
NK131(do)006:1251: lus kyi bya ba yongs thong rnal mar zhog /
NK131(do)006:1252: ngag gi smra brjod ma mang brag cha 'dra /
NK131(do)006:1253: yid la mi bsam la zla'i chos la ltos /
NK131(do)006:1255: gzhan yang bram ze chen po'i rdo ba skor gsum sogs /
NK131(do)006:1256: rgya gar gyi rgyu gzhung mang po dang /
NK131(do)006:1257: bod kyi yang dgas po bka' rgyud pa sogs /
NK131(do)006:1258: phyag chen gyi rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:1259: ma gcig labs sgron sogs zhi spyod pa mang pos /
NK131(do)006:1260: spyod lam ma bcos tha mal rang ka /
NK131(do)006:1261: shes pa ma bcos tha mal shes pa /
NK131(do)006:1262: blos byas yid kyi bzo rgya'i chos dang bral ba'i /
NK131(do)006:1265: dbyangs gcig tu bsnyad pa 'di rnams thams cad kyis kyang sgom pa nor bar 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)006:1267: bem po la rig pa bcug pas mgul bar nus pa'i dus su na /
NK131(do)006:1268: mi sum stong la rang gi rig pa bcug nas
NK131(do)006:1269: sgoms pas mi sum stong po des chos bya mi
NK131(do)006:1270: dgos par / skye ba de la sangs rgyas su 'gyur zer ba dang /
NK131(do)006:1273: rgya bod kyi grub thob mang pos /
NK131(do)006:1274: sku lder la sogs bem po la rig pa gtad pa tsam gyis /
NK131(do)006:1276: dam pa so chung pa lha sar byon nas /
NK131(do)006:1277: bar snang gi dril bu la rig pa gtad pa'i tshe /
NK131(do)006:1278: sgra rang 'khrol du byung par snang zhing /
NK131(do)006:1279: sngon rgyal po in+t+ra b+ho d+hi mkha' spyod du gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK131(do)006:1280: u rgyan gyi 'khor 'bangs thams cad kyang dus gcig la mkha' spyod du gshegs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1281: dam pa sangs rgyas kyi bla ma bdag nyid chen po /
NK131(do)006:1282: dpal ldan sum bcu so drug po re re mkha' spyod du gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK131(do)006:1290: dus re la mkha' spyod du gshegs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1291: rje btsun sa skya pa'i lam 'bras su yang /
NK131(do)006:1292: 'khor tshom bu lnga ldan gcig dang bcas te sangs rgya bar bshad pa /
NK131(do)006:1293: de yang bdag nyid 'tshang rgya ba'i tshe rten 'brel
NK131(do)006:1294: gyi che bas rgyud gnyis gcig char grol ba'i dus
NK131(do)006:1296: bar chad sel ba'i chos skyong dang /
NK131(do)006:1297: dngos grub ster ba'i bla ma dang /
NK131(do)006:1298: gsol ba 'debs pa'i slob ma dang bzhi ste /
NK131(do)006:1299: lnga tshan gcig sangs rgyas bar bshad pas /
NK131(do)006:1300: de dag thams cad skyon can du 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)006:1302: snang ba thams cad chos chos nyid yin snyam pa'i nges shes skyes na /
NK131(do)006:1303: 'tshams med lnga sogs mi dge ba byas tshad sangs
NK131(do)006:1304: rgyas kyi lam du 'gyur zer ba la sogs spyod
NK131(do)006:1305: pa'am nor pa mtha' yas pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1308: de la spyir gnas lugs kyi lta ba dang //
NK131(do)006:1309: rtogs pa mthar thug mngon du gyur nas //
NK131(do)006:1310: the tshom med pa'i nges shes skyes pas //
NK131(do)006:1311: byang chub kyi sems kyis blangs pa'i byams snying rje dang /
NK131(do)006:1312: thabs zab mos zin pa'i dge mi dge gang yang lam gyi grogs su 'gro la /
NK131(do)006:1313: thabs kyis ma zin na ni dge ba ltar snang
NK131(do)006:1314: ba rnams kyi lam du ci 'gyur ci cha ste
NK131(do)006:1315: / de yang kyee rdo rje las /
NK131(do)006:1316: skye bo mi zad pa yi las //
NK131(do)006:1317: gang dang gang gis 'ching gyur pa //
NK131(do)006:1318: thabs dang bcas na de nyid kyis //
NK131(do)006:1322: bzlog pa'i sgom pa 'di nyid ni //
NK131(do)006:1323: sangs rgyas mu stegs kyis mi shes /
NK131(do)006:1326: dper na chu yis gang ba'i klung //
NK131(do)006:1327: rgal 'dod skye bo shing dang ni //
NK131(do)006:1328: rtsa sogs bsdus te 'jus nas su //
NK131(do)006:1329: rkyal te pha rol rgal ba na //
NK131(do)006:1331: de bzhin chos dang chos min la //
NK131(do)006:1333: bde ba'i byang chub thob gyur nas //
NK131(do)006:1334: chos dang chos min rab tu spong /
NK131(do)006:1337: dge dang sdig pa'i las rnams kun //
NK131(do)006:1338: de nyid shes pas grol bar 'gyur //
NK131(do)006:1339: nyon mongs ye shes chen po ste //
NK131(do)006:1340: nags la me bzhin rnal 'byor grogs /
NK131(do)006:1342: 'od srung gis zhus pa'i mdor yang //
NK131(do)006:1343: dper na grong khyer skye bo mi gtsang lud //
NK131(do)006:1344: de bzhin bu ram shing pa'i zhing la phan //
NK131(do)006:1345: de bzhin byang chub sems dpa'i nyon mongs lud //
NK131(do)006:1346: des ni sangs rgyas chos rnams bskyed la phan /
NK131(do)006:1349: dper na sngags dang sman gyis yongs su zin pa'i dug gis ni shi bar byed mi nus so //
NK131(do)006:1351: shes rab dang thabs mkhas pas yongs su zin pa'i /
NK131(do)006:1352: byang chub sems dpa' de'i nyon mongs pa'i dug gis kyang /
NK131(do)006:1353: log par ltung bar byed mi nus so //
NK131(do)006:1356: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug ste /
NK131(do)006:1358: me mnyam pa yis rten nas ni /
NK131(do)006:1360: bdud rtsi nyid phyir rten nas ni /
NK131(do)006:1361: bdud rtsi nyid du 'gyur ba yin /
NK131(do)006:1363: shes rab dang thabs zab mos yongs su zin pa'i /
NK131(do)006:1364: nyon mongs par snang ba de nyid byang chub kyi rgyur gyur pa yin te /
NK131(do)006:1365: gsang chen thabs mkhas kyi mdor /
NK131(do)006:1366: tshong dpon thabs la mkhas pas /
NK131(do)006:1367: tshong pa g.yon can mdung thung gis bsad pas /
NK131(do)006:1368: tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa rdzogs par bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1370: tshong dpon gyi bu mo la spyad pas /
NK131(do)006:1371: bskal pa mang po'i tshogs 'dums pa sogs shin tu mang bas /
NK131(do)006:1372: de rnams kyang spyod pa nor bar 'gyur ram /
NK131(do)006:1374: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad bka' sgros mdzad nas /
NK131(do)006:1375: ru ta nag po bkrag med 'dul ba la /
NK131(do)006:1376: sh+aakya thub pa btang pas ru ta na re /
NK131(do)006:1377: bu chung khyod kyis bdag thul ba ma yin no zer bas /
NK131(do)006:1378: sh+aakya thub pa skyengs te log par bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1381: 'di lta bu'i tshig snyigs ma'i rgyud gzhung khung ma rnams su e yod the tshom za la /
NK131(do)006:1382: gal te yod du chug kyang nor par cis shes /
NK131(do)006:1383: sh+aakya thub pa rab byung sprul pa'i cha lugs zhi ba'i tshul can gyis /
NK131(do)006:1384: mi 'dul bar bstan pa'i tshul mdzad pas 'gal ba ci yod /
NK131(do)006:1385: sngon de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa de nyid /
NK131(do)006:1386: byang chub snying po rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs te /
NK131(do)006:1387: byang chub brnyes par mdzad pa la /
NK131(do)006:1388: bdud sde dpung dang bcas pas byang chub la bar
NK131(do)006:1389: chad brtsams pa'i dus na yang sku de nyid bcom
NK131(do)006:1390: ldan 'das phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK131(do)006:1392: gshin rje'i gshed dmar nag rnams su bstan nas /
NK131(do)006:1393: bdud dpung thams cad bcom par mdzad pa sogs rgyud sde rnams su gsal mod /
NK131(do)006:1394: gzhan yang 'jigs byed kyi rgyud kyi bshad pa /
NK131(do)006:1395: khu skyo gnyos gsum gyi lo rgyus rnams su /
NK131(do)006:1396: drag po 'jigs byed bya ba 'khor bcas kyis /
NK131(do)006:1397: lha ma yin gyi rgyal po b+ha su d+ha ri bsad nas zos /
NK131(do)006:1398: de nas kho'i bsam pa la /
NK131(do)006:1399: 'dzam bu'i gling na da nga bas dbang che ba med snyam nas /
NK131(do)006:1400: drag po 'khor bcas kyis yul lho phyogs kyi sa /
NK131(do)006:1401: ma ga ta pa kong ka'i mi thams cad bsad nas /
NK131(do)006:1402: sha khrag la longs spyod pa la /
NK131(do)006:1403: de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das yul ma ga ta'i grong khyer ser skyar bzhugs pas /
NK131(do)006:1404: gzigs nas gan du byon te /
NK131(do)006:1405: bden bzhi'i chos bshad pas ma thul bar /
NK131(do)006:1406: slar go bo ta ma khyed rang ri'i r+ts+wa la zo lung gi chu la 'thung /
NK131(do)006:1407: bya rgod phung po'i ri la song la /
NK131(do)006:1408: gso sbyong gyis zer nas ma thul lo /
NK131(do)006:1409: de nas spyan ras gzigs byon te /
NK131(do)006:1410: pha rol phyin pa bcu'i chos bshad pas /
NK131(do)006:1411: mi dkar po khyod rang song la /
NK131(do)006:1412: yig drug bzlos zer nas ma thul /
NK131(do)006:1413: de nas rta mgrin gyis phyag rgya bzhi'i chos bstan pas /
NK131(do)006:1414: khyod rang logs su song la rta skad mtsher zer nas ma thul /
NK131(do)006:1415: zer ba la sogs kyi lo rgyus mang du snang bas /
NK131(do)006:1416: rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi rgyud man ngag dang bcas
NK131(do)006:1417: pa thams cad kyang log par ni mi mdzad dam
NK131(do)006:1419: gur mgon gyi rgyud kyi lo rgyus /
NK131(do)006:1420: bram ze mchog sred nas lots+tsha ba kyi ljags nas brgyud pa'i lo rgyus su yang /
NK131(do)006:1421: dbang phyug gi bu nag po chen pos /
NK131(do)006:1422: mi rnams thams cad nang brgya za /
NK131(do)006:1423: nub brgya re za zhing 'jig rten gyi khams brlab par khad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1424: rta mgrin gyi 'dul du phyin pas /
NK131(do)006:1425: nag pos zhal du khyur mid byas te phyir phyung nas /
NK131(do)006:1426: khyod la nga 'dul ba'i gnyer med kyis /
NK131(do)006:1427: khyod rang gnas su r+ts+wa zo zer nas ma thul zhes bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1429: rdo rje rtse mo'i rgyud du /
NK131(do)006:1430: h+aum mdzad kyis rdo rje zhags pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1431: lcags sgrog la sogs rnams btang nas /
NK131(do)006:1432: lha che po bkug cing bsdams pa rnams byas pa la zhags pa sogs bcad nas bros pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1433: rdo rje lcags kyus bkug pa las /
NK131(do)006:1434: h+aum mdzad kyis bka' nyan par bskul ba la /
NK131(do)006:1436: kyee gnor sbyin nga 'jig rten gsum gyi bdag po yin na /
NK131(do)006:1437: khyod la nga ci'i phyir nyan /
NK131(do)006:1438: khyod dang khyod kyi gnas ni sngar ma mthong ngo //
NK131(do)006:1441: nga ni gnod sbyin thams cad za bar byed pas te /
NK131(do)006:1442: ces dam la gnas par bskul bas /
NK131(do)006:1444: gnod sbyin khyod ngas ngo mi shes te /
NK131(do)006:1445: bstan pa la yang nga gnas /
NK131(do)006:1446: nga 'jig rten gsum gyi bdag po yin pas mthu stobs 'dran no zer nas /
NK131(do)006:1447: lha rnams kyis rang rang gi mtshon cha stong phrag re sprul nas h+aum mdzad la 'thabs so //
NK131(do)006:1448: de nas h+aum mdzad kyis mtshon cha rnams dum bur byas te /
NK131(do)006:1451: thal bar gzhom par bka' stsal bas /
NK131(do)006:1452: nga 'ajigartena gsum gyi bdag po yin pas /
NK131(do)006:1453: khyod nga'i bka' la nyon zer ba dang /
NK131(do)006:1454: de nas h+aum mdzad kyis bcom ldan 'das la /
NK131(do)006:1455: lha chen po 'di rang gi stobs kyis dregs nas /
NK131(do)006:1456: bstan pa la 'dud du mi stub na ji ltar
NK131(do)006:1457: bgyi zhus pa la sogs mang du mchis par snang
NK131(do)006:1458: bas / rgyud de dag kyang dor dgos par 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)006:1460: mi yul na thub pa zas gtsang gi sras yin pa bzhin du /
NK131(do)006:1461: lha la brgya byin dang lha ma yin la thag bzang ris dang /
NK131(do)006:1462: dud 'gro la seng ge dam brtan dang /
NK131(do)006:1463: yi dgas la kha la me 'bar dang /
NK131(do)006:1464: dmyal ba la chos kyi rgyal po rnams /
NK131(do)006:1465: sangs rgyas kyi mchog gi sprul pa'i mdzad pa bcu gnyis ston pa yin zer ba la sogs pa /
NK131(do)006:1466: 'bras bu'i nor sa mtha' yas pa snang /
NK131(do)006:1469: de la brgya byin sogs thub pa lnga po gzhan rnams kyang /
NK131(do)006:1470: mchog gi sprul sku mdzad pa bcu gnyis ston pa can yin zhes pa'i bshad pa med cing /
NK131(do)006:1471: spyir gdul bya de lta bu rnams la /
NK131(do)006:1472: gdul byed sprul sku thub pa drug tu bstan pa yin pas 'gal ba med la /
NK131(do)006:1473: mchog gi sprul sku mdzad pa bcu gnyis ston pa
NK131(do)006:1474: can yin par bshad par yod du chug kyang 'gal
NK131(do)006:1477: ji ltar chu 'dzin las ni bsil zhim dngas shing 'jam la yang ba'i chu byung ba /
NK131(do)006:1478: de ni sa gzhir rgyu dang gnas kyi dbye bas rnam pa mang po'i ro nyid 'gyur /
NK131(do)006:1479: de bzhin legs yangs thugs rje'i sprin gyis snying po las byung yan lag brgyad ldan la /
NK131(do)006:1480: rgyud dang gnas kyi dbye bas skye dgu rnams la rnam pa mang po'i ro nyid 'gyur /
NK131(do)006:1482: de'i phyir sems can gyi don gyi ngor /
NK131(do)006:1483: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' mngal du rab tu 'jug pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:1484: dmyal bar gshegs pa yang byis pa'i skye bo rnams kyis rtag par nus pa ma yin te /
NK131(do)006:1485: dpal a ra li'i rgyud chen por /
NK131(do)006:1486: de nas byang chub sems dpa' de rnams rkang gnyis kyi mchog nyid thob nas /
NK131(do)006:1487: sangs rgyas kyi bzlos gar ston par mdzad do //
NK131(do)006:1490: la lar rdzogs par byang chub mdzad /
NK131(do)006:1491: la lar dka' ba spyod pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1492: lha las babs par sprul pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1493: de bzhin khab nas nges 'byung dang /
NK131(do)006:1494: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba ste /
NK131(do)006:1495: la lar rab tu 'byung bar mdzad /
NK131(do)006:1496: 'dul ba ston mdzad de bzhin du /
NK131(do)006:1497: bsam gyis mi khyab mngon pa'i chos /
NK131(do)006:1498: la lar sngags kyi tshul 'chad mdzad /
NK131(do)006:1499: la lar pha rol phyin pa'i tshul /
NK131(do)006:1500: la lar bye brag smra ba'i lam /
NK131(do)006:1501: la lar mdo sde ston pa ste /
NK131(do)006:1502: la lar rnam shes smra ba mang /
NK131(do)006:1503: la lar de bzhin dbu ma'o //
NK131(do)006:1504: la lar dmyal bar gshegs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1505: la lar sems can rjes bzung ba /
NK131(do)006:1506: sems can 'dul ba rgyur bcas nas /
NK131(do)006:1507: snying rje'i bsam pas gar mdzad do //
NK131(do)006:1509: sprul pa'i sku de sku yi mchog /
NK131(do)006:1510: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i rgyud 'chang ba /
NK131(do)006:1511: phyogs bcur sprul pa sna tshogs 'gyed /
NK131(do)006:1513: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdor yang /
NK131(do)006:1514: nam mkhas ji snyed khyab gyur pa /
NK131(do)006:1515: sku yis kyang ni de snyed khyab /
NK131(do)006:1517: sprul sku ni gdul bya mtha' yas pa'i bsam pa dang 'thun par /
NK131(do)006:1518: sgyu 'phrul rol pa'i rnam 'phrul sna tshogs pas /
NK131(do)006:1519: sems can gyi don rgyun chad med par mdzad pa ste /
NK131(do)006:1521: gang gis srid pa ji srid par /
NK131(do)006:1522: 'gro la phan pa sna tshogs dag /
NK131(do)006:1523: mnyam du mdzad pa'i sku de nyid /
NK131(do)006:1524: thub pa'i sprul sku rgyun mi 'chad /
NK131(do)006:1526: rigs drug so so dang 'thun pa'i sprul sku thub drug 'gog pa ni /
NK131(do)006:1527: sangs rgyas kyi sku'i gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1528: sku rnam pa sna tshogs dang sku mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:1529: gzhan yang sems can gyi las tshul bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1530: rten 'brel gyi nus pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1531: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa 'phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams 'gog pa ste /
NK131(do)006:1532: rtol med kyi tshig yang dag pa'o //
NK131(do)006:1534: mdor na bla ma'i brgyud tshul theg pa'i rnam dbye /
NK131(do)006:1540: khyad par dbang bzhi'i bskur tshul /
NK131(do)006:1542: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig thams cad kyang /
NK131(do)006:1543: rnal 'byor med kyi rgyud gzhung khung ma gang dang yang mi mthun pa'i chos skad dang /
NK131(do)006:1544: cho ga'i go rims nor sa dang /
NK131(do)006:1545: cho ga phyin ci log 'ba' zhig snang /
NK131(do)006:1546: zhes 'dir ma dpe ldeb nyer bdun nas so gsum bar chad yod /
NK131(do)006:1547: gdams pa rnams gsan pa yin te /
NK131(do)006:1548: de yang spyir sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams las /
NK131(do)006:1549: bya spyod yo ga gsum nas dbang ni bum dbang /
NK131(do)006:1550: lam ni dam rgya bskyed rims gtso che /
NK131(do)006:1551: rnal 'byor bla med zla gsang thig le sogs /
NK131(do)006:1552: pha rgyud rnams nas dbang ni gsang dbang /
NK131(do)006:1553: lam ni don chos rgya rdzogs rims rlung gtso bor byed /
NK131(do)006:1554: ma rgyud nas dbang ni gsum pa /
NK131(do)006:1555: lam ni dpe las kyi phyag rgya /
NK131(do)006:1556: rdzogs rims ni thig le gtso che /
NK131(do)006:1557: snying po don gyi rgyu 'grel dpal rnyog med la sogs ni /
NK131(do)006:1559: lam ni phyag rgya chen po'i rdzogs chen la gtso bor byed ces dang /
NK131(do)006:1560: de ltar bzhi po de theg pa mchog dman dang /
NK131(do)006:1561: zab mi zab kyi sgo nas gong 'og tu phye ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:1563: de yang rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul dra ba 'di la /
NK131(do)006:1564: rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po la sogs pa'i /
NK131(do)006:1565: rgyud 'grel gdams pa lag len dang bcas pa dpag med gcig bzhugs kyang /
NK131(do)006:1566: nyams su len pa la tshig gsum po 'dis chog ste /
NK131(do)006:1567: dag snang yid la byas pas /
NK131(do)006:1568: dngos 'dzin yid kyi spu ris subs nas /
NK131(do)006:1569: snang ba sprul skur 'char ba 'di ni /
NK131(do)006:1570: bud d+ha g+hu h+ya'i gdams pa yin /
NK131(do)006:1573: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i rnam thar dang bcas pa gsungs shing /
NK131(do)006:1574: sangs rgyas gsang ba 'di bod du yang /
NK131(do)006:1575: gangs te ser byon nas der bzhugs pa la /
NK131(do)006:1576: rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyis gdan 'dren du btang pa las /
NK131(do)006:1577: nga der yongs na srog gi bar chad du 'gro bas mi yong gsungs nas /
NK131(do)006:1578: bsam gtan phyi ma'i rim pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1579: dpung bzang legs grub rnams kyi bsdus 'grel re mdzad nas bskur /
NK131(do)006:1580: de la rgyal po dgyes nas 'bul ba mang po bardzangasa pas /
NK131(do)006:1583: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i sgrub dkyil rdo rje las rim /
NK131(do)006:1584: dkyil 'khor chos ston bya ba gzhal yas khang gi gsal byed /
NK131(do)006:1586: bsam gtan phyi ma rnas la tshig 'grel mdzad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1591: bod kyi rab byung la sogs pa rnams la /
NK131(do)006:1592: zhal lta'i springs yig dang bcas pa bskur bas /
NK131(do)006:1593: rgyal po yang shin tu dgyes so //
NK131(do)006:1594: gzhan yang sgeg pa rdo rje /
NK131(do)006:1598: sngags snying mar grags pa rnams kyi rgyud gzhung man ngag /
NK131(do)006:1599: dbang dang gdams pa thams cad kyi dam pas gsan par bshad cing /
NK131(do)006:1600: de'i lo rgyus la sogs shin tu mang bas /
NK131(do)006:1601: dam pa rgya gar gyis kyang rdzogs chen dang /
NK131(do)006:1602: snying ma'i chos skor ma bsgyur ba dang /
NK131(do)006:1603: ma bshad pa'i shes byed yang dag pa rnyed na bstan du gsol /
NK131(do)006:1605: dam pa rgya gar gyis mdzad pa'i zhi byed ces yongs su grags pa 'di'i /
NK131(do)006:1606: bka' babs snyan rgyud bzhi'i gdams pa la /
NK131(do)006:1607: thun mong gi gdams pa grub thob pho mo lnga bcu'i gdams pa /
NK131(do)006:1608: gzhung gnad bsdus pa lam dngul sgong dag pa /
