NK131(do)006:1609: ngo sprod kyi gnad bsdus pa lam dri med gser sgong dag pa /
NK131(do)006:1610: gdams pa'i gnad bsdus pa lam dri med shel sgong dag pa rnams kyi /
NK131(do)006:1611: phal che ba gcig rdzogs chen sogs /
NK131(do)006:1612: snying ma'i bla ma pad+ma 'byung gnas /
NK131(do)006:1618: bal po b+ha su d+ha ra rnams la gsan pa'i rdzogs chen dang /
NK131(do)006:1619: snying ma rnams kyi gdams pa yin pas /
NK131(do)006:1621: chos zhi byed rnams chos log yin no //
NK131(do)006:1622: yang na de'i nang gi rdzogs chen sogs rnams log pa yin bstan du gsol /
NK131(do)006:1623: des na dam pa rgya gar gyis rdzogs chen ma bsgyur ba la sogs pa'i tshig 'dis /
NK131(do)006:1624: ma byon pa'i sangs rgyas gnyis par zhal gyis bzhes
NK131(do)006:1625: pa'i dam pa sangs rgyas kyang skyon can du ma
NK131(do)006:1627: sngon gyi rgyal blon byang chub sems dpa'i sku ring la bsgyur ba'i chos min pas /
NK131(do)006:1628: rdzogs chen 'di gsang sngags snying ma'ang ma yin /
NK131(do)006:1629: dus phyis lo pan mkhas grub rnams kyis ma bsgyur bas /
NK131(do)006:1630: gsang sngags gsar ma yang ma yin /
NK131(do)006:1631: kho rang la dgos kyi rgyud dang rgya gzhung mtha' yas pa yod par 'dod pas /
NK131(do)006:1632: n+aa ro dang ni khu chos drug lta bu /
NK131(do)006:1633: rgyud sde'i dgongs pa bla mas man ngag tu sdebs pa de yang ma yin /
NK131(do)006:1636: de lta na rgyal blon de rnams kyi dus su /
NK131(do)006:1637: rdzogs chen la sogs pa rnams ni ma bsgyur /
NK131(do)006:1638: kyee rdor la sogs de bas kyang med pas /
NK131(do)006:1639: de dus kyi rgyal blon rnams rdo rje theg pa'i
NK131(do)006:1640: skal ba dang mi ldan pa'i skal chad yin nam
NK131(do)006:1644: b+ai ma la rnams kyis gsungs pa'i gsang sngags bla med kyi lam de gang yin bstan du gsol /
NK131(do)006:1645: gzhan yang sngon gyi lo pan 'di rnams kyis kyang /
NK131(do)006:1646: gsang sngags bla med gsar ma rnams de dus ma bsgyur ba de /
NK131(do)006:1647: de kun gyis kyang rgya gar nas ma rnyed pas ma bsgyur ba yin nam /
NK131(do)006:1648: yod kyang ma bsgyur ba yin /
NK131(do)006:1649: de lta na ni gzhan la yang mtshungs so //
NK131(do)006:1650: yang de dus su slob dpon pad+ma la sogs pas
NK131(do)006:1651: bsgyur ba'i gsang chen bla med kyi man ngag rnams
NK131(do)006:1652: / kun dang thun mong ma yin pa'i don gyis /
NK131(do)006:1653: kun gyis spyod yul du ma gyur pas thams cad kyi mngon du ma snang mod /
NK131(do)006:1654: rgyud gzhung kha gcig ni mngon du yang snang ste /
NK131(do)006:1656: gsang sngags bla med kyang de dus /
NK131(do)006:1657: sgyu 'phrul gsang snying la sogs sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad /
NK131(do)006:1658: gsang snying gi 'grel pa nyi 'od seng ges mdzad pa rnams /
NK131(do)006:1661: de'i 'grel pa sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa gnyis /
NK131(do)006:1662: bee ro tsa nas bsgyur bar /
NK131(do)006:1663: 'phang thang sogs su bshad gsungs shing /
NK131(do)006:1664: sku'i rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor /
NK131(do)006:1665: gsung gi rgyudazla gsang thig le /
NK131(do)006:1666: thugs kyi rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa /
NK131(do)006:1667: sgyu 'phrul dra ba rnams lce bkra shis kyis bsgyur bar /
NK131(do)006:1669: lhan dkar gnyis su bshad ces /
NK131(do)006:1671: 'di rnams thams cad ni rdzogs chen gyi rjes 'breng snying ma yin zhing /
NK131(do)006:1672: khyad par du sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi bla ma rgyud pa sogs kyang /
NK131(do)006:1673: gsang snying la sogs pa dang khyad med do //
NK131(do)006:1674: gzhan yang de dus sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK131(do)006:1677: bee ro tsa na gsum la bshad cing bsgyur ba la snga dar zer /
NK131(do)006:1678: de nas de rnams pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis /
NK131(do)006:1679: snyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra /
NK131(do)006:1680: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs rnams la bshad cing bsgyur ba la bar dar zer /
NK131(do)006:1682: rma rinachena mchog la bshad cing bsgyur ba la phyi dar zer la /
NK131(do)006:1683: de dag ni sngags snying ma rdzogs chen gyi rjes 'breng yin no //
NK131(do)006:1684: phyis kyi lo pan rnams kyis ma bsgyur ba'i shes byed med de /
NK131(do)006:1689: lo chen rin bzang rnams kyis rdzogs chen dang /
NK131(do)006:1691: yang dag gi 'grel pa kun snying gis mdzad pa rnams bsgyur bar /
NK131(do)006:1692: bcom ldan ral gris bshad 'dug pa ci yin /
NK131(do)006:1693: kho rang la dgos rgyud yod pas ci nyes te /
NK131(do)006:1694: dam pa'i zhi byed la'ang kho rang gi dgos rgyud /
NK131(do)006:1695: da lta'i rgyud gzhan kun dang chos skad ris mi mthun pa'i /
NK131(do)006:1696: a li ka li chu rlung rol pa'i gsang rgyud che chung /
NK131(do)006:1697: bdag med ma'i brda rgyud rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:1698: phyag chen brda rtsal kho rang gi dgos rgyud /
NK131(do)006:1699: brda rgyud le'u lnga bcu rtsa lnga pa yod par bshad pas na /
NK131(do)006:1700: dgos rgyud yod pas ci nyes /
NK131(do)006:1702: lam 'bras la sogs pa rnams la yang /
NK131(do)006:1704: brtag gnyis sogs rnams kyang dgos rgyud yin pa dang 'dra mod /
NK131(do)006:1705: chos drug lta bu rgyud sder med na ni /
NK131(do)006:1706: bla mas sdebs rgyu cang yod dam /
NK131(do)006:1707: thams cad 'dra ba gcig dgos na ni /
NK131(do)006:1708: rdo rje theg pa'i dbye ba mang pos ci byed rtol med kyi tshig go /
NK131(do)006:1710: glang dar mas bstan pa snubs pa'i rjes su /
NK131(do)006:1711: rdzun rgyud brtsams pa de nas /
NK131(do)006:1713: gnubs a ro drang shag rnams kyis /
NK131(do)006:1715: lce btsun gyis b+ai ma la snying tig /
NK131(do)006:1716: las 'brel rtsal gyis mkha' 'gro snying tig /
NK131(do)006:1717: rdo rje gling pas rdor sems snying tig gnubs dang
NK131(do)006:1718: nyang ral sogs kyis bka' brgyad dang bder 'dus sogs
NK131(do)006:1720: bod blun pos rang bzo byas pa'i rgyud min rgyud du rdzus nas /
NK131(do)006:1721: bstan pa chu rnyog ma can lta bur byas pa'i chos log yin /
NK131(do)006:1722: rgyu mtshan 'di rnams la dgos nas /
NK131(do)006:1723: lots+tsha ba rin chen bzang po dang /
NK131(do)006:1725: pho brang zhi ba 'od rnams kyis /
NK131(do)006:1726: da lta las zad rgyal po'i khrims nyams pas /
NK131(do)006:1727: rdzogs chen ming btags sngags log bod du dar /
NK131(do)006:1728: de yi rgyal khams phung te 'di 'dra 'gyur /
NK131(do)006:1732: 'o na glang dar mas bstan pa snubs phyin chad /
NK131(do)006:1733: de nas sngags pa rnasama kyis brtsams pa'i chos log yin du chug /
NK131(do)006:1734: de yan chad kyi pad+ma sam b+ha wa /
NK131(do)006:1736: sangs rgyas gsang ba rnams kyis /
NK131(do)006:1737: rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan dang /
NK131(do)006:1738: sa skya pa'i mkhon klu dbang bsrung ba rdo rje rinachena sogs la gnang ba'i rdzogs chen dang /
NK131(do)006:1739: yang phur rnams kyang log pa yin nam /
NK131(do)006:1740: de lta na ni klu dbang bsrung ba sogs sa
NK131(do)006:1741: skya pa rjes 'breng dang bcas pa rnams kyis kyang
NK131(do)006:1743: rang gzhan thams cad log pa'i lam du khrid pa ni /
NK131(do)006:1744: sa skya pa thams cad 'jam dpa'i dabyangasakyi rnam sprul du grags kyang cher ma 'os so //
NK131(do)006:1745: gzhan yang dar rje yongs grags /
NK131(do)006:1747: lce btsun rnams kyi dus la /
NK131(do)006:1749: lha bla ma sogs kyis sngags log brtsams par dgongs nas /
NK131(do)006:1750: sun 'byin gyi 'byam yig btang du chug ste /
NK131(do)006:1751: phal cher dus mtshungs yin nam /
NK131(do)006:1754: nyang ral la sogs pa rnams /
NK131(do)006:1755: phyis rang byung rdo rje ba sogs dang dus mtshungs tsam yin pas /
NK131(do)006:1756: de la dgongs nas ces pa 'di tol med do //
NK131(do)006:1757: phyis 'dis rnams 'ong par dgongs nas gsungs pa yin na ni /
NK131(do)006:1759: sh+aakya thub pa las kyang ches lhag par 'gyur te /
NK131(do)006:1760: sh+aakya thub pas ni bod lta bu'i chos log rnams lung ston gyis mi lang /
NK131(do)006:1761: zhes zer ba ma yin nam /
NK131(do)006:1762: 'di rnams kha gcig ni ma nges bzhin du smra ba ste /
NK131(do)006:1763: bka' brgyad dang bder 'dus ces pa'i ming tsam gyi cha yang ma nges par smra ba'o /
NK131(do)006:1765: rdzogs chen ming btags chos log /
NK131(do)006:1767: rdzogs chen gyi ming gis btags pa'i sngags log mang po dar bas /
NK131(do)006:1768: des rgyal khams phung zer ba yin gyis /
NK131(do)006:1769: rdzogs chen dar bas zer ba ma yin mod /
NK131(do)006:1771: a tsa ra dmar po la sogs pas /
NK131(do)006:1772: chags lam gyi gdams pa zhes bya ba'i lam bstan nas spyod tsing sna tshogs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1773: ser khyim zer nas rab byung gis bud med bsten pa sogs rnams 'byung pas /
NK131(do)006:1774: de rnams dgag pa'i phyir du yin gyi /
NK131(do)006:1775: rdzogs chen dgag pa ma yin par nges shing /
NK131(do)006:1777: de dus gsang sngags gsar ma'i kye rdor cha 'thun gyi rgyud /
NK131(do)006:1778: phyag rgya chen po thig le'i rgyud /
NK131(do)006:1779: ye shes snying po ye shes theg le rnams a
NK131(do)006:1780: tsa ra dmar zhabs kyis byas par 'dod pa sogs
NK131(do)006:1781: / rgyud mang du dgags zin pa'i rnams /
NK131(do)006:1782: phyis kyi mkhas grub mang pos dpang du byed par snang mod /
NK131(do)006:1784: rje rin po che mgos kyis /
NK131(do)006:1785: dang por rdzogs chen la slob gnyer mdzad /
NK131(do)006:1786: lots+tsha sbyangs nas rgya gar la rdzogs chen zhur song /
NK131(do)006:1787: snga phyir rgya gar du lan bcu gnyis su phyin /
NK131(do)006:1788: bla ma bdun bcu mkha' 'gro ma gnyis dang don gnyis bsten /
NK131(do)006:1789: gsang 'dus la sogs bla med kyi rgyud mtha' dag la mkhas par sbyangs nas bod du bsgyur /
NK131(do)006:1790: mar pa sogs bu slob mkhas grub mang du byung /
NK131(do)006:1791: mar pas kyang brtag gnyis ma gtogs /
NK131(do)006:1792: mgos 'gyur la thugs rtsis dang bshad pa mdzad /
NK131(do)006:1793: deng sang bod na gsang 'dus bshad srol gang yod pa thams cad /
NK131(do)006:1794: mgos kyi chos rgyud du ma gyur pa med /
NK131(do)006:1795: rgya gar ba kun gyis kyang /
NK131(do)006:1796: rdzogs chen bya ba rgya gar du byung pa med /
NK131(do)006:1798: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa ma yin /
NK131(do)006:1799: rang bzo'i rdzun chos yin pa 'dug gsungs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1800: rang gis kyang 'tshang rig pa la brten nas /
NK131(do)006:1801: skyes bu dam pa des rdzogs chen sun 'byin gyi 'byam yig gnyis mdzad /
NK131(do)006:1802: sa pan gyis kyang mgos kyi 'byam yig la yi rang phul /
NK131(do)006:1805: mgos kyis dang por rgyal sras zur po che la /
NK131(do)006:1806: sgyu 'phrul gsang snying zhur song pa la ma gnang nas /
NK131(do)006:1807: de la zhe mkhon du bzung pa yin te /
NK131(do)006:1809: sngar kha che na nang pa'i pan+di ta gcig bslab pa 'chal nas /
NK131(do)006:1810: gnas dbyung byed par brtsams pa la /
NK131(do)006:1811: khos de ltar ma byed mkhar rnga ma brdung dang /
NK131(do)006:1812: nga rang 'gro zer ba la ma nyan par de ltar byas pas /
NK131(do)006:1813: khos snying nad du bzung ste bstan pa la 'dran bcug pa'i grub mtha' gcig brtsams snyam nas /
NK131(do)006:1815: sog po'i log chos bya ba brtsams ces pa ltar du /
NK131(do)006:1816: zur la zhe gnag pa'i dbang gis /
NK131(do)006:1817: sgyu 'phrul gsang ba snying po la sogs pa rnams la skyon btsal nas /
NK131(do)006:1818: smad pa'i phyir du 'byam yig bcos pa yin gyis /
NK131(do)006:1819: rgya gar nas rdzogs chen min pa /
NK131(do)006:1820: mdo rgyud bstan bcos thams cad khong gis snyed nas bsgyur ba ni ma yin mod /
NK131(do)006:1821: mgos kyis kyang rgya gar nas /
NK131(do)006:1822: rgyal bu sprin gyis shugs can la gshin rje 'char ka'i rgyud sgrub thabs /
NK131(do)006:1823: mdos la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:1824: gsang ba 'dus pa sogs lhan du zhus nas bsgyur te /
NK131(do)006:1825: char ka mgos lugs zhes grags pa la /
NK131(do)006:1826: sun snyon gyis chos la skyon btags pa'i nyes pas /
NK131(do)006:1827: khong rang la yang skyon mang po byung pa'i lo rgyus kyang brjod par snang mod /
NK131(do)006:1828: rje mar ba lo tsha yang mgos kyi slob ma yin zhing /
NK131(do)006:1829: mgos 'gyur la thugs rtsis su mdzad cing bshad pa yang mdzad gsung ba /
NK131(do)006:1830: 'gyur la rtsis mdzad pa ni srid mod /
NK131(do)006:1832: mgos nas mar pa la brgyud de /
NK131(do)006:1833: de'i slob ma me rngog mtshur gsum dang /
NK131(do)006:1834: mi la sogs su brgyud pa'i chos srol e yod ni the tshom za mod /
NK131(do)006:1835: deng sang bod na 'dug pa'i gsang 'dus kyis bshad srol gang yod /
NK131(do)006:1836: mgos kyi chos brgyud du ma gyur pa med ces pa'ang /
NK131(do)006:1837: ha cang rdzun du ma gyur gcig /
NK131(do)006:1840: mkhas pa pan+di ta'i lugs kyi brgyud pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1841: grub thob nyams kyi brgyud pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1842: man ngag rim lnga dang bcas pa rnams /
NK131(do)006:1843: mkhas pa ye shes snying po dang /
NK131(do)006:1844: n+aa ro pan chen nas mar pa la brgyud pa /
NK131(do)006:1845: gsang 'dus mar lugs su grags pa thams cad dang /
NK131(do)006:1847: ye shes zhabs lugs kyi dbang rgyud man ngag dang bcas pa /
NK131(do)006:1849: ku su lu la sogs pa nas /
NK131(do)006:1851: de nas rong pa gar dge /
NK131(do)006:1852: lha byang chub 'od la sogs la brgyud pa rnams te /
NK131(do)006:1855: ye shes zhabs lugs gnyis kyi dbang bka'/
NK131(do)006:1858: re wan tra pa sogs nas /
NK131(do)006:1859: chags lots+tsha ba la brgyud pa chags lugs skor dang /
NK131(do)006:1860: ye shes zhabs lugs gnyos lo nas brgyud pas gnyos lugs dang /
NK131(do)006:1861: ye shes zhabs lugs gnyan chung lots+tsha nas /
NK131(do)006:1862: sa skya pa la brgyud pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:1863: yang 'phags lugs kyi dbang bshad man ngag dang bcas pa pan chen sh+aakya sh+ri nas /
NK131(do)006:1864: sa skya pa la brgyud pa sa lugs rnams te /
NK131(do)006:1865: de thams cad la mgos nas brgyud rim 'ded pa gcig kyang ma mthong ngo /
NK131(do)006:1866: rgya gar gyi bla ma rnams kyis /
NK131(do)006:1867: nged kyi rgya gar na rdzogs chen bya ba med ces gsungs pa sogs kyang /
NK131(do)006:1868: rdzun po che la dus rtags mang /
NK131(do)006:1869: zhes pa ltar bla ma de rnams spags par ma gyur gcig /
NK131(do)006:1870: sa skya pan chen gyis mgos kyi 'byam yig la yi rang phul ba bden srid kyang /
NK131(do)006:1871: rdzogs chen sogs smad pa la phul ba ma yin te /
NK131(do)006:1873: gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba rnams 'di bzhed /
NK131(do)006:1874: phyi 'gyur ba rnams 'di bzhed ces gsungs shing /
NK131(do)006:1875: rdzogs chen bkag pa'i gsung med /
NK131(do)006:1876: lha btsas zhes bya'i lots+tsha ba /
NK131(do)006:1877: des kyang chos log sun 'byin pa /
NK131(do)006:1878: zhes bya'i bstan bcos mdzad nas ni /
NK131(do)006:1879: chos dang chos min rnam par phye /
NK131(do)006:1880: zhes pa'i rjes su chos log ngos bzung ba ni /
NK131(do)006:1881: de nas chos rje sa skya pa /
NK131(do)006:1882: chen po bzhugs pa yan chad du /
NK131(do)006:1883: chos log spyod pa nyung zhes thos /
NK131(do)006:1884: phyis nas phag mos byin rlabs dang /
NK131(do)006:1885: sems bskyed rmi lam ma la sogs /
NK131(do)006:1886: yi dam sgom pa dkrong bskyed dang /
NK131(do)006:1887: dkar po gcig thub la sogs pa /
NK131(do)006:1888: sangs rgyas bstan dang 'gal ba yi /
NK131(do)006:1889: chos log du ma deng sang 'phel /
NK131(do)006:1892: dgas po bka' rgyud kyi 'bri stag mtshal 'brug pa
NK131(do)006:1893: rnams kyi chos lugs kha yar bkag pa ma gtogs
NK131(do)006:1894: / rdzogs chen bkag pa yod med de'i gsung rab rnams gzigs pas gsol lo //
NK131(do)006:1895: gzhan yang sdom gsum rab dbyer sa pan gyi zhal nas /
NK131(do)006:1896: gzhan yang gsang sngags gsar snying la /
NK131(do)006:1897: bod du sbyar ba'i rgyud sde mang /
NK131(do)006:1898: de 'dra'i rang bzo'i mdo rgyud la /
NK131(do)006:1899: mkhas pas yid brtan mi bya'o //
NK131(do)006:1902: rang bzo'i mdo rgyud yod gsung pa ma gtogs /
NK131(do)006:1903: dgos su rdzogs chen bkag pa sogs kyi bstan bcos der ma mthong zhing /
NK131(do)006:1904: khyad par khong rang gis bod du bsgyur ba'i chos
NK131(do)006:1905: thams cad phal cher gsan pa'i rnam grangs mdzad pa'i
NK131(do)006:1906: skabs su / sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhi po yang /
NK131(do)006:1907: nyan bshad yod pa phal cher thos /
NK131(do)006:1908: thos pa de dag thams cad kyang /
NK131(do)006:1909: ming kyang tsam du ma bzhag go /
NK131(do)006:1910: bye brag smra dang mdo sde pa /
NK131(do)006:1911: sems tsam pa dang dbu ma yi /
NK131(do)006:1912: gdams ngag ji snyed phal cher thos /
NK131(do)006:1913: deng sang bod la grags pa yi /
NK131(do)006:1914: zhi byed rdzogs chen gcod la sogs /
NK131(do)006:1916: gzhan yang bod dang rgya gar la /
NK131(do)006:1917: deng sang grags pa phal mo che /
NK131(do)006:1918: bdag gis legs par 'bad de nyan /
NK131(do)006:1919: slabs pa de dag ming rkyang min /
NK131(do)006:1920: des na bdag la phyogs lhung med /
NK131(do)006:1922: snying ma dang rdzogs chen dgag pa yod med gzur gnas thams cad kyis dgongs pa ltar yin /
NK131(do)006:1924: chos rje sa skya pa khu dbon rnams /
NK131(do)006:1925: sngar rdzogs chen pa'i brgyud pa yin na'ang /
NK131(do)006:1926: phyis chos log yin par rig nas rgyab du skyur /
NK131(do)006:1929: de sogs bden pa ni ma yin te /
NK131(do)006:1930: pad+ma sam b+ha wa'i dngos slob mkhon klu dbang bsrung ba dang /
NK131(do)006:1931: tshe 'dzin gyi sras po rdo rje rin chen nas bzung te /
NK131(do)006:1932: de'i sras shes rab yon tan /
NK131(do)006:1934: de'i sras tshul khrims rgyal po /
NK131(do)006:1935: de bzhin du rdo rje gtsug tor /
NK131(do)006:1938: de'i sras sh+aakya blo gros zhes bya ba thams cad kyang /
NK131(do)006:1939: phyi pha rol du phyin pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1940: nang rdo rje theg pa'i gzhung lugs la bslab cing /
NK131(do)006:1941: khyad par du sngags snying ma rdo rje theg pa'i gsang ba sde drug /
NK131(do)006:1943: phra mo nyer gcig rnams gtso bor bzung nas /
NK131(do)006:1944: spyod pa la sogs kyi chos drug ces bya ba'i man ngag dag ldan zhing /
NK131(do)006:1945: yang dag grub pa he ru ka lha dgu dang /
NK131(do)006:1946: rdo rje phur pa'i yi dam gyi sgo nas dngos grub thob pa sha stag yin zhing /
NK131(do)006:1947: sh+aakya blogrosa la sras gnyis las /
NK131(do)006:1948: gcen po shes rab tshul khrims kyis yab mes kyi chos thams cad sbyangs shing /
NK131(do)006:1949: rdo rje phur pa'i sgo nas dngos grub mnyes te /
NK131(do)006:1950: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab cing /
NK131(do)006:1951: tshangs par spyod pa mdzes par bya ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:1952: de'i gcung po mkhon dkon mchog rgyal pos /
NK131(do)006:1953: yab mes kyi chos phal che ba gcig gis tshims par mdzad nas /
NK131(do)006:1954: sngags phyi 'gyur dar byung ba dang /
NK131(do)006:1955: de la spro zhing gcen gyis kyang bskul te /
NK131(do)006:1957: 'brog mi sogs la kyee rdo rje la sogs pa'i
NK131(do)006:1958: rgyud 'grel man ngag dang bcas pa gsan zhing sbyangs
NK131(do)006:1959: pa mdzad do // de'i sras sa chen /
NK131(do)006:1965: bsod nams rgyal mtshan gyi sras /
NK131(do)006:1968: de thams cad kyis kyang sngags bsar snying gnyis la /
NK131(do)006:1969: dus skabs kyi dar rgyas che chung tsam ma gtogs pa /
NK131(do)006:1970: thog mar yab mes kyi chos sngags snying ma la sbyangs nas grub pa brnyes par mdzad cing /
NK131(do)006:1971: sngags gsar ma la thugs sbyong mdzad pa 'ga' zhig yin no //
NK131(do)006:1974: rje btsun grags pa rnams kyis yang phur sogs la yig sna yang mang du mdzad /
NK131(do)006:1976: rdo rje phur pa'i rtsa rgyud kyi dum bu la /
NK131(do)006:1977: pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi rgya dpe dang mthun pa'i bzhi 'gyur mdzad /
NK131(do)006:1979: chos rje 'jam pa'i dbyangs chen po bsod nam rgyal mtshan yan chad kyi /
NK131(do)006:1980: sa skya mkhon gyi gdung rabs thams cad kyang /
NK131(do)006:1981: sngags snying ma yang phur gyi grub pa brnyes pa sha stag yin pa la sus snyon du yod /
NK131(do)006:1982: de nas chos rje bsod nams rgyal mtshan dpal bzang pos /
NK131(do)006:1983: yab mes kyi chos rnams nub kyis dogs nas /
NK131(do)006:1984: mkhas pa dpal ldan seng ge dang /
NK131(do)006:1985: gan pa rin chen rgyal mtshan rnams la yab mes kyi chos yang dag dang /
NK131(do)006:1986: phur pa rnams kyi dbang bka' bshad bka' rnams gsan cing /
NK131(do)006:1987: rgyun gyi thugs dam gyi gtso bor mdzad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:1990: dkyil chog la sogs pa'i yig sna mang du mdzad cing /
NK131(do)006:1991: dbus gtsang gi gdan sa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:1994: bsam yas la sogs pa rnams su /
NK131(do)006:1995: phur pa'i sgrub mchod kyi srol chen po btsugs nas /
NK131(do)006:1996: da lta yang ma chag par lo dus bzhin sgrub pa la sus snyon /
NK131(do)006:1997: des na phyis rgyab tu skyur zhes /
NK131(do)006:1998: sa skya pa la yang bskur 'debs ngan pa de lta bu smras nas /
NK131(do)006:1999: sa skya pa rnams dri ma can du ma gyur gcig /
NK131(do)006:2003: rgyal ba 'bri khung pa la sogs pa rnams /
NK131(do)006:2004: dang por ma brtags par rdzogs chen re gsan /
NK131(do)006:2005: yang phyis mkhas grub du gyur nas /
NK131(do)006:2006: chos log yin par mkhyen cing /
NK131(do)006:2007: ngan skyugs ltar dor te su la yang ma gsungs
NK131(do)006:2008: pas da lta yang de rnams nas rgyud pa'i bshad
NK131(do)006:2009: srol med lo / zhes pa la /
NK131(do)006:2011: rje btsun mi las dang por zhus nas /
NK131(do)006:2012: phyis dor ba'i lo rgyus ma tshor zhing /
NK131(do)006:2013: 'gur mdzad pa rnams su rdzogs pa chen pos mdun nas gzer /
NK131(do)006:2014: phyag rgya chen pos rgyab nas gzer /
NK131(do)006:2015: kha nas gdams ngag khrag ltar skyug /
NK131(do)006:2017: rje btsun gyis mdzad pa'i bde mchog snyan rgyud kyi /
NK131(do)006:2018: phyag rgya chen po ye shes gsal byed du /
NK131(do)006:2019: sems gsal stong rtog bral phyag rgya chen po de la /
NK131(do)006:2020: phyag chen pas rtog bral zer /
NK131(do)006:2021: rdzogs chen pas chos nyid zer /
NK131(do)006:2022: phar phyin pas stong nyid zer /
NK131(do)006:2023: zhes sogs gsungs pa ma gtogs skyur bar mi snang zhing /
NK131(do)006:2024: phag mo grub pas kyang dang por gsan nas /
NK131(do)006:2025: phyis dor ba'i gtam khong rang gis gsungs pa rnams su ni mi snang /
NK131(do)006:2026: khyad par nyid kyi gsung rnams su /
NK131(do)006:2027: gsar ma'i rgyud bzhi snying ma'i theg pa dgu /
NK131(do)006:2028: zhes sogs de gnyis mtshungs pa'i rgyu mtshan dang bcas
NK131(do)006:2029: pa mang du snang ba la yang snyon du med
NK131(do)006:2031: khams na bzhugs pa'i dus chung ngu nas rdzogs chen dang /
NK131(do)006:2032: phur pa 'jigs byed rnams la thugs dam mdzad /
NK131(do)006:2033: dus phyis nyid kyi bstan bcos sdom gsum gnad gcig
NK131(do)006:2034: dang dgongs gcig la sogs pa rnams su shes byed
NK131(do)006:2035: lung dang bcas pa dpag tu med pa gsungs te
NK131(do)006:2036: / spyi bo la sogs pa'i rtsa 'khor lo bzhir /
NK131(do)006:2037: nyon mongs bzhi dag pa'i bral 'bras la /
NK131(do)006:2038: sngags snying ma la mtshon na /
NK131(do)006:2039: spyi bor 'jam dpal sku'i lha tshogs lta bur sangs rgyas /
NK131(do)006:2042: lte bar ma mo rbod gtong gi lha tshogs lta bur sangs rgyas /
NK131(do)006:2044: gzhan yang rdzogs chen gyi rgyud kyi lung 'dren sogs mtha' yas par snang zhing /
NK131(do)006:2045: da lta de rnams nas brgyud rim ded pa med pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK131(do)006:2046: chos log tu rig nas phyis dor bas so //
NK131(do)006:2047: zhes pa ni rtog med kyi tshig ste /
NK131(do)006:2049: sngar bka' bsdams pa'i gdam pa zhus pa rnams /
NK131(do)006:2050: chos log tu rig nas phyis dor ba yin nam ste /
NK131(do)006:2051: bka' bsdams pa'i chos dgas po lha rje nas 'ded pa nyung zhing /
NK131(do)006:2052: mi la ras pa'i chos rgyud ded pa shin tu dar ba'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:2053: phag mo grub pas kyang dgas po lha rje dang mjal ba phyin chad nas /
NK131(do)006:2054: sa skya pa'i rgyud lung man ngag dang bcas pa rnams /
NK131(do)006:2055: chos log tu rig nas dor ba yin nam ste /
NK131(do)006:2056: da lta khong nas brgyud pa mi snang phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:2057: chos rje 'jig rten mgon po 'bri khung pas kyang /
NK131(do)006:2058: sngar thugs dam mdzad pa'i rdo rje 'jigs byed kyang /
NK131(do)006:2059: chos log tu dgongs nas dor bar 'gyur te /
NK131(do)006:2060: da lta khong nas brgyud pa mi snang pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:2061: dgas po bka' brgyud pa'i rgyal ba yang dgon pas /
NK131(do)006:2062: rdzogs chen dang snying ma'i bla ma mang po brten nas /
NK131(do)006:2063: sngags snying ma'i bka' gter mang du gsan /
NK131(do)006:2064: rdzogs chen rgyud mtha' sogs la yig sna mang du mdzad /
NK131(do)006:2065: nyams rdzogs kyi yon tan phul du phyin pa mnga' zhing /
NK131(do)006:2067: chos thams cad kyang thams cad du bden mod kyang /
NK131(do)006:2068: rdzogs chen zhes pa'i sgra bo che /
NK131(do)006:2069: sprang go ba'i len phyogs kyang de la bgyis /
NK131(do)006:2070: gcig char gyi rtogs pa yang de la 'khrungs /
NK131(do)006:2072: gnas lugs nyams su len pa'i phyag rgya chen po dang gcig /
NK131(do)006:2073: lam khyer rkyen la byed pa'i pha rol phyin pa dang gnyis /
NK131(do)006:2074: snang rkyen lam du slong ba'i sdug bsngal zhi byed dang gsum /
NK131(do)006:2075: mthar thug zad par skyel ba'i rdzogs pa chen po dang bzhi /
NK131(do)006:2076: 'di bzhi rnal 'byor bdag gi dam chos gcig lags pas /
NK131(do)006:2077: chos gzhan gang la'ang 'gram chu mi btang lags so //
NK131(do)006:2078: zhes sogs gsungs nas tshad mar mdzad /
NK131(do)006:2080: phyon ma rog rtsal zhes pa'i /
NK131(do)006:2082: bka' rgyud de rnams kyang dri ma can du ma sbyor zhig /
NK131(do)006:2083: rje dus gsum mkhyen pa la sogs pa /
NK131(do)006:2084: kar+m+aa pa rjes 'brang dang bcas pa thams cad kyis /
NK131(do)006:2085: sngags snying ma rdzogs chen dang bcas pa la /
NK131(do)006:2086: thos bsam sgom gsum gyi sgo nas thugs dam mdzad pa 'ba' zhig yin te /
NK131(do)006:2087: rje dus gsum mkhyen pas kyang /
NK131(do)006:2088: bka' bsdams pa po to ba'i slob ma /
NK131(do)006:2089: bla ma brag dkar ba la rdzogs chen a ro sogs mang po gsan zhing /
NK131(do)006:2092: snying ma'i bla ma khams kyi kahthoga pa byams pa 'bum la bsnyen rdzogs dang /
NK131(do)006:2094: snying ma'i ma phur la sogs pa rnams zhus nas thugs nyams su bzhes /
NK131(do)006:2095: der rjes sprul sku thams cad mkhyen pa rang byung rdo rjes /
NK131(do)006:2099: snye mdo ba kun dga' don grub /
NK131(do)006:2102: ku ma ra tsa rnams la /
NK131(do)006:2103: sngags snying ma'i dbang rgyud sgrub dkyil /
NK131(do)006:2104: man ngag mtha' yas pa'i bka' gter rnams gsan nas /
NK131(do)006:2105: mkhas shing thugs dam gyi snying por mdzad de /
NK131(do)006:2106: snying tig chen mo'i yig cha dang /
NK131(do)006:2107: gzhan yang yig sna sgrub skor mang du mdzad cing /
NK131(do)006:2108: nyid kyis mdzad pa'i zab mo nang don /
NK131(do)006:2109: dam tshig rgya mtsho la sogs pa'i bstan bcos rnams su yang dpang du mdzad nas lung drangs te /
NK131(do)006:2110: zab mo nang don gyi rtsa dbu ma chos lnga ldan ngos 'dzin pa'i skabs su /
NK131(do)006:2112: snying khar dngas ma lnga 'dus kyi sems shes gsungs pa yang 'di kho na ste /
NK131(do)006:2113: sha'i dngas ma rtsa dbu ma /
NK131(do)006:2114: khrag gi dngas ma a thung /
NK131(do)006:2115: rgyus pa'i dngas ma a ham /
NK131(do)006:2116: rlung gi dngas ma srog rlung /
NK131(do)006:2117: dngas ma'i dngas ma ni kun gzhi'i rnam shes so //
NK131(do)006:2119: rtsa ba thig le 'chad pa'i skabs su /
NK131(do)006:2120: thig le'i don ni thig ces pa /
NK131(do)006:2121: ti la ka bde ba chen po snying po'i don te /
NK131(do)006:2122: le ni snang ba du mar brdal ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:2123: zhes b+ai ma las gsungs so /
NK131(do)006:2125: tha mal gyi dus kyi shes pa'i gnas skabs bshad pa'i skabs su /
NK131(do)006:2127: thog ma'i ka dag 'khrul med las //
NK131(do)006:2128: nges pa med pa'i lhun grub gsal //
NK131(do)006:2129: 'khrul pa med pa'i sbag sbog de //
NK131(do)006:2130: ma rig pa ni gsum dag la //
NK131(do)006:2131: shes pa gsal gsal rig rig de //
NK131(do)006:2132: yud tsam phyir 'gyus snang cha las //
NK131(do)006:2133: yul la bdag tu bzung ba'i blos //
NK131(do)006:2134: rkyen bzhi'i dmigs pa ma dag pas //
NK131(do)006:2135: yul drug so so'i snang ba shar //
NK131(do)006:2136: nyon mongs drug gis bdag tu bzung //
NK131(do)006:2137: de nas rims kyis snod bcud kyi //
NK131(do)006:2138: snang pa du ma'i gzugs 'dus pa'o //
NK131(do)006:2139: 'di nyid mi shes byis pa rnams //
NK131(do)006:2140: zo chu bzhin du rgyun mar gnas //
NK131(do)006:2141: so so'i lugs dang tshad len pa'o //
NK131(do)006:2142: zhes mkhas pa chen po b+ai ma las //
NK131(do)006:2143: rdzogs pa chen po'i don bsdus pa'i skabs su gsungs so //
NK131(do)006:2145: lus kyi rtsa 'khor rnams las lha spro ba'i skabs su /
NK131(do)006:2146: spyi bo nas 'jam dpal la sogs pa sku'i dkyil 'khor rnams byung pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2147: mgrin pa nas rta mgrin la sogs pa gsung gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK131(do)006:2148: snying kha nas mi bskyod pa dang yang dag la sogs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK131(do)006:2149: lte ba nas rin po che dang bdud rtsi yon tan gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK131(do)006:2150: gsang gnas nas don grub dang /
NK131(do)006:2151: phur pa 'phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK131(do)006:2152: yan lag rgal tshig las ma mo'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK131(do)006:2153: de'i yan lag du 'jig rten pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2154: drag sngags la sogs pa thams cad kyang /
NK131(do)006:2155: lus kyi rtsa rlung byang chub sems kyi yan lag tu rgyud dang man ngag rnams nas gsungs so //
NK131(do)006:2157: gzhan yang nyid kyis mdzad pa'i bstan bcos mang por /
NK131(do)006:2158: snying ma'i lung mang du drangs te /
NK131(do)006:2159: legs par bshad pa yin no //
NK131(do)006:2160: gzhan yang rta mgrin dregs pa kun sgrol sogs bskyed rims bskor dang /
NK131(do)006:2161: lan gcig kar+m+aara bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK131(do)006:2162: b+ai ma la dang mjal nas rdzogs pa chen po'i tshig don thams cad la /
NK131(do)006:2164: snying tig gi khrid yig la sogs bskyed rdzogs kyi yig sna mang du mdzad cing /
NK131(do)006:2165: rdzogs chen snying tig 'di la pad+ma 'byung gnas nas
NK131(do)006:2166: brgyud pa gcig yod na thang pa la dgongs pa
NK131(do)006:2167: byung pa las / phyis pad+ma las 'brel rtsal gyis gter nas bton nas /
NK131(do)006:2170: rtsa ri bod rlungs su spyan drangs nas bka' lung zhus shing /
NK131(do)006:2171: chos rje rang byung pa nyid kyis u rgyan la
NK131(do)006:2172: zla ba gsum gyi bar du gsol ba btab pas
NK131(do)006:2173: / dngos su mjal nas gnang bas /
NK131(do)006:2174: u rgyan dang nga gnyis kyi bar du brgyud pa gzhan nas 'ded mi dgos gsungs nas /
NK131(do)006:2175: spre'u lo zla ba bcu gnyis pa'i nyer brgyad la bde chen steng du /
NK131(do)006:2176: rtogs ldan ye shes rgyal mtshan /
NK131(do)006:2177: sog po ye shes rgyal mtshan slob dpon rgyal mtshan /
NK131(do)006:2179: sman lung gi sprul sku shag gzhon /
NK131(do)006:2180: 'jam dpal brtson 'grus seng ge rnams la gnang nas /
NK131(do)006:2181: 'di lta bu'i chos nub par 'phangs pas /
NK131(do)006:2182: slob dpon rdo rje dpal gyis gtsang phyogs su dar bar gyis /
NK131(do)006:2183: slob dpon rgyal pas ru 'tshams su dar bar gyis /
NK131(do)006:2184: ye shes rgyal bas kong po dang khams su dar bar gyis /
NK131(do)006:2185: ye shes rgyal mtshan pas hor dang rgya nag la dar bar gyis /
NK131(do)006:2186: sprul sku bas dbus su dar bar gyis /
NK131(do)006:2187: 'jam dpal brtson 'grus seng ges gzhan phan mi yong
NK131(do)006:2188: pas khyodaranga gsol ba thob la nyams su longs gsungs
NK131(do)006:2189: nas / de tsam pa'i thugs rtsis mdzad de /
NK131(do)006:2190: thugs dam gyi gtso bo dang rab mchog mdzad pa la /
NK131(do)006:2191: log shes can min pa snyon du med do /
NK131(do)006:2193: de nas rang byung rdo rjes kyang rdzogs chen pa
NK131(do)006:2194: rnams kyi sems bsrung pa'i phyir du zol gyi kha
NK131(do)006:2197: 'dzam gling rgyan gcig rang byung rdo rje yang dri
NK131(do)006:2198: ma can du byed pa ni cher mi 'tsham pa'i
NK131(do)006:2199: gtam mo // de na rdzogs pa chen po chos min yin pa'i gtan tshigs kyis yin na /
NK131(do)006:2200: rang byung rdo rje sa bon po rnams kyi sems 'dzin pa'i phyir bon dang /
NK131(do)006:2201: mi dge spyod pa thams cad kyi sems 'dzin pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)006:2202: mi dge ba thams cad kyang byed dgos par 'gyur ram /
NK131(do)006:2203: 'o na de rjes chos rje rol pa'i rdo rje 'dzam gling chos kyi grags pas /
NK131(do)006:2205: ye rgyal ba la sogs pa rnams bsten pas /
NK131(do)006:2207: sngags snying ma bka' gter dang /
NK131(do)006:2208: rdzogs chen gyi skor ches mtha' yas pa rnams la /
NK131(do)006:2210: thugs dam gyi yang gtso bor mdzad cing /
NK131(do)006:2211: kar+m+aara bzhugs pa'i dus kyi tshe /
NK131(do)006:2212: bcom ldan 'das kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa mthar thug pa /
NK131(do)006:2213: rdzogs pa chen po thod rgal gyi rtog pa mngon du gyur te /
NK131(do)006:2215: rang sems snying po stong gsal kun tu bzang /
NK131(do)006:2216: gdod nas dag pa rdzogs pa chen po'i dbyings /
NK131(do)006:2217: bzhi lnga'i gdangs la rang gsal kun tu khyab /
NK131(do)006:2218: 'od lnga'i gdangs la rang gsal mnyam par bzhag /
NK131(do)006:2219: gnyis 'dzin rtog bral ma 'khrul dngas ma'i sems /
NK131(do)006:2220: phyi nang snang ba rang grol chos kyi sku /
NK131(do)006:2221: gnas lugs rtogs pa 'bras bu kun tu bzang /
NK131(do)006:2222: ma rtogs sems can 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor 'khyams /
NK131(do)006:2224: rgya yul du byon dus rgyud kyi rgyal po /
NK131(do)006:2225: sgyu 'phrul gsang ba'i snying po 'di nub par 'phangs pas gsungs nas /
NK131(do)006:2226: rgyud 'grel rgyal ba g.yung ston gyis mdzad pa la /
NK131(do)006:2227: cha lag dang bcas pa par du brkos te /
NK131(do)006:2228: stong phrag gcig btab nas rgya hor bod dang mdo dbus kun tu chos sbyin mdzad nas /
NK131(do)006:2231: rgyal ba gang zhig rnam gsum srid pa'i rten 'brel
NK131(do)006:2232: las 'das rnam 'phrul rgya mtsho'i dpal ldan mkha' khyab
NK131(do)006:2234: ces sogs sku gsung thugs kyi sgo nas bstod pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2235: dpal ldan mchog tu gsang ba bla med rdo rje
NK131(do)006:2236: theg pa'i rgyud sde rgya mtsho'i zab don mthar thug
NK131(do)006:2237: gyur pa gsang ba snying po'i rgyud /
NK131(do)006:2238: ji bzhin gsal byed dgongs 'grel du ma'i don ston
NK131(do)006:2239: rnam bshad yon tan rgya mtsho mnga' ba badz+ra shi
NK131(do)006:2241: tshad med kun tu 'gro la phan par bya phyir
NK131(do)006:2242: phun tshogs bsod nams rgya mtsho'i dpal 'bar mi dbang
NK131(do)006:2243: sras po a su ra pa yis /
NK131(do)006:2244: rmad byung lhag bsam mthu yis par du legs bsgrubs
NK131(do)006:2245: chos sbyin dge ba rgya mtsho de yis mkha' mnyam
NK131(do)006:2246: 'gro kun myur du byang chub shog /
NK131(do)006:2248: rdo rje theg pa thams cad kyi mthar thug mdzad pa'o //
NK131(do)006:2249: des na dgas po bka' brgyud pa yang /
NK131(do)006:2250: thams cad kya dpang dang tshad mar mdzad pa la /
NK131(do)006:2251: phyogs zhen dang log rtog ngan pa'i dbang gis kha g.yar nas /
NK131(do)006:2253: dgas po bka' brgyud pa la sogs pa'i gang zag
NK131(do)006:2254: chen po thams cad kyang dri ma can du byas
NK131(do)006:2255: pa'i / rtol med kyi tshig la /
NK131(do)006:2256: rgyus med pa'i blo chung rnams kyang mgo 'khor nas bden 'dzin byed pa ni /
NK131(do)006:2257: snying rje'i gnas yang dag pa'o //
NK131(do)006:2258: shangs pa bka' brgyud pa yang /
NK131(do)006:2259: mkhas grub khyung po nas brtsams te /
NK131(do)006:2263: a seng la sogs pa thams cad kyis kyang /
NK131(do)006:2264: rdzogs chen dang snying ma la thos bsam sgom gsum 'ba' zhig mdzad pa ni /
NK131(do)006:2265: so so'i rnam thar lo rgyus rnams las ches gsal lo //
NK131(do)006:2266: bka' bsdams pa'i bla ma rnams kyang /
NK131(do)006:2267: rdzogs chen snyan rgyud la thugs dam mdzad pa ches mang te /
NK131(do)006:2268: a ro ye shes 'byung gnas zhes bya ba /
NK131(do)006:2269: mdo sde dkon mchog sprin las /
NK131(do)006:2270: dge slong mtha' grol gzhon nu zhes lung bstan pa'i skyes chen de la /
NK131(do)006:2271: thugs kyi sras bzhi yod pa'i /
NK131(do)006:2272: gcig cog ro zangs dkar mdzod khur /
NK131(do)006:2273: des rngo legs pa'i shes rab /
NK131(do)006:2274: des dge slong chos kyi shes rab /
NK131(do)006:2275: gzhan yang bka' bsdams pa'i po to ba /
NK131(do)006:2277: brag dkar ba la sogs ches mang ba rnams kyis /
NK131(do)006:2278: rdzogs chen snyan rgyud la thos bsam sgom gsum mdzad pa 'ba' zhig yin zhing /
NK131(do)006:2279: jo bo rje la snye thang du bod ston rnams kyis /
NK131(do)006:2280: dang po bod du brtsams pa'i bstan bcos 'ga' gzigs phul bas /
NK131(do)006:2281: gzhan la mnyes tshor ma mdzad /
NK131(do)006:2282: a ro ye shes 'byung gnas kyi mdzad pa'i /
NK131(do)006:2283: theg chen rnal 'byor bya ba'i rnying ma'i bstan bcos la mnyes te /
NK131(do)006:2286: don zab la rgya che bar 'dug gsung so //
NK131(do)006:2287: des na bka' bsdams pa'i dam pa rnams kyang dri ma can du ma mdzad gcig /
NK131(do)006:2288: ma gcig labs sgron sogs gcod kyi bka' rgyud rnams kyis kyang /
NK131(do)006:2289: rdzogs chen la thos bsam sgom gsum mdzad pa 'ba' zhig yin te /
NK131(do)006:2291: lhu mkhar gyi dge ga shes spyan ston /
NK131(do)006:2293: skye ston bsod nams bla ma rnams la /
NK131(do)006:2295: rdzogs chen sems sde'i skor rnams gsan /
NK131(do)006:2296: khyad par du skyo ston shag ye'i slob ma /
NK131(do)006:2297: ma gcig nyid kyi a ne mo kher sgom zhig mo bya ba la /
NK131(do)006:2298: mkhas pa nyer lnga'i gdams pa /
NK131(do)006:2299: rdzogs pa chen po nyon mongs gcig chod bya ba la gtso bor nyams len mdzad nas /
NK131(do)006:2300: nyid kyi bstan bcos rnams su yang phyag chen blo las 'das par rig /
NK131(do)006:2301: rdzogs chen ye dag chen por rig /
NK131(do)006:2303: sras kyi yum la bstod par /
NK131(do)006:2304: ma rtag chad kyi mtha' la mi 'jigs pa'i /
NK131(do)006:2305: bka' rdzogs pa chen po'i sgo ru zhugs /
NK131(do)006:2306: theg dman log lta zil gyis gnon /
NK131(do)006:2307: chos lta ba'i phu thag chod pa'i ma /
NK131(do)006:2308: zhes sogs mang bas bka' brgyud de rnams kyang dri ma can du ma sbyor cig /
NK131(do)006:2310: mkhas pa'i dbang po bcom ldan ral gri dang /
NK131(do)006:2312: chos kyi rje kun mkhyen chen po yab sras rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2313: chos rje bu ston yab sras dang /
NK131(do)006:2314: chos rje bsod nams rgyal mtshan la sogs pas /
NK131(do)006:2315: bod du 'gyur ro cog gi bka' bstan bcos rnams bsdus nas /
NK131(do)006:2316: dag ma dag phye ba'i dkar chag rnams nas /
NK131(do)006:2317: rdzogs chen gyi rgyud gzhung thams cad /
NK131(do)006:2318: mi gral nas khyi phyung ba ltar phud pas /
NK131(do)006:2319: rgyud rnams rgyud 'bum du ma tshud mdor na bka' 'gyur /
NK131(do)006:2320: bstan bcos gang yang bstan 'gyur du ma tshud pas /
NK131(do)006:2321: chos ma yin pa'i grangs la btang snyoms su bzhag /
NK131(do)006:2322: bstan pa'i bdag po nya kun dga' dpal gyi kyang 'byam yig btang lo /
NK131(do)006:2325: de la brjod par bya ste /
NK131(do)006:2326: bcom ldan ral gris snying ma'i rgyud phud pa'i bshad pa /
NK131(do)006:2327: bstan rgyan che chung gar yang mi snang zhing /
NK131(do)006:2328: khyad par du rgyud zab mo dpal gsang ba snying po la /
NK131(do)006:2329: mgos lha btsas la sogs pas sgro bkur byas pa de spang bar bya ste /
NK131(do)006:2330: 'di rgyud yang dag yin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK131(do)006:2332: slob dpon b+ai shwa mi tras mdzad par gsang snying gi lung rnams drangs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2333: log pa'i skyon bzhi la sogs pa'i 'gal spong rnams
NK131(do)006:2334: mdzad nas tshad mar sgrubs pa la sus kyang snyon
NK131(do)006:2335: du med do // gud du phud pas skyon che na /
NK131(do)006:2336: dus 'khor 'grel chen rnams phyi nang gang yin ma nges pas /
NK131(do)006:2337: po ti gud du byas ces gsungs mod /
NK131(do)006:2338: dbus pa blo gsal gyis bka' 'gyur bstan 'gyur gnyis ka'i dkar chag du /
NK131(do)006:2339: snying ma'i rgyud 'grel rnams phud pa'i bshad pa med cing /
NK131(do)006:2345: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud snga phyi gsum la sogs
NK131(do)006:2346: pa rnams 'gyur byang dang bcas pa bzhengs nas dri
NK131(do)006:2347: ma med pa'i dkar chag kyang mdzad do //
NK131(do)006:2348: rgyud tshad ma yin min sogs kyi dbye ba /
NK131(do)006:2349: pho brang zhi ba 'od sogs kyis mdzad zin kyang /
NK131(do)006:2351: chos kyi mtshan nyid gang la'ang yod med dag /
NK131(do)006:2352: mi shes mthong ba med phyir rgyu bzhi yis /
NK131(do)006:2353: rnam dbye smra ba'i kha ni bdud kyis phye /
NK131(do)006:2354: chos la nyes smod thub pa'i gzhung las bkag /
NK131(do)006:2355: ces 'byung ba'i don la bsams nas dbye ba ma gsungs so //
NK131(do)006:2356: des na skyes bu dam pa de dag kyang chon
NK131(do)006:2357: ma'i grogs ltar phyin ci log la ma sbran gcig
NK131(do)006:2358: / chos rje kun mkhyen chen pos /
NK131(do)006:2359: thog mar bla ma byang chub seng ge dang /
NK131(do)006:2360: sras kyi mtho bo stag bsham pa tshul khrims bzang po'i drung du /
NK131(do)006:2361: dpal yang dag he ru ka dang /
NK131(do)006:2362: rdo rje phur pa la sogs pa sngags snying ma'i dbang rgyud sgrub skor mang du gsan nas /
NK131(do)006:2366: chos rje yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK131(do)006:2368: mkhas mchog kyi ston 'jam dbyangs rnams la /
NK131(do)006:2369: sngags snying ma bka' gter gyi sgrub skor dang /
NK131(do)006:2370: rdzogs chen gyi skor mtha' yas pa zhig gsan nas /
NK131(do)006:2371: mkhas par mkhyen cing thugs nyams su bzhes khyad par mkhas mchog kyi ston la /
NK131(do)006:2372: grub thob 'dar phyar gyis gter nas bton pa'i rta mgrin yang gsang khros pa gsan nas /
NK131(do)006:2373: thugs dam du mdzad pas rta mgrin dang /
NK131(do)006:2374: u rgyan gu ru gnyis kyi zhal gzigs te /
NK131(do)006:2375: sku 'bum 'dzam gling rgyan gyi srog shing yang u rgyan gyis btsugs par gzigs /
NK131(do)006:2376: sku 'bum gyi lha khang brgya rtsa brgyad kyi lha khang gcig gu ru'i lha khang dang //
NK131(do)006:2377: gcig rta mgrin zhal gzigs kyi lha khang du mdzad /
NK131(do)006:2378: rta mgrin de nyid bu chen gzhan la yang spel te /
NK131(do)006:2384: nya kun dga' rnams kyis kyang thugs dam mdzad cing /
NK131(do)006:2385: sgrub dkyil gyi yig sna yang mang du mdzad /
NK131(do)006:2387: gu ru chos dbang gnyis kyi gter kha gong 'og ces gsungs shing /
NK131(do)006:2388: khyad par du gu ru chos dbang ni /
NK131(do)006:2389: grub pa brnyes pa'i skyes chen dam pa zhes /
NK131(do)006:2390: bstod bskur dang basngagasa pa chen po mdzad pa rnams /
NK131(do)006:2391: nyid kyi bka' 'bum rnams su gsal mod /
NK131(do)006:2392: des na chos rje kun mkhyen chen pos bka' 'gyur
NK131(do)006:2393: bstan 'gyur gnyis bzhengs pa'i gtam yang mi snang bas
NK131(do)006:2394: / phud pa sogs kyi tshig ni phyon ma'i grogs dang 'dra ba ma yin nam /
NK131(do)006:2395: de'i slob ma jo nang lots+tshasa rgyud 'bum gcig bzhengs 'dug pa de'i nang du ni /
NK131(do)006:2396: snying ma phud pa'i gtam mi snang la /
NK131(do)006:2397: khyad par du phur pa'i rgyud /
NK131(do)006:2399: gsar ma'i phyag rdor gyi skor mang po dang /
NK131(do)006:2401: bde mchog ra li nyer bzhi po'i rgyud thams cad rdzun ma yin zhes phud par snang la /
NK131(do)006:2406: zhang ston bsod grags sogs bu chen rnams kyis kyang /
NK131(do)006:2407: rdzogs chen dang snying ma rnams la thos bsam sgom gsum mdzad pa ma gtogs pa /
NK131(do)006:2408: phud pa la sogs pa rnams ni lho nub bden bral gyi tshig go /
NK131(do)006:2409: des na kun mkhyen yab sras kyis kyang chos gral nas phud ces pa /
NK131(do)006:2410: de yab sras kyang phyon ma'i grogs ltar ma sbran gcig /
NK131(do)006:2411: chos rje bu ston gyis kyang /
NK131(do)006:2412: nyid kyi mes po la rdzogs chen sems sde'i skor dang /
NK131(do)006:2413: mdo sgyu 'phrul la sogs bka' gter mang po gsan nas /
NK131(do)006:2414: bsnyen sgrub kyang mang du mdzad cing /
NK131(do)006:2415: kho bo'i bla ma thar lo nyi rgyal mtshan dang /
NK131(do)006:2418: bsam yas sogs nas rgya dpe rnyed pas /
NK131(do)006:2420: kho bos ni kha gcig btang snyoms su bzhag gsung mod /
NK131(do)006:2421: de las gzhan pa'i snying ma la skyon can du gzigs nas /
NK131(do)006:2422: bka' 'gyur bstan 'gyur gnyis nas phud pa'i gtam gud du mi snang zhing /
NK131(do)006:2423: gsar ma'i rgyud mang po la the tshom gyi gzhi dang /
NK131(do)006:2424: rgyud rdzun mar byas nas phud pa ni mang mod cing /
NK131(do)006:2425: rdo rje phur pa'i rgyud ni khyad par nang du bzhengs shing /
NK131(do)006:2426: 'di lta bu'i ngan brjod byas pa ni ma mthong zhing ma tshor bas /
NK131(do)006:2427: de yang dri ma can du ma mdzad gcig /
NK131(do)006:2428: chos rje bsod nams rgyal mtshan gyis bstan 'gyur bzhengs kyang /
NK131(do)006:2429: de'i na nga nas snying ma'i bstan bcos rnams phud pa'i gtam mi snang bas /
NK131(do)006:2431: chos rje pa yang phyon ma'i grogs ltar ma sbran zhig /
NK131(do)006:2432: bstan pa'i bdag po nya kun dgas kyang /
NK131(do)006:2433: bstan pa la dgongs nas 'byam yig btang ba ngo mtshar che ste /
NK131(do)006:2434: de bas kyang dus 'khor la sogs pa sems 'grel skor gsum po thams cad bka' min dang /
NK131(do)006:2435: chos min du sgrub pa 'di la 'byam yig gcig
NK131(do)006:2436: btang nas dag ma dag gi shan mi dbye ba
NK131(do)006:2438: yid gnyis su gyur pas dgongs mdzod cig /
NK131(do)006:2439: da lta bod 'dir bsgrigs pa'i rgyud 'bum dang /
NK131(do)006:2440: bstan 'gyur rnams ni phal cher phyogs zhen can kha
NK131(do)006:2441: gcig gis ni phyogs re ba re bris pa yin
NK131(do)006:2442: / kha gcig gis so sor gud gud du bris /
NK131(do)006:2443: phyogs med ris med kyi dad pa can /
NK131(do)006:2444: shes rab gzu bor gnas pa thams cad dang /
NK131(do)006:2445: gzhan yang sa skya pa yab sras rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2446: sngon gyi bka' bsdams pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2448: mtshal 'brug la sogs dgas po bka' brgyud pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2452: dbus pa blo gsal la sogs pa rnams kyis /
NK131(do)006:2453: snying ma'i bka' bstan bcos rnams /
NK131(do)006:2454: khyad par gser dngul gyis bzhengs pa mang mod /
NK131(do)006:2455: gzhan yang phyogs zhen can gyis bsgrigs pa'i rgyud 'bum dang /
NK131(do)006:2456: dkar chags rnams su med pas /
NK131(do)006:2457: gcig shos sun 'byin pa ni rtol med pa'i rdzun tshig go /
NK131(do)006:2458: phyogs zhen can rnams kyi rgyud 'bum kha gcig dang /
NK131(do)006:2459: bstan 'gyur kha gcig tu ma tshud cing phud pa sogs rnams chos min du byed na /
NK131(do)006:2460: dus 'khor rgyud 'grel rgyud phyi ma dang bcas pa /
NK131(do)006:2464: bde mchog nam mkha' dang mnyam pa /
NK131(do)006:2465: bde mchog gi bshad rgyud ra li nyi shu rtsa bzhi /
NK131(do)006:2467: kyee rdo rje'i gsang ba mdzod rgyud /
NK131(do)006:2469: gnyis med rnam rgyal gshin rje sra khog rtsa snang ba /
NK131(do)006:2471: phyag rdor gyi gsang bstan drag po me lce /
NK131(do)006:2472: rdo rje snying po lce dbab /
NK131(do)006:2475: gtum mo thugs kyi gsang rgyud phyi ma'i phyi ma dang bcas pa sogs dang /
NK131(do)006:2476: gzhan yang ches mang ba rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2477: zhi byed kyi mdo rgyud rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2478: gzhan yang bstan 'gyur kha gcig tu /
NK131(do)006:2479: gser chos bzhi la sogs shangs pa bka' rgyud kyi gdams pa rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2480: bka' babs snyan rgyud bzhi la sogs pa dam pa'i zhi byed kyi gzhung thams cad dang /
NK131(do)006:2481: mar pa lots+tsha'i bde mchog snyan rgyud kyi skor rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2482: gzhan yang chos mang zhing mang ba ma tshud cing /
NK131(do)006:2483: rgyud gzhung de dag thams cad kyang /
NK131(do)006:2484: kha gcig yang dag tu byed /
NK131(do)006:2485: kha gcig gis lhad can du byed /
NK131(do)006:2486: kha gcig gis rdzus mar byed /
NK131(do)006:2487: kha gcig gis the tshom gyi gzhir mdzad pas /
NK131(do)006:2488: de rnams gang bden pa yin /
NK131(do)006:2489: khyung po'i gser chos bzhi'i gzhung rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2491: snyan rgyud kyi gzhung rnams kyang /
NK131(do)006:2492: chos log tu byed dam legs par dgongs shig /
NK131(do)006:2493: gzhan yang grub chen gser stong ba /
NK131(do)006:2496: rdzogs chen la thugs dam mdzad pa 'ba' zhig yin zhing /
NK131(do)006:2503: snyan rgyud kyi 'phrang gsal ba rdzogs chen gsang bskor sogs /
NK131(do)006:2504: rgyud pa sde bzhi'i skor rnams gsan nas /
NK131(do)006:2507: chos rje kun spangs chen pos sngags snying ma yang
NK131(do)006:2508: phur la sogs kyi dbang rgyud man ngag mtha' yas
NK131(do)006:2509: pa dang / khyad par rdzogs chen gyi skor mtha' dag cig la thugs sbyong mdzad nas /
NK131(do)006:2511: de nas grub chen yu mo'i sras mo /
NK131(do)006:2512: ma gcig sprul sku jo 'bum la /
NK131(do)006:2513: rgyal thabs spyi blugs kyi dbang zhus /
NK131(do)006:2514: rdzogs chen sems klong gi skor mtha' yas pa'i rgyud gzhung /
NK131(do)006:2515: man ngag thams cad gsan nas thugs nyams su bzhes /
NK131(do)006:2516: de rjes jo nang pa rim par byon pa /
NK131(do)006:2521: kun mkhyen chen po yab sras rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2523: kun mkhyen gangs pa la sogs pa thams cad kyis kyang thugs nyams su bzhes shing /
NK131(do)006:2524: snying por mdzad pa la sus snyon du yod /
NK131(do)006:2526: da lta rdzogs chen gyi rgyud gzhung 'di thams cad kyi nang nas brtsom pa'i yong tshul dang /
NK131(do)006:2527: tshig don gyi rnam bzhag la mkhas pa gang gis mthong kyang /
NK131(do)006:2528: yid ches pa'i rgyud gzhung gcig kyang med lo /
NK131(do)006:2531: de la gong du bshad pa ltar /
NK131(do)006:2532: sa skya pa yab sras rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2536: zhi gcod bka' rgyud pa'i mkhas grub rnams las lhag pa'i /
NK131(do)006:2537: tshig don gyi rnam bzhag la mkhas pa 'ga' da lta rnyed las che /
NK131(do)006:2539: 'on kyang ngan sar mi sdod par /
NK131(do)006:2540: chos thams cad kyi zab shos dang /
NK131(do)006:2545: dus 'khor sogs bla med kyi rgyud dang /
NK131(do)006:2546: de dag gi snying po'i don phyag rgya chen po /
NK131(do)006:2547: sbyor drug rim lnga sogs thams cad /
NK131(do)006:2548: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga bya ba theg pa dman pa yin /
NK131(do)006:2549: de rnams kyi gong na lung a nu yo ga bya ba /
NK131(do)006:2552: dgongs pa 'dus pa la sogs pa mdo bcu bzhi rnams yod /
NK131(do)006:2553: de thams cad kyi gong du theg pa rim pa dgu'i yang rtse /
NK131(do)006:2554: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga 'di yod pa yin /
NK131(do)006:2555: 'di'i thams cad na gsang 'dus la sogs pa phyag rgya chen po'i chos skor thams cad /
NK131(do)006:2556: gzhob rdog pas bardzisa pa dang 'dra ste snying po med zer nas /
NK131(do)006:2557: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa'i snying po dam pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2558: rab phul du gyur pa rnal 'byor bla na med
NK131(do)006:2559: pa'i rgyud sde phyag rgya chen po'i lam thams cad
NK131(do)006:2560: khyad du gsod / theg chen gyi mdo sde thams
NK131(do)006:2561: cad kyang lta ba rdzogs chen la ma sleb pas
NK131(do)006:2562: khyad du gsod / / lta ba dman zer nas khyad du gsod lo /
NK131(do)006:2565: de la brjod par bya ste spyir 'di lta bu'i
NK131(do)006:2566: rnam dbye dang brjod tshul byed pa rdzogs chen pa'i
NK131(do)006:2568: rdzogs chen la brjod 'dod kyi dbang gis /
NK131(do)006:2569: rang nyid kyis ci dran dran bris pa yin na shin tu nas bden du chug ste /
NK131(do)006:2571: snying ma'i chos tshul rnams la log par rtog pa'i /
NK131(do)006:2572: mkhas rlom can gyi blun pa smra mkhas pas can dang mtshungs so /
NK131(do)006:2573: spyir du theg pa dman pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2574: ma rdzogs pa rnams kyis kyang /
NK131(do)006:2575: khyed de ltar thams cad theg pa dman pa yin
NK131(do)006:2576: pas ngan par sdod pa yin zer ba ma lags
NK131(do)006:2577: sam / de lta min na theg pa thams cad
NK131(do)006:2578: kyis rang rang gi che ba'i yon tan brjod pa
NK131(do)006:2579: sam / lugs yin pas / a ti yo ga
NK131(do)006:2580: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse yin par brjod
NK131(do)006:2583: snying ma ba don 'thun rnams kyis ni /
NK131(do)006:2584: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs chen gsum /
NK131(do)006:2585: gang zag dbang po rab la dgongs /
NK131(do)006:2587: gsang ba 'dus pa sogs bskyed pa ma h+aa yo
NK131(do)006:2588: ga bya ba theg pa dman pa yin ces zer
NK131(do)006:2589: ba'i / rdzogs chen pa gcig byung ma byung the tshom za bas /
NK131(do)006:2590: de yang khyed rang gi rdzun tshig du ma gyur cig go /
NK131(do)006:2593: pha rgyud ma rgyud gnyis med dang gsum du byed mod /
NK131(do)006:2594: de mtshungs 'dir yang bla med la /
NK131(do)006:2595: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs chen gsum du phye ba la 'gal ba sus 'tshol /
NK131(do)006:2597: gang gi mtshan yang dag par brjod pa mi shes pa des /
NK131(do)006:2598: dus kyi 'khor lo mi shes pa de thams cad
NK131(do)006:2599: 'khor ba pa ste rdo rje 'dzin pa'i lam dang
NK131(do)006:2601: des na rnal 'byor pa yang blo'i khyad kyis /
NK131(do)006:2602: gong ma gong ma rnams kyis gnod /
NK131(do)006:2604: yin lugs kyi don la khyad med kyang /
NK131(do)006:2605: chos so so'i che ba'i rang skad brjod pa la skyon ma mthong te /
NK131(do)006:2606: dam pa rgya gar la sogs pas kyang /
NK131(do)006:2607: a ti yo ga theg pa'i yang rtse yin par gsungs pa gong du brjod pa ltar ro //
NK131(do)006:2608: lung a nu yo ga bya ba bka' brgyad dang
NK131(do)006:2609: bde gshegs 'dus pa sogs yin zer ba'i rdzogs chen
NK131(do)006:2611: gal srid yod na de ni ma nges bzhin du smra ba ste /
NK131(do)006:2612: 'di ni rdzogs chen 'gags pa'i mkhas rlom can /
NK131(do)006:2613: tshig gi brjod tshul tsam la'ang rmongs pa'i gang zag
NK131(do)006:2614: de rnams dang gnyis su med cing tha mi thad
NK131(do)006:2615: do // gsang 'dus sogs phyag chen gzhob rdog pas bardzisa pa dang 'dra zer nas /
NK131(do)006:2616: bstan pa'i snying po rnal 'byor bla med kyi rgyud sde dang /
NK131(do)006:2617: phyag chen gyi lam khyad du gsod pa'i rdzogs chen pa de yang /
NK131(do)006:2618: rdzogs pa chen po chos min du sgrub pa rnams dang khyad med do //
NK131(do)006:2619: spyir yang 'di dag rnams rang rang gi brjod 'dod
NK131(do)006:2620: kyi dbang gis rdzun dang smyon rtol byed pa'i tshig
NK131(do)006:2621: yin las che / de min drang po yin na /
NK131(do)006:2622: rdzogs chen gyi gzhung khungs ma gang nas bshad bstan du gsol /
NK131(do)006:2624: gsang sngags la zhugs nas so thar la rtsis su byas na /
NK131(do)006:2625: theg dman du ltung ba yin zer ba dang /
NK131(do)006:2629: spyir de lta bu dang 'thun pa'i tshig byung pas nyes na /
NK131(do)006:2630: gdul bya'i skye bo nges pa dang bral ba rnams la /
NK131(do)006:2631: rang gi sems kyi bsam pas /
NK131(do)006:2632: skye ba 'di nyid la sangs rgyad nyis kyi 'bras bu gter ba /
NK131(do)006:2634: nges pa dang bral ba ni /
NK131(do)006:2635: nyan thos pa'i mchog gi sdom pa /
NK131(do)006:2636: 'dod pa spyod pa spangs pa ste /
NK131(do)006:2637: de'i nges pa dang bral ba sems kyi bsam pa 'dod pa la spyod par 'dod pa'o //
NK131(do)006:2638: zhes dri med 'od las gsungs shing /
NK131(do)006:2639: gzhan yang bir+wa pas dam pa la gdams pa gnang zhing /
NK131(do)006:2640: 'dul ba bsrungs pas mi grol gsungs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2641: bram ze chen po dang mee tri pa la sogs kyis kyang de ltar gsungs shing /
NK131(do)006:2643: 'dul ba'i sde snod la sogs chos rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2644: rang rang gzhung dang grub pa'i mtha' yis ni /
NK131(do)006:2645: 'od gsal phyag rgya chen po mthong mi 'gyur /
NK131(do)006:2646: zhe 'dod byung pas 'od gsal ma mthong bsgribs /
NK131(do)006:2647: rtog pa'i bsrung sdoms dam tshig don la nyams /
NK131(do)006:2648: shes gsungs pa de rnams kyis kyang /
NK131(do)006:2649: sde snod gsum gyi lam thams cad khyad du bsad par 'gyur ram /
NK131(do)006:2650: des na lta sgom spyod gsum la dor ba'i gsung
NK131(do)006:2651: rnams chos min du sgrub pa ni ches cher rnam
NK131(do)006:2653: khungs pa rdo shing brag las byung pa shas che zhing /
NK131(do)006:2654: sgrub rgyud dang snyan rgyud gnyis ka chad /
NK131(do)006:2657: chos dag man ngag gter du sbas nas phyung pas /
NK131(do)006:2658: snyan brgyud la sogs chad par 'dod na /
NK131(do)006:2659: mar rngog la sogs pa'i brgyud pa dang bcas pa
NK131(do)006:2660: rnams kyi rgyud rnams rdo rje snying pos bsdus te
NK131(do)006:2661: / glegs bam du byas nas u rgyan du mkha' 'gro ma rnams la gtad pa /
NK131(do)006:2662: rgya rim pa bdun gyis btab te sbas nas bzhugs pa la /
NK131(do)006:2663: klu sgrub kyis lkugs par rdzus te ke'u tshang gi phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:2664: shing gdug pa'i tshal gyi nang rol du man+dala dbul zhing bsdad pas /
NK131(do)006:2666: 'di gus pa che ba gcig 'dug pas /
NK131(do)006:2667: nang du mchod pa byed du chug zer nas /
NK131(do)006:2668: nang du btang pa dang slob dpon gyis mchod pa byas so /
NK131(do)006:2669: de nas dus gzhan zhig gi tshe /
NK131(do)006:2670: mkha' 'gro ma rnams yengs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2671: he badz+ra gur gdan bzhi sogs rnams phyug te /
NK131(do)006:2672: snyug dong du bcug nas glo skar la phyi rol du 'phangs pas /
NK131(do)006:2673: sgo dang rol mo rnams las sgra rang 'khrol du byung pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2675: lkug pas chos rkus so zer nas btsal bas ma rnyed /
NK131(do)006:2676: de nas slob dpon gyis snyug dong khyer te bros pas /
NK131(do)006:2677: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis bsdas kyang ma zin te /
NK131(do)006:2678: khyod klu grub yin te 'ong bas /
NK131(do)006:2679: skal ldan rnams la byin gcig zer ba la /
NK131(do)006:2680: slon dpon gyis dar bar mdzad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2681: kha gcig gis lwa ba pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2683: rta mchog b+ai na pa rnams kyis phyung bar 'dod pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2684: ma h+aa ma ya'i rgyud ku kur ri pas /
NK131(do)006:2685: u rgyan nas gter nas phyung te rkus stabs kyis bros 'ongs pa la /
NK131(do)006:2686: ye shes dang 'jig rten gyi mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis ded par bshad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2687: gzhan yang gter nas phyung par bshad pa'i chos mtha' yas pa yod par snang bas /
NK131(do)006:2688: rang rang gi chos dang bla ma rgyud pa la
NK131(do)006:2689: bkur pa 'debs pa'i tshig tu mi 'gro 'am soms
NK131(do)006:2690: shig / dam pa'i zhi byed kyi chu klung rol pa'i mdo rgyud rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2691: chu klung chen po'i gsang rgyud /
NK131(do)006:2692: mkha' 'gro ma'i gsang rgyud la sogs pa rnams /
NK131(do)006:2693: dur khrod dpal gyi rgyu skar rol pa na /
NK131(do)006:2694: mkha' 'gro ma'i gsang mdzod sgo nyis rim bcad pa'i nang na /
NK131(do)006:2695: lcags kyi sgrom bu dgu gling nas bton te yi ger btab par bzhed cing /
NK131(do)006:2696: da lta bod du yang zhi byed kyi mdo rgyud phal che ba rnams /
NK131(do)006:2697: lho brag ban pa na gter du sbas nas yod par /
NK131(do)006:2698: zhi byed pa chen po rnams gsungs pas /
NK131(do)006:2699: de dag kyang bsgrub brgyud chad dam /
NK131(do)006:2700: gzhan yang phyag rgya chen po sems khrid /
NK131(do)006:2701: dgas po lha rje gter du sbas nas /
NK131(do)006:2702: dung mtsho ras pas bton pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2703: rje btsun ras chung pas n+aa ro pan chen gyis ro snyoms skor drug rnams /
NK131(do)006:2704: lho brag mkhar chu'i brag rgan mo 'dzum shor 'dra ba'i nang na /
NK131(do)006:2705: gnubs nam mkha' snying po'i zhabs rjes kyi byang shar 'tshams su sbas pa /
NK131(do)006:2706: phyis gtsang pa rgya ras kyis gter nas bton te dar bar mdzad pa yin mod cing /
NK131(do)006:2707: de yang ti pu pa'i zhal nas //
NK131(do)006:2708: rgya gar 'o ma'i rgya mtsho nas //
NK131(do)006:2709: gdams ngag mar gyi snying po 'di //
NK131(do)006:2710: rgyud sde rnams na gab nas yod //
NK131(do)006:2711: pan+di ta yis long gtam byas //
NK131(do)006:2712: grub thob rnams kyi khong snying yin //
NK131(do)006:2713: dur khrod 'grim pa'i go cha yin //
NK131(do)006:2714: ku su lu yi sman sbyor yin //
NK131(do)006:2715: n+aa ro pan chen gyi rtogs pa yin //
NK131(do)006:2716: pan+di ta dang ku su lu //
NK131(do)006:2718: snod ldan khyod la bstan pa yin //
NK131(do)006:2719: gdams ngag bshad la dus tshod dgos //
NK131(do)006:2720: da lta bstan pa'i dus min pas //
NK131(do)006:2722: gtad gnyer gyis la gter du sbos //
NK131(do)006:2723: skye ba gsum gyi 'og rol du //
NK131(do)006:2724: blo ldan gang zag len du 'ong //
NK131(do)006:2725: de yi lag du gtod gcig gyis //
NK131(do)006:2726: smon lam thob la sbos shig gsungs /
NK131(do)006:2727: zhes ras chung pa la lung bstan pa ltar mdzad do //
NK131(do)006:2728: des na ro snyoms skor drug rnams kyang /
NK131(do)006:2729: sgrub brgyud snyan brgyud chad par smra'am /
NK131(do)006:2730: de sogs gzhan yang shin tu mang te ma spros so //
NK131(do)006:2731: des na rigs 'dzin gyi sa la gnas pa'i grub
NK131(do)006:2732: chen sangs rgyas gnyis pa lta bu'i pad ma 'byung
NK131(do)006:2733: gnas kyis / dus gsum chags thogs med par mkhyen nas /
NK131(do)006:2734: chos dang gdams pa zab mo'i rnams tshong dus kyi 'o ma ltar 'chal gyis dgongs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2735: gnas dang dus kha gcig gi tshe bstan pa'i snod med pa ltar /
NK131(do)006:2736: phyi ma'i dus kha gcig gi tshe bstan du rung bar dgongs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2737: kha gcig chos la gsar ngas che ba'i phyir du /
NK131(do)006:2738: phyis gsar du byung ba la nan tan gyis 'jug pa ltar byung bas /
NK131(do)006:2739: de lta bu rnams la dgongs nas gter du sbas shing /
NK131(do)006:2740: de nyid 'don pa'i gang zag kyang /
NK131(do)006:2741: phyi rabs kyi skyes bu dam pa /
NK131(do)006:2742: las dang skal bar ldan pa'i mnga' bdag lta bu rnams /
NK131(do)006:2743: lung bstan smon lam dang bcas te sbas pa rnams /
NK131(do)006:2744: phyis las dang skal bar ldan pa'i gang zag de
NK131(do)006:2745: lta bus gter nas phyung te 'gro don mdzad pas
NK131(do)006:2746: / bstan pa yun rin du gnas shing rgyun mi 'chad pa'o //
NK131(do)006:2747: khyad par du mnga' bdag nyang dang /
NK131(do)006:2750: skye ba mang por pad ma 'byung gnas kyis rjes su bzung te /
NK131(do)006:2751: las dang skal bar ldan pa'i rigs ldan yin zhing /
NK131(do)006:2753: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas dang yang yang /
NK131(do)006:2754: dngos dang rmi lam 'od gsal gyi ngang nas mjal zhing /
NK131(do)006:2755: dbang bka' lung rjes gnang dang bcas pa legs par mnos pa yin pas /
NK131(do)006:2756: sgrub brgyud dang snyan rgyud chad pa sogs kyi bkur pa btab pa ni /
NK131(do)006:2757: rang gi bla ma dang chos la yang bkur pa 'debs pa'i snga ltas yin no //
NK131(do)006:2758: chu klung rol pa'i mdo las kyang //
NK131(do)006:2759: nga yi bstan pa chos kyi gzhung //
NK131(do)006:2760: thugs nas thugs kyi gter du sba //
NK131(do)006:2761: yang na sa yi snying por bya //
NK131(do)006:2762: ci phyir mu stegs can mgo rgod //
NK131(do)006:2763: nges don dkrugs par gyur ta re //
NK131(do)006:2764: de phyir chu klung rgyun mi gcod /
NK131(do)006:2767: rgyu dang rgyud kyi rgyal po gang //
NK131(do)006:2768: phyag na rdo rje khyod nyid kyis //
NK131(do)006:2769: gter nas gter du phyung te brtsal /
NK131(do)006:2771: sa rdo las khungs byung zhes ma brjod cig /
NK131(do)006:2773: rdzogs chen la'ang thog mar skyabs 'gro sems bskyed /
NK131(do)006:2774: bar du stong nyid snying rje'i nyams len /
NK131(do)006:2775: tha mar sangs rgyas su bsngo ba smon lam gyis
NK131(do)006:2776: rgyas gdab pa yod pas chos yang dag du mi
NK131(do)006:2778: sangs rgyas pa'i rgyud du bcos pa de rnams ta los bris gsungs so /
NK131(do)006:2780: de ni shin tu nas kyang 'grub ste /
NK131(do)006:2781: dus 'khor du yon tan gyi chos dang ldan pa phyi rol pa'i nang du snang yang /
NK131(do)006:2782: bdag cag gis bsnyen bskur bar bya'o //
NK131(do)006:2784: yul gyi sgra yi don shes na /
NK131(do)006:2785: bcas bcos sgra yis ci zhig bya /
NK131(do)006:2787: don la ston na thog mtha' bar gsum du dge ba'i chos de las lhag pa /
NK131(do)006:2788: rgyud rnam dag du 'dod pa la yang cang yod dam /
NK131(do)006:2790: rdzogs chen la chos log yin par lung bstan pa med zer gyi 'dug ste /
NK131(do)006:2791: de med pas rnam dag du mi 'grub na /
NK131(do)006:2792: bod kyi mdo rgyud 'di tsam zhig grags pa la'ang lung bstan mi rnyed /
NK131(do)006:2793: spyir rang res ma rnyed pas med par yang mi 'grub ces zer mod /
NK131(do)006:2795: de la ma rnyed pas med par mi 'grub ces pa shin tu yin te /
NK131(do)006:2796: de'i rgyu mtshan mdo ting nge 'dzin mchog dam pa nas /
NK131(do)006:2797: ma 'ongs pa na 'byung pa'i chos min gyi bya ba rnams lung bstan pa'i skabs su /
NK131(do)006:2798: ma 'ongs pa'i dus na nga'i dge slong thams cad kyis bya bar ma yin pa /
NK131(do)006:2803: kha na ma tho ba thams cad la brtson pas nyams te /
NK131(do)006:2805: jo bo bla ma d+har+m+aa rak+shi tas kyang /
NK131(do)006:2806: dam chos gtsug lag zhus nas mo bon skyong /
NK131(do)006:2808: thams cad mkhyen pa zhes pa /
NK131(do)006:2809: shes bya thams cad gzigs pa yin na ni /
NK131(do)006:2810: rdzogs chen chos log yin par lung bstan par yang 'thad do /
NK131(do)006:2812: gal te med du chug kyang bod lta bu'i yul
NK131(do)006:2813: re re'i chos log re re nas lung bston gyis
NK131(do)006:2814: ga na lang / chos ma brtags pa gsung ba 'dis chog /
NK131(do)006:2817: de la sangs rgyas kyi mkhyen pas shes bya thams
NK131(do)006:2818: cad chags thogs med par mkhyen pa yin phyin chad
NK131(do)006:2819: / bod lta bu'i yul re re'i chos log lung ston gyis mi lang pa'i dka' las /
NK131(do)006:2820: sangs rgyas la yod pa de yang cher ma 'os /
NK131(do)006:2821: bod lta bu'i yul re re'i chos log lung bstan pas chog mod /
NK131(do)006:2822: yul thams cad du rdzogs chen lta bu'i chos log ci yod /
NK131(do)006:2823: yul thams cad du yod na ni /
NK131(do)006:2824: bod du chos log rdzogs chen brtsams zhes pa'i nges
NK131(do)006:2825: pa 'di 'thad dam soms shig /'jig rten gyi khams
NK131(do)006:2826: thams cad du chos log yod kyang /
NK131(do)006:2827: sangs rgyas spobs pa zad na ma gtogs /
NK131(do)006:2828: de thams cad lung bstan pa la'ang tshegs ci yod /
NK131(do)006:2829: des na mkhas mkhas 'dra ba'i gsung 'di dag rnams kyang blun tshig tsam du zad do //
NK131(do)006:2830: cis kyang chos log yin pa la lung bstan dgos na /
NK131(do)006:2831: rdzogs chen dgag pa'i 'byam yig 'di snyed gcig 'jig
NK131(do)006:2832: rten du grags nang de la lung bstan mi snang
NK131(do)006:2833: bas chos yang dag tu 'grub mod /
NK131(do)006:2834: 'byam yig du dgags pa thams cad don gnas yin cing bden na /
NK131(do)006:2835: 'byam yig kha gcig tu gsar ma'i rgyud gzhung ches mang ba zhig dgag pa rnams la /
NK131(do)006:2836: phyis kyi mkhas grub mang pos tshad mar mdzad mod /
NK131(do)006:2837: cis kyang 'byam yig rnams bden na /
NK131(do)006:2838: dus 'khor rgyud 'grel la sogs pa sems 'grel skor
NK131(do)006:2839: gsum po thams cad khyed kyis kyang chos min du
NK131(do)006:2840: mdzod gcig ste / de rnams kyang kha gcig gis dgags pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:2842: rdzogs chen 'di gsang sngags zab chos su bardzusa nas /
NK131(do)006:2843: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa thams cad khyad du gsod pa'i chos log /
NK131(do)006:2844: phyag rgya chen po'i lam la bar du gcod pa'i bdud chos su 'dug /
NK131(do)006:2847: rdzogs chen gyis phyag rgya chen po'i lam la bar gcod du 'gro bar khyed kyis shes na /
NK131(do)006:2848: rdzogs pa chen po chos min du bsgrub cing spangs pas /
NK131(do)006:2849: phyag rgya chen po'i lam la bar du gcod par ma gyur cig /
NK131(do)006:2851: dpal ldan sa skya pa'i chos brgyud rnams kyang /
NK131(do)006:2852: lam 'bras bu dang bcas la sogs pa /
NK131(do)006:2853: phyag rgya chen po'i khrid rnams kyis tshim par mdzad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2854: dag po bka' brgyud pa rnams kyang /
NK131(do)006:2855: gdams ngag na ro'i chos drug /
NK131(do)006:2856: dam chos phyag rgya chen po /
NK131(do)006:2857: yi dam 'khor lo sdom pas tshim par mdzad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2858: bka' gdams pa rnams kyang a ti sha'i chos tshul
NK131(do)006:2859: dri ma med pa rnams kyi tshim par mdzad pa
NK131(do)006:2860: dang / zhi byed dang gcod yul ba rnams kyang /
NK131(do)006:2861: dam pa'i zhi byed snga phyi bar gsum rnams kyis tshims par mdzad pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2862: theg mchog snying po'i lam phyag rgya chen po'i man ngag sangs rgyas nyid /
NK131(do)006:2863: klu grub yab sras sogs rnams kyis bsgrigs pa'i khrid /
NK131(do)006:2866: grub pa sde bdun sogs zhus shing nyams su len pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2867: mdor na rang gi bka' brgyud gong ma de rnams kyi bsgrub pa'i chos /
NK131(do)006:2870: lo pan gyis bsgyur ngo shes pa de nyams su blangs na chog /
NK131(do)006:2871: gal te gsar du zhu yang /
NK131(do)006:2872: dri med kyi chos rnam dag khungs btsun pa /
NK131(do)006:2875: rdzogs chen gyi rdzun chos la ma brtags par 'jug pa de mi 'thad /
NK131(do)006:2878: khyed kyis tshad mar khas blangs pa'i /
NK131(do)006:2879: rang rang gi bka' brgyud gong mas sgrub pa'i chos
NK131(do)006:2880: dpang du byed pa de rnams la'ang skyon rgyab pa
NK131(do)006:2881: dang / chos rnam dag min par kha rgyab pa
NK131(do)006:2882: tsam gyis chos log du 'gyur na ni shin tu
NK131(do)006:2884: rtog ge ba kha gcig gis srid pa ma mo'i rgyud la brten nas ni /
NK131(do)006:2885: lam 'bras brgyud kyi rdo rje'i tshig rkang byas /
NK131(do)006:2888: bla ma gong ma'i gsung sgros snyan snyan rnams bsdus /
NK131(do)006:2890: sa skya pa rnams kyi brgyud pa rnams kyang chos des tshim mod /
NK131(do)006:2891: bka' brgyud pa'i phyag chen ni /
NK131(do)006:2892: bla med kyi rgyud nas bshad pa'i phyag chen min
NK131(do)006:2893: la rnal 'byor bzhi'i rim pa dang sbyar ba da
NK131(do)006:2894: lta 'di rnams / sems tsam rnam bden pa'i lugs yin pas /
NK131(do)006:2895: de la phyag chen du btags nas nyams su len pa ni ches cher 'khrul pa'o //
NK131(do)006:2897: phyag rgya chen po gcig chod la /
NK131(do)006:2898: sa lam rtsi ba rmongs pa 'khrul /
NK131(do)006:2899: zhes sogs tshig rnams smra ba ni /
NK131(do)006:2900: bdud tshig yin pas rna ba dgab /
NK131(do)006:2904: tshig 'di khyed kyis gzhan la ma 'phel ba gyis /
NK131(do)006:2905: glen gtam du song na 'bri stag dang /
NK131(do)006:2907: rgyud sde bzhi sde snod gsum gang dang yang mi mthun par snang bas /
NK131(do)006:2908: yang dag pa'i lam ma lags snyam gsung mod /
NK131(do)006:2909: des na des tshims par byas pa la yang dgos pa ci yod /
NK131(do)006:2910: gzhan yang mang ste de tsam gyis chog mod /
NK131(do)006:2911: bka' gdams pa'i chos tshul rnams kyang /
NK131(do)006:2912: phal cher gcig sa pan gyi dgags pa sdom gsum rab dbyer gsal mod cing /
NK131(do)006:2914: bka' gdams pa la skyon pa shin tu mang ba dang /
NK131(do)006:2916: dgas po lha rjes bka' gdams pa'i rnam thar bskyangs pa rnams la skyon pas /
NK131(do)006:2917: des tshims kyang yon tan ci yod pa yin /
NK131(do)006:2918: dam pa sangs rgyas kyi zhi byed dang /
NK131(do)006:2920: chags lo sogs kyis bkag ste /
NK131(do)006:2921: chu klung rol pa'i skad dod mi shes pa'i tshul dang /
NK131(do)006:2922: a li ka li'i dbang bskur rnams la /
NK131(do)006:2923: lha med pa'i dbang rgyud sde'i don dang 'gal ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:2925: zhi byed thams cad jo sras rten 'brel dang /
NK131(do)006:2926: zhig po nyi seng gis byas shing /
NK131(do)006:2927: phal cher chos log yin zhes gsungs zhing /
NK131(do)006:2928: sgron gsal chags 'gyur bsham du yang /
NK131(do)006:2929: kha gcig snying ma gter ma zhi byed dang /
NK131(do)006:2930: zhes log pa yin gsungs mod /
NK131(do)006:2932: rtog ge ba sogs kha gcig gis /
NK131(do)006:2933: ma jo smyon ma'i rgyo chos yin /
NK131(do)006:2935: gcod dang zhi byed thams cad rnams /
NK131(do)006:2936: rgyud sde rnams las bshad re kan /
NK131(do)006:2938: zhi gcod bka' brgyud pa de rnams kyis tshims par byas kyang dgos pa ci mthong /
NK131(do)006:2939: rnal 'byor yan lag drug pa la yang mkhas pa kha gcig gis /
NK131(do)006:2940: rtsa ba'i rgyu la e wam gnyis yig med /
NK131(do)006:2941: bsdus pa'i rgyud la 'gal ba du ma mthong /
NK131(do)006:2942: gang nas blangs pa'i khungs kyang mi snang na /
NK131(do)006:2943: 'phyon ma'i bu bzhin 'di la su yid ston /
NK131(do)006:2945: khyed kyi 'di la len byed tshad ma med /
NK131(do)006:2946: chen po rnams las tshad mar ma grags phyir /
NK131(do)006:2947: dus zhabs la sogs tshad ma'i skyes bu min /
NK131(do)006:2949: sbyor ba yin lag drug gi khrid rim kyang /
NK131(do)006:2950: gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud dang 'gal bar snang /
NK131(do)006:2951: de don nyams su blangs pas su zhig grol /
NK131(do)006:2953: dus 'khor la sogs sems 'grel skor gsum /
NK131(do)006:2954: sbyor drug dang bcas pa bkag pas /
NK131(do)006:2955: des tshim par byas pa la yang dgos pa ci mthong ba yin /
NK131(do)006:2957: zhi phyag rdzogs gsum rdzun dang bzhi bsres kyis /
NK131(do)006:2958: la stod dmar po'i thugs kyi nying khu byas /
NK131(do)006:2960: thugs rje chen po dmar po lugs bkag pa dang /
NK131(do)006:2961: gzhan yang mar pa'i bde mchog snyan brgyud sogs kyang bkag cing /
NK131(do)006:2962: nya kun dga' sogs kyis dgas po'i phyag chen sems khrid /
NK131(do)006:2963: mtshal ba'i thabs lam gtum mo rnams dang /
NK131(do)006:2964: gzhan yang gdams pa phal mo che thams cad bkag pas /
NK131(do)006:2965: bod kyi gdams pa rnams la chos log du ma gyur pa /
NK131(do)006:2966: rgya lam na re 'ga' srid tsam mo //
NK131(do)006:2967: gzhan yang ra li nyer bzhi po bkag pa'i shugs la /
NK131(do)006:2968: sa skya pa'i brtag gnyis kyi bshad srol kyang khegs te /
NK131(do)006:2969: sa skya pas ra li'i nam mkha' mnyam rgyud nas /
NK131(do)006:2970: rgyud kyi bshad thabs tshul bzhi sogs drangs nas dpang du byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK131(do)006:2971: des na khyed kyi lugs ltar na bka' rgyud gong ma de rnams kyi chos lugs thams cad kyang /
NK131(do)006:2973: de rnams gang la yang skyon ma rgyab pa mi snang pa'i phyir ro /
NK131(do)006:2974: gsar du zhus kyang de rnams las lhag pa'i dge skyon med de /
NK131(do)006:2975: bod gangs can gyi khrod nas ni rnyed pa ci ltar 'gyur te mi rnyed do //
NK131(do)006:2976: rdzogs chen gyi rdzun chos la zhugs na mi 'thad pa ltar /
NK131(do)006:2977: khyed rang lam 'dir ma zhugs pas gtan du 'tshangs pa lags mod /
NK131(do)006:2978: yang bod du chos yang dag yin par yid ches pa la /
NK131(do)006:2979: sangs rgyas kyis gsungs nges shes pa /
NK131(do)006:2982: rgya gar la sogs pa'i mkhas grub sangs rgyas kyi lung bstan thob pas mdzad ngos shes pa /
NK131(do)006:2983: lo pan gyis bsgyur ngos shes pa /
NK131(do)006:2984: tshig don la mkhas pas dpyad bzod pa gcig dgos gsungs mod /
NK131(do)006:2986: de la khyab pa cung zad med do //
NK131(do)006:2987: 'o na dus 'khor sogs sems 'grel rtsa 'grel rnams sangs rgyas kyiis ma gsungs par ngo shes sam /
NK131(do)006:2988: sham b+ha la la sogs pa'i mkhas grub /
NK131(do)006:2989: sangs rgyas kyi lung bstan thob pas mdzad ngo shes pa ma yin nam /
NK131(do)006:2990: lo pan dam pas bsgyur ngo shes pa ma yin nam /
NK131(do)006:2991: tshig don la mkhas pas dpyad mi bzod pa gcig byung pa yin nam ste /
NK131(do)006:2992: bka' min dang chos min du sgrub pa gsan par ma gyur dam /
NK131(do)006:2994: kha gcig blun dad kyis chog zer ba 'dug ste /
NK131(do)006:2996: blun dad 'ba' zhig gis 'grub pa mi srid /
NK131(do)006:2999: rgyu 'bras kyi rten 'brel ma log na blun dad du ci ltar 'gro ste //
NK131(do)006:3000: gshin rje'i gshed kyi rgyud du //
NK131(do)006:3001: chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK131(do)006:3002: don la the tshom med pa yis //
NK131(do)006:3003: mkhas pa la ni dngos grub nye //
NK131(do)006:3004: yang na blun po dad pa brtan //
NK131(do)006:3005: de la sbyor ba'i dngos grub nye //
NK131(do)006:3006: rtog cing spyod pa'i rtog ge ba //
NK131(do)006:3007: de la sbyor ba'i dngos grub ring //
NK131(do)006:3008: man ngag dam pa bstan byas kyang //
NK131(do)006:3009: slob ma yid gnyis yod gyur na //
NK131(do)006:3010: de la dngos grub ring par bshad //
NK131(do)006:3011: bla mas man ngag sbas byas kyang //
NK131(do)006:3012: bla ma dam pa'i man ngag ces //
NK131(do)006:3013: gces par byas na 'grub par nges /
NK131(do)006:3015: rgyu 'bras kyi rten 'brel ma shes kyang /
NK131(do)006:3016: blun dad brtan na 'grub par gsungs mod /
NK131(do)006:3017: po ta ba'i dpe chos kyi gtam rgyud las kyang /
NK131(do)006:3018: bla ma gcig 'brel ba'i dus su /
NK131(do)006:3019: slob ma gcig gis gdams pa zhus pas /
NK131(do)006:3020: phyag cog pa gcig mdzad nas /
NK131(do)006:3021: ma ra na dz+ha gsungs pas /
NK131(do)006:3022: slob mas phyag skyog pa mdzad pa de phyag rgya dang /
NK131(do)006:3023: ma ra na dz+ha zhes pa de sngags yin snyam nas bsgrubs pas /
NK131(do)006:3024: 'phrin las bzhi grub pa gcig byung par bshad pas /
NK131(do)006:3025: blun dad byed pa rnams la chos spong gi las dang /
NK131(do)006:3026: chos la dbang za ba'i nyes pa de mi phog par snang bas /
NK131(do)006:3027: shin du nas kyang legs so //
NK131(do)006:3028: blo gros can du 'dod pa kha gcig ni /
NK131(do)006:3029: blo the tshom gyi sgrog tu bcug nas /
NK131(do)006:3030: chos dang gang zag dam pa rnams la spu ris 'byed pa 'dis /
NK131(do)006:3031: legs te legs na bstan la phan zhing /
NK131(do)006:3032: nyes te nyes na ngan song gi rgyu sgrub par ma gyur cig go //
NK131(do)006:3034: gang zag thams cad phan tshun sdang shugs kyi dbang gis /
NK131(do)006:3035: chos la yang smod pa de byung ba yin zhing /
NK131(do)006:3036: chos la smod cing skyon brjod pas /
NK131(do)006:3037: chos spong gi las chen po rnams bsags par 'gyur te /
NK131(do)006:3039: 'jam dpal dam pa'i chos spong ba'i las kyi sgrib pa ni 'di 'dra'o //
NK131(do)006:3040: 'jam dpal gang la la de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa'i chos la la ni bzang par 'du shes /
NK131(do)006:3041: la la ni ngan par 'du shes na dam pa'i chos spong ba'o //
NK131(do)006:3042: dam pa'i chos spangs pas de bzhin gshegs pa la bkur pa 'debs pa yin no //
NK131(do)006:3043: dge 'dun la ngan du brjod pa yin no //
NK131(do)006:3045: 'di ni ma rig pa'o zhes zer na dam pa'i chos spong ba'o //
NK131(do)006:3047: chos ni chos ma yin par ston pa'o //
NK131(do)006:3048: zhes zer na chos spong ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:3050: spobs pas chos go ba mi byed do zer na chos spong ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:3051: chos kyi snang ba legs par ma bshad do zer na chos spong ba yin no /
NK131(do)006:3052: khong du ma chud pas tshig du 'gal ba byas so zhes zer na chos spong ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:3053: yi ge'i ming gis de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' la 'jug go zer na chos spong ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:3054: mdo sde dang mdo sder 'gal bar byas so zhes zer na chos spong ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:3056: tshigs su bcad pa 'gal bar byas so zhes zer na chos spong ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:3057: 'di ni legs par gsungs pa'i don la mos shing /
NK131(do)006:3058: la la ma mos so zhes zer na chos spong ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:3060: dkrug ma byed na chos spong ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:3061: kun tu rtog pas smra na chos spong ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:3062: 'di la spyad 'di la ma spyad zer na chos spong ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:3064: 'di ni legs par gsungs pa ma yin no zhes zer na chos spong ba yin no //
NK131(do)006:3065: zhes sogs dang rgyud blar yang /
NK131(do)006:3066: nyon mongs rmongs bdag rnams kyis 'phags pa bkur ba dang /
NK131(do)006:3067: des gsungs chos la brnyas gang de kun zhen ltas byas /
NK131(do)006:3068: des na zhen lta'i dri can de la blo mi sbyar /
NK131(do)006:3069: gos gtsang mtshon gyis rnam bsgyur snum gyis gos pa min /
NK131(do)006:3070: blo gros dman phyir bkar mos bral phyir log pa'i nga rgyal phyir /
NK131(do)006:3071: dam chos 'phongs pa'i sgrib pa'i bdag phyir drang don de nyid nges 'dzin phyir /
NK131(do)006:3072: rnyed pa rkam phyir lta ba'i dbang phyir chos sun 'byin pa brten pa'i phyir /
NK131(do)006:3073: chos 'dzin bsring phyir mos pa dman phyir dgra bcom rnams kyi chos spong byed /
NK131(do)006:3075: sngags kyi tshul zab mo'i dgongs pa dang /
NK131(do)006:3076: dgongs pa'i tshig don ma rtogs par /
NK131(do)006:3077: sgra ji bzhin par bzung nas sangs rgyas kyi bka' ma yin no zhes /
NK131(do)006:3078: bkur pa 'debs pas ni rang nyid nyams par byed de /
NK131(do)006:3079: rnam snang mngon byang gi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK131(do)006:3080: bdag gi sems gnas gtan la ma phebs par 'khrul nas 'di skad du /
NK131(do)006:3081: 'di ni sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa ma yin gyis /
NK131(do)006:3082: 'di dag ni rang bzo can gyis byas pa yin no //
NK131(do)006:3083: zhes zer ba dag 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)006:3085: mi blun po de dag ni 'gro ba gnyis su 'gro bar rig par bya ste /
NK131(do)006:3086: gnyis gang zhes na 'di lta ste /
NK131(do)006:3090: gang zhig chos mchog gtso bo 'di /
NK131(do)006:3091: rgyal bas mchod pa'i chos kyi mdzod /
NK131(do)006:3092: sa stengs mis ni spong byed pa /
NK131(do)006:3093: de ni mnar med dmyal bar 'gro /
NK131(do)006:3095: bde mchog nyung ngu'i rgyud las kyang /
NK131(do)006:3096: mos pa du ma'i sems can la /
NK131(do)006:3097: spyod pa sna tshogs ston mdzad de /
NK131(do)006:3098: sna tshogs tshul gyi gdul bya la /
NK131(do)006:3099: thabs ni sna tshogs ston pa yin /
NK131(do)006:3100: zab mo'i chos ni ston pa la /
NK131(do)006:3101: gal te mos par ma gyur kyang /
NK131(do)006:3102: smod pa dag tu mi bya ste /
NK131(do)006:3103: chos nyid bsam mi khyab rtan bya /
NK131(do)006:3106: ji ltar zab mo'i chos nyams de bzhin mkhas pa rnams kyis me dang ni /
NK131(do)006:3107: mi bzad sbrul gdug gshed ma dang ni thog la'ang shin tu 'jigs mi bya /
NK131(do)006:3108: me sbrul dgra dang rdo rje mes ni srog dang bral ba tsam byed kyi /
NK131(do)006:3109: de las mnar med rnams kyi 'gro ba shin tu 'jigs par 'gro mi 'gyur /
NK131(do)006:3110: gang zhig yang yang sdig grogs bsten pas sangs rgyas ngan sems ldan gyur dang /
