NK131(do)006:3111: gang zhig pha ma dgra bcom gsod dang mchog tshogs 'byed pa'i mi /
NK131(do)006:3112: de yang chos nyid nges par bsams na myur du thar 'gyur gyi /
NK131(do)006:3113: gang zhig yid ni chos la sdang ba de la thar pa gang la yod /
NK131(do)006:3116: shes rab 'chal par gyur pa'i las byas bsags pa de dag gis /
NK131(do)006:3117: sher phyin dang chos spong bar 'gyur te /
NK131(do)006:3118: de dag gis chos spangs pas /
NK131(do)006:3119: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi
NK131(do)006:3120: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid spangs par 'gyur
NK131(do)006:3121: te / rnam mkhyen spangs pas chos brlag par 'gyur zhing /
NK131(do)006:3122: de'i las kyis lo bye ba khrag khrig mang por /
NK131(do)006:3123: sems can dmyal bar bsreg par 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)006:3124: de sems can dmyal ba de nas thar yang /
NK131(do)006:3125: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dmyal ba rnams su skye la /
NK131(do)006:3126: dmyal ba de dag zhig kyang 'jig rten gyi khams
NK131(do)006:3127: gzhan gyi dmyal ba rnams su 'pho zhing sreg go
NK131(do)006:3128: // de nas kyang byol song gi gnas su skye zhing /
NK131(do)006:3129: de dag gi las zad nas rgya la mir skyes kyang /
NK131(do)006:3130: chos spang ba'i las byas pa dang /
NK131(do)006:3135: mi'i skye ba gang du yang /
NK131(do)006:3139: smrig ma mkhan gyi rigs dang /
NK131(do)006:3141: sna dang lce dang rkang lag med pa dang /
NK131(do)006:3144: dkon mchog gsum gyi sgra med par skye ba dang /
NK131(do)006:3147: chos spong bar gyur pa 'di'i gzugs brnyan tsam du yang mi spyod do //
NK131(do)006:3151: 'di la khyed dang bdag cag gis bslab par mi bya ste /
NK131(do)006:3154: 'di ni ston pa'i bstan pa ma yin no /
NK131(do)006:3155: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa ma yin no //
NK131(do)006:3157: de bdag nyid kyang spong la /
NK131(do)006:3158: gzhan la'ang mos pa med par byed cing /
NK131(do)006:3159: bdag gzhan gyi bsam pa nyams par byed pa /
NK131(do)006:3160: bdag gzhan chud gsan par dga' ba /
NK131(do)006:3161: bdag nyid kyang phyir spang bar 'dod la /
NK131(do)006:3163: chos 'jig pa'i las bsags pa de'i gzugs brnyan du yang 'gyur re kan /
NK131(do)006:3165: ngas ni gang zag de lta bur thos par yang bya bar ma gnang na /
NK131(do)006:3166: 'phrad pa dang 'grogs par lta smos kyang ci smos so //
NK131(do)006:3168: mdor na rdo rje theg pa'i zab mo mthar thug pa rnams la /
NK131(do)006:3169: skyon btags nas smad pas chos spong ba'i las bsags
NK131(do)006:3170: shing de'i nyes pa gong du smos pa rnams dang
NK131(do)006:3172: lha mi kun gyis spangs shing yid du mi 'ong pa dang /
NK131(do)006:3173: bsnyen sgrub bzlas pa sogs la 'bad kyang ngag gi nus pa mi yong pa dang /
NK131(do)006:3174: chos bdag mkha' 'gro chos skyong rnams kyis kyang /
NK131(do)006:3175: blo bur du srog 'phrog pa dang /
NK131(do)006:3176: mi 'dod pa sna tshogs steng du 'bab cing /
NK131(do)006:3179: de'i rkyen gyis rdo rje dmyal bar yang 'o rgyal myong bar 'gyur ro //
NK131(do)006:3180: des na nyon mongs kyis kun nas blangs te chos la skyon brjod pas /
NK131(do)006:3181: chos spong gi las chen po bsags pa'i tshig 'di dag gi rjes su /
NK131(do)006:3182: kha phyir ltas kyi blo mig can gzhan kha gcig kyang ri bong tshal ltar /
NK131(do)006:3183: rdzogs pa chen po la sogs pa rdo rje theg
NK131(do)006:3184: pa'i chos zab rgyas can rnams la smod pa ni
NK131(do)006:3185: shin tu yang rigs pa ma yin te /
NK131(do)006:3186: gong du brjod pa rnams la rtog par bya'o //
NK131(do)006:3187: gzhan yang rdzogs chen sogs sngags snying ma la khyad
NK131(do)006:3188: par 'phags pa'i che ba drug yod par gsungs rong
NK131(do)006:3190: dang po spyan 'dren yon bdag gis che ba ni /
NK131(do)006:3191: mnga' bdag me dbon rnam gsum 'phags pa rig gsum mgon po'i sprul pas spyan drangs pa yin la /
NK131(do)006:3192: da lta gang zag skya ser res yon bdag byas nas bskur ba dang mi 'dra gsungs mod /
NK131(do)006:3193: phyag bzhes gtsug lag gi khyad par kyi che ba ni /
NK131(do)006:3194: sngon dpal gyi bsam yas dang /
NK131(do)006:3195: chos 'khor stod smad du gtan la phab pa yin la /
NK131(do)006:3196: da lta'i dgon phug cag cogare dang ma 'dra /
NK131(do)006:3197: bsgyur byed lots+tsha'i khyad par gyi che ba ni /
NK131(do)006:3198: sngon pa gor bee ro tsa na dang /
NK131(do)006:3199: ka cog rnam gnyis la sogs pa sprul pa'i lots+tsha bas bsgyur pa'i chos yin la /
NK131(do)006:3200: da lta'i lots+tsha ba kha gcig kun dgun bal yul du bsdad /
NK131(do)006:3201: dbyar mang yul du don nas /
NK131(do)006:3202: sngon gyi mkhas pa'i 'gyur la rang bzo'i bcos sna tshogs byed pa dang mi 'dra gsungs /
NK131(do)006:3203: pan+di ta'i khyad par gyi che ba ni /
NK131(do)006:3204: sngon gyi pan+di ta pad+ma 'byung gnas /
NK131(do)006:3207: bi ma la mi tra la sogs /
NK131(do)006:3208: rigs 'dzin gyi sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpas spyan drangs pa'i chos yin la /
NK131(do)006:3209: da lta'i pan+di ta kha cig lto ma phyid par /
NK131(do)006:3210: bod du gser mtshol la yongs pa'i bzang sprang tsho gcig dang mi 'dra /
NK131(do)006:3211: zhu rten me tog gi khyad par gyis che ba ni sngon gser phye bre la mjal /
NK131(do)006:3212: gser gla ba'i bslud bu bkang nas phul /
NK131(do)006:3213: gser rta khal dang drel khal du phul nas zhus pa'i chos yin /
NK131(do)006:3214: da lta mchan khung nas gser zho re re gnyis
NK131(do)006:3215: gnyis nyug nyug byas nas zhus pa dang mi 'dra
NK131(do)006:3216: / brjod bya chos kyi khyad par gyi che ba ni /
NK131(do)006:3217: sngon sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa gra ma nyams pa'i dus su /
NK131(do)006:3218: sprul pa'i lo chen rnams kyis bka' 'gyur ba med par gtan la phab pas /
NK131(do)006:3219: shes bya dngos po'i 'dug tshul gtan la 'bebs shing /
NK131(do)006:3220: de rtogs par byed pa'i thabs du mas brgyan pa'i chos dang /
NK131(do)006:3221: dus da lta'i lots+tsha ba rdzun po chos sngon mkhas pa'i 'gyur la bcos ma sna tshogs byed /
NK131(do)006:3222: sangs rgyas kyi gsung dang bla ma'i bka' la ra chod byas nas /
NK131(do)006:3223: mi res chos re bcos te cig skyon gcig la 'gel /
NK131(do)006:3224: pha dpe la bu dpe mi stub pa'i chos dang mi 'dra ste khyad par che zhes /
NK131(do)006:3225: rong pa chos bzang gis gsungs so //
NK131(do)006:3226: des na rgya bod gnyis char du byon pa'i mkhas
NK131(do)006:3227: grub sa skya pa la sogs pa ches mang ba
NK131(do)006:3229: dpang dang tshad mar byed pa'i sngags snying ma rdzogs chen dang bcas pa rnams sun 'byin nas /
NK131(do)006:3230: chos spong gi las bsags pa'i nyes pa dang /
NK131(do)006:3231: rnam smin ni gong du brjod pa ltar mtha' yas pas /
NK131(do)006:3232: zab mo'i chos ni ston pa la /
NK131(do)006:3233: gal te mos par ma gyur kyang /
NK131(do)006:3234: smod pa dag tu mi bya ste /
NK131(do)006:3235: zhes pa'i don dran par byas nas /
NK131(do)006:3236: chos spong ba'i las la bag yod par byos shig /
NK131(do)006:3238: rang byung nyid kyi don dam de /
NK131(do)006:3239: dad pa nyid nas rtogs bya ba /
NK131(do)006:3240: ces pa ltar rgyal ba'i gsung rabs mtha' yas pa rnams la /
NK131(do)006:3241: phyogs zhen dang zhen lta'i dri ma spangs te /
NK131(do)006:3242: gzu bor gnas pa'i blos phyogs med ris med kyi sgo nas nyams su blangs zhing /
NK131(do)006:3243: gal te nyams su len pa mi lcogs kyang /
NK131(do)006:3244: thams cad la phyogs ris spangs pa'i dad pa chen
NK131(do)006:3245: po bskyed na thabs mkhas pa chen por 'gyur ro
NK131(do)006:3246: // de lta min na bod yul du dar ba'i
NK131(do)006:3247: dam pa'i chos phal cher la skyon ma bkal ba
NK131(do)006:3248: // dang / sun ma phyung pa mi snang zhing /
NK131(do)006:3249: phan tshun rdza rdabs pa ltar byas pa snang bas /
NK131(do)006:3250: tshul mthun gyi skyes bu rnams tsho don la ston pa'i blo gros dang ldan par byas nas /
NK131(do)006:3251: yid chos la sdang ba las phyir phyogs par bya'o ///
NK131(do)006:3252: kye ma deng sang rnyigs dus 'dir //
NK131(do)006:3253: mkhas par khas che phal cher yang //
NK131(do)006:3254: don la mi ston tshig phyir 'breng //
NK131(do)006:3255: phyogs re'i cha bzung gcig shos smad //
NK131(do)006:3256: sdang shugs log rtog zhen blta yis //
NK131(do)006:3257: dri mas rab slad dam chos dor //
NK131(do)006:3258: nyon mongs kun nas dkris dbang gis //
NK131(do)006:3259: dam pa'i chos spangs de yi rgyus /
NK131(do)006:3261: phyi ma mnar med dmyal gting du //
NK131(do)006:3262: skyabs med gyur pa spyi tshugs ltung //
NK131(do)006:3263: dman pa bsod nams dman pa la //
NK131(do)006:3265: des na dam chos spong ba yi //
NK131(do)006:3266: las kyi rnam smin 'jigs pas na //
NK131(do)006:3267: skal med log rtog can ma gtogs //
NK131(do)006:3268: shes ldan su zhig 'di la rten //
NK131(do)006:3269: ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan gyi //
NK131(do)006:3270: zab mo'i chos la ma mos kyang //
NK131(do)006:3271: bskur pa gdab par mi bya ste //
NK131(do)006:3272: chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK131(do)006:3273: don nyid dran gyis mi gsung ngam //
NK131(do)006:3274: des na rgyal ba sras bcas kyi //
NK131(do)006:3275: gsung rab ma lus thams cad la //
NK131(do)006:3276: dad pas der rjes 'brang ba legs //
NK131(do)006:3277: bod kyi slob dpon phyogs zhen can //
NK131(do)006:3278: gzu bor mi gnas kha gcig gis //
NK131(do)006:3279: don la mi ston tshig phyir 'brangs //
NK131(do)006:3282: de lta min na rgya bod kyi //
NK131(do)006:3283: mkhas grub skyes mchog thams cad dang //
NK131(do)006:3284: bod du snga phyir byon pa yi //
NK131(do)006:3285: lo pan mkhas grub mang po yis //
NK131(do)006:3286: dpang dang tshad mar byas pa la //
NK131(do)006:3287: der rjes 'breng ba ci ma rung //
NK131(do)006:3288: rgya bod mkhas grub thams cad kyis //
NK131(do)006:3289: bshad bsgyur mdzad pa ma yin zhing //
NK131(do)006:3290: bod kyis rang bzo byas zer ba //
NK131(do)006:3291: dngos su snyon tol byed par zad //
NK131(do)006:3293: rgya bod mkhas grub thams cad kyis //
NK131(do)006:3294: bshad sgrub bsgyur ba ma yin zhes //
NK131(do)006:3295: nges par smra ba 'di mi rigs //
NK131(do)006:3296: yang na deng sang kha gcig gis //
NK131(do)006:3297: dus kyi 'khor lo la sogs pa'i //
NK131(do)006:3298: sems 'grel skor gsum thams cad la //
NK131(do)006:3300: rgyud 'grel de rnams thams cad la //
NK131(do)006:3301: len byed tshad ma med do lo //
NK131(do)006:3302: dus zhabs pa la sogs pa ni //
NK131(do)006:3303: chen po rnams la ma grags phyir //
NK131(do)006:3304: tshad ma'i skye bu ma yin lo //
NK131(do)006:3305: khyed kyang tshul 'di smra na smos //
NK131(do)006:3307: sangs rgyas gsang ba b+ai ma la //
NK131(do)006:3308: bee ro tsa na la sogs kyis //
NK131(do)006:3309: ma bsgyur ma mdzad thag chod ces //
NK131(do)006:3310: tshul min dran tshad smra ba yi //
NK131(do)006:3311: kha de bdud kyis ma phye 'am //
NK131(do)006:3312: spyir gyi gsar snying kha yar la //
NK131(do)006:3313: lhad sogs yod par smra mod kyis //
NK131(do)006:3314: snying ma rdzogs chen rjes 'breng bcas //
NK131(do)006:3315: tshig 'bru gcig kyang mi dag la //
NK131(do)006:3316: bod kyis brtsams pa'i chos log ces //
NK131(do)006:3318: des na mkhas pa blo gros ldan //
NK131(do)006:3319: dbang rnon chos rjes 'breng ba rnams //
NK131(do)006:3320: tshig la ma ston don la ston //
NK131(do)006:3321: yang na blun po mos pa brtan //
NK131(do)006:3322: dbang rtul dad rjes 'breng na yang //
NK131(do)006:3323: rgya bod mkhas grub 'di snyed kyi //
NK131(do)006:3325: 'phags pa'i yul gyi mkhas grub mchog /
NK131(do)006:3326: pad 'byung dri med bshes gnyen dang //
NK131(do)006:3327: sangs rgyas gsang ba h+aum ka ra //
NK131(do)006:3328: sgeg pa rdo rje dam pa sogs //
NK131(do)006:3329: rgya gar mkhas grub lta ci smos //
NK131(do)006:3330: bod du snga phyir byon pa yi //
NK131(do)006:3331: skyes chen dam pa thugs rje can //
NK131(do)006:3332: bee ro tsa na ka cog sogs //
NK131(do)006:3333: rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK131(do)006:3334: sad mi mi bdun la sogs pa'i //
NK131(do)006:3335: sngar byon lo pan thams cad dang //
NK131(do)006:3336: phyis kyi rngog btsun legs shes sogs //
NK131(do)006:3337: bka' gdams pa'i skyes chen dang //
NK131(do)006:3338: mnyam med dpal ldan sa skya pa //
NK131(do)006:3339: klu dbang bsrung ba la sogs nas //
NK131(do)006:3340: chos rje bsod rgyal yan chad kyi //
NK131(do)006:3341: skyes chen dam pa thams cad dang //
NK131(do)006:3342: mi la dgas po phag mo grub //
NK131(do)006:3344: dus gsum mkhyen dang karma pa //
NK131(do)006:3345: rang byung rdo rje chos kyi grags //
NK131(do)006:3346: sprul sku chos dpal bzang po yan //
NK131(do)006:3347: skyes chen karma pa rnams sogs //
NK131(do)006:3348: dgas po bka' brgyud thams cad dang //
NK131(do)006:3349: bka' babs skor gsum brgyud pa dang //
NK131(do)006:3350: ma gcig labs sgron la sogs pa'i //
NK131(do)006:3351: zhi gcod bka' brgyud thams cad dang //
NK131(do)006:3352: mnyam med shangs pa bka' brgyud sogs //
NK131(do)006:3353: bod kyi bka' brgyud de rnams dang //
NK131(do)006:3354: dus phyis grub chen gser stengs pa //
NK131(do)006:3356: mkhas grub u rgyan gnyan ras dang //
NK131(do)006:3359: rgyal ye yon tan rgya mtsho dang //
NK131(do)006:3360: dbang rgyal sher 'bum skal pa bzang //
NK131(do)006:3361: mkhan chen 'dzim pa spang khang pa //
NK131(do)006:3362: kun mkhyen chos rje yab sras dang //
NK131(do)006:3363: 'jam dbyangs brda ston rgyal ba g.yugs //
NK131(do)006:3364: mkhas grub g.yag sde pan chen sogs //
NK131(do)006:3365: bka' brgyud so so'i srol 'dzin pa'i //
NK131(do)006:3366: sdom brtson rig pa 'dzin pa yi //
NK131(do)006:3367: mkhas grub phal mo che rnams kyis //
NK131(do)006:3368: rdzogs chen la sogs snying ma la //
NK131(do)006:3369: thugs dam snying po mdzad pa mang //
NK131(do)006:3370: mkhas grub de dag thams cad las //
NK131(do)006:3371: log rtog can gyi gang zag 'ga' //
NK131(do)006:3372: lhag pa yin nam shes ldan dag /
NK131(do)006:3373: gang zag tshig la rab ston cing //
NK131(do)006:3374: rtog ge ngan la rab tu zhen //
NK131(do)006:3375: phyogs zhen chags sdang gis dkrugs pa'i //
NK131(do)006:3376: mkhas par rlom pa kha gcig dang //
NK131(do)006:3377: smra mkhams can gyi skye bo yi //
NK131(do)006:3378: rjes su 'brangs nas chos spangs na //
NK131(do)006:3379: rang gzhan gnyis ka nyams 'gyur bas //
NK131(do)006:3380: don med chos spongs bsags pa yi //
NK131(do)006:3381: rjes su ma 'brang shes ldan dag /
NK131(do)006:3382: gang la'ang phyogs lhung rab spangs shing //
NK131(do)006:3383: mkhas grub phyogs ris med pa yi //
NK131(do)006:3384: rjes su 'brongs shig shes ldan dag /
NK131(do)006:3385: bka' brgyud gong ma de dag las //
NK131(do)006:3386: da lta'i gang zag phal mo che //
NK131(do)006:3387: mkhas ltar snang yang snang tsam yin //
NK131(do)006:3388: mngon shes nyams rtogs chos spyan med //
NK131(do)006:3389: kun rtog ngan pas dpyad pa yi //
NK131(do)006:3390: log rtog ngan pa 'ba' zhig yin //
NK131(do)006:3391: bka' brgyud gong ma thams cad kyis //
NK131(do)006:3392: zhi phyag rdzogs gsum thams cad la //
NK131(do)006:3393: snying por mdzad pa mang snang bas //
NK131(do)006:3394: dad pas de rjes 'breng ba legs //
NK131(do)006:3395: gal te de rnams kyis nor na //
NK131(do)006:3396: gzhan gyi nor bas rab tu bzod //
NK131(do)006:3397: nor kyang nor sa ma nor mod //
NK131(do)006:3398: log par rtog la ci cha yod //
NK131(do)006:3399: rkun po rnams kyis khyir btags pas //
NK131(do)006:3400: ra skyes khur ba bram zer bor //
NK131(do)006:3401: log rtog can gyi skyes bo 'gas //
NK131(do)006:3403: chos spongs 'tshams med las lci ba'i //
NK131(do)006:3404: rjes su gang zag kha gcig kyang //
NK131(do)006:3405: zhugs nas mi bzad sdig pa'i las //
NK131(do)006:3406: byed pa phye lhebs mer 'phyogs mtshungs //
NK131(do)006:3407: gal te gang zag re re yis //
NK131(do)006:3408: log rjes 'brengs nas rdzogs chen sogs //
NK131(do)006:3409: rdo rje theg pa sun 'byin nas //
NK131(do)006:3410: mi bzad sdig to'i las byed na //
NK131(do)006:3411: gangs can khrod kyi chos rnams la //
NK131(do)006:3412: nyams su blang rung nyin skar tsam //
NK131(do)006:3413: de yi rgyu mtshan 'di lta ste //
NK131(do)006:3414: zhi phyag gcod dang ro snyoms dang //
NK131(do)006:3415: lam 'bras rdo rje'i tshig rkang dang //
NK131(do)006:3416: bde mchog snyan brgyud sems khrid dang //
NK131(do)006:3417: thabs lam gtum mo zhag bdun dang //
NK131(do)006:3418: dpal ldan dus kyi 'khor lo sogs //
NK131(do)006:3419: sems 'grel skor gsum man ngag bcas //
NK131(do)006:3420: gsang 'dus gnyis med rnam rgyal dang //
NK131(do)006:3421: bde mchog ra li'i skor la sogs //
NK131(do)006:3422: rgyud sde phal mo che rnams kun //
NK131(do)006:3423: bka' dang chos min ma sgrubs sam //
NK131(do)006:3424: legs par dpyod dang shes ldan dag /
NK131(do)006:3425: bdag ni tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK131(do)006:3426: dal thob mtho ris yon tan ldan //
NK131(do)006:3427: bshes gnyen mchog la sogs pa yi //
NK131(do)006:3428: dam chos sgrub pa'i 'thun rkyen rnams //
NK131(do)006:3429: ma tshang med par 'byor gyur nas /
NK131(do)006:3430: rgyal ba'i bstan pa thams cad la //
NK131(do)006:3431: phyogs ris med pa'i dad thob nas //
NK131(do)006:3432: tshul bzhin nyams su len par shog /
NK131(do)006:3433: tshul bzhin nyams len ma nus nang //
NK131(do)006:3434: rgyal ba'i gsung rab thams cad la //
NK131(do)006:3435: phyogs med dad pa byed par shog /
NK131(do)006:3437: rdzogs pa chen po la sogs pa /
NK131(do)006:3438: sngags snying ma rjes 'breng dang bcas pa'i tshig don la /
NK131(do)006:3439: log par rtog pa'i 'khrul pa ngan pa 'joms pa'i bstan bcos /
NK131(do)006:3440: log rtog 'khrul 'joms shes bya ba 'di ni /
NK131(do)006:3441: theg pa chog gi rnal 'byor pa /
NK131(do)006:3442: klong kun mkhyen dri med 'od zer sogs mtshan bdun du grags pa de nyid kyis /
NK131(do)006:3444: dpyid zla ra ba hor lugs kyi zla ba dang po /
NK131(do)006:3445: bcom ldan 'das kyis cho 'phrul chen pos /
NK131(do)006:3446: mu mu stegs kyi ston pa drug la logs pa /
NK131(do)006:3447: stegs pa rnams pham par mdzad pa'i dus kyi zla ba'i /
NK131(do)006:3448: dkar phyogs kyi tshes bcu'i nyin par rdzogs par bris pa 'dis /
NK131(do)006:3449: log par rtog pa rnams kyi 'khrul pa thams cad bcom nas /
NK131(do)006:3450: phyis rdzogs pa chen po'i chos la skyabs kyi dam pa mchog du byed par gyur cig //
NK131(do)006:3452: 'bri khung dpal 'dzin gyis gsung rnams la ser mgo dang /
NK131(do)006:3453: kun mkhyen klong chen rab 'byams kyi gsung rnams mtshal mgo dkar 'jam rnams yin gsung pa /
NK131(do)006:3454: phyi mo la yang gsal bar 'khod 'dug lags /
